var book = {
	"name": "Ki Kam",
	"numChapters": 28,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka jingïathuhkhana ka banyngkong nga la thaw, A Theophilos, shaphang kiei kiei baroh kiba U Jisu u la sdang ban leh bad ban hikai ruh,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> haduh kata ka sngi ha kaba la pdiang ïa u sha jrong, ynda u la ai hukum da U Mynsiem Bakhuid ha kita ki apostol ïa kiba u la lah jied:",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ha kiba u la pynpaw im ruh ïa lade, hadien ba u la shah, da bun ki dak shynna, ba la ïohi ïa u da ki, jin sawphew sngi, bad u da ïathuh ïa kiei kiei ruh shaphang ka hima U Blei.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te haba u la ïaseng lem bad ki, u la hukum ïa ki ban ym leit noh na Jerusalem, hynrei, ban ap ïa ka jingkular jong U Kpa, kaba u ong, “Phi la ïohsngew na nga.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Naba u Ïoannis shisha u la pynbaptis da ka um, hynrei, yn pynbaptis ïa phi da U Mynsiem Bakhuid sa khyndiat sngi naduh mynta.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Kumta, haba ki la ïawan lang, ki la ïakylli ïa u, ki da ong, “Ko Trai, ha kane ka por men pynïoh pat ïa ka hima ha ki Israel?”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> U la ïathuh te ha ki, “Ym dei ïa phi ban tip ïa ki Ïa lane ki aïom kiba U Kpa u la buh ha ka bor jong u hi.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, phin ïoh diang ïa ka bor, ynda la wan U Mynsiem Bakhuid ha phi; bad phin long ki nongphla ïa nga ha Jerusalem, bad ha Judia baroh bad ha Samaria, bad haduh bakut ka pyrthei.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda u la lah ïathuh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, haba ki dang ïakhmih, la shim noh ïa u sha jrong; bad u lyoh u la pdiang noh ïa U ba kim ïohi shuh ïa U.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba ki dang ïakhmih shaiñ sha bneng, katba u dang kiew, ha khmih, ar ngut ki rangbah ki la ïawan ïeng hajan jong ki ha ki jaiñkup balieh;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> kiba la ong ruh, “Ko rangbah Galilaïa, balei phi ïeng khmied sha bneng? Une U Jisu ïa uba la shim noh sha jrong na phi sha bneng, un wan ha kajuh ka rukom kumba phi la ïohi ïa u ba u leit sha bneng.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïaleit phai sha Jerusalem na u lum ba la khot “Olib”, uba hajan Jerusalem, kat ka jingleit sngi Sabbaton.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ynda ki la lah ïapoi hapoh, ki la ïakiew sha ka kamra kaba haneng ha kaba ki la ïashong; u Petros bad u Ïoannis, bad u Jakob bad u Andriw, u Philip bad u Thomas, u Bartholomai bad u Mathaïos, u Jakob u khun u Alphaïos, bad u Simon uba Shitrhem, bad u Juda u para u Jakob.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Kine baroh ki la ïaineh da kawei ka jingmut ha ka jingduwai, lem bad ki kynthei, bad ka Mari ka kmie U Jisu, lem bad ki para jong u de.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Ha kita ki sngi te, haba u Petros u la ïeng hapdeng ki synran, u la ong (te ka jingïalang ki briew ka la long jin shispah arphew),",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “Ko para, ka la dei ban pyndep ïa kata Ka Jingthoh, ïa kaba U Mynsiem Bakhuid u la kren mynshuwa da ka shyntur u Dabid shaphang u Judas, uba la long u nongïalam ïa kita kiba la kem ïa U Jisu:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> naba la ñiew ïa u lem bad ngi bad u la ïoh ka bynta ha kane ka kam.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te une u briew, u la thied ïa ka lyngkha da ka bainong ka jingbymhok; bad haba u la hap khongpong, u la pait ar liang, bad la mih noh ki snier jong u baroh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ïa kane, ki la tip baroh kiba shong ha Jerusalem, kat ban khot ïa kata ka lyngkha ha ka ktien jong ki hi, “Akeldama”, kata ka long, “Ka lyngkha ka snam.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Naba la thoh ha ka kitab Ki Salm, “ ‘Ai ba ka jaka shong jong u kan long kaba kynjah, bad wat ai ban don ba shong ha ka’; “bad, “ ‘Ai un shim da uwei pat ïa ka kam jong u.’",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> “Namar kata, na kita ki briew kiba la ïalang bad ngi baroh shi katta ba U Trai Jisu u la ïawan ïaleit ruh hapdeng jong ngi,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> ba la sdang naduh ka jingbaptis u Ïoannis, haduh kata ka sngi ha kaba la shim noh ïa u sha jrong na ngi, uwei na kita ka dei ban thung kum u nongphla lem bad ngi shaphang ka jingmihpat jong U.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki la pynïeng ar ngut, u Joseph uba la khot “Barsabas”, uba la sin “Justos”, bad u Matthias.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Bad ki la ïaduwai, ki la ong, “A me, U Trai uba ithuh ïa ki dohnud baroh, to pyni uno na kine ar ngut ba me la jied,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> ban shim ïa kata ka bynta ha kane ka kam bad ka kam apostol, na kaba u Judas u la hap noh, ba un leit sha la ka jong ka jaka.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad ki la pynnoh ïa ki jingïathong na ka bynta jong ki; te kata ka jingïathong ka la hap ha u Matthias; kumta, la ñiew ïa u lem bad kita ki khatwei ngut ki apostol."
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda la poi ka sngi Pentekost, ki baroh ki la ïadon lang ha kawei ka jaka.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te kyndit kyndit la wan ka jingsawa na bneng kum ka lyer bah ba beh kyrthep, bad ka la pyndap ïa ka ïing baroh kawei ha kaba ki la ïashong.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad la paw ha ki, ki thylliej kiba pait pnat, kum ka ding; te ka la shong halor uwei pa uwei na ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad la pyndap ïa ki baroh da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, bad ki la ïasdang ban kren ha kiwei pat ki thylliej, kat kumba U Mynsiem u la ai bor ïa ki ban kren.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te la don ki Jiw kiba shong basa ha Jerusalem, ki briew ki bariewblei na ki jaid bynriew baroh kiba napoh ka bneng.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba la ïohsngew ïa kane ka jingsawa, u paidbah u la ïawan lang bad u la sngewlyngngoh, naba u briew baroh u la ïohsngew ba ki kren ha ka ktien jong u hi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Baroh te ki la kyndit thred, bad ki la sngewphylla, ki da ïa-ong, “Ha khmih kine baroh kiba kren kim long ki nong Galilaïa?",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Kumno te ngi, ngi ïohsngew, u briew baroh ha la ka jong ka jong ka ktien ha kaba la kha ïa ngi?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ki Parthia, bad ki Mid, bad ki Elam, bad kiba shong ha Mesopotamia, ha Judia, bad ha Kappadokia, ha Pontos, bad ha Asia,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> ha Phrygia, bad ha Pamphilia, ha Ijipt, bad ha ki phang ka Libya kaba hajan Kyrini, ki nongshong basa kiba na Rom, ki Jiw bad kiba la kylla niam ruh,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> ki Krit, bad ki Arab, ngi ïaïohsngew ba ki da ïakren ha ki thylliej jong ngi hi, ïa ki kam baphylla jong U Blei!”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Baroh te ki la kyndit thred, bad ki la ïasngewlyngngoh lyngngaiñ, ki ïa-ong paralok hi, “Ka mut aïu kane?”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, kiwei da kaba beiñ ki la ong, “Ki la kdang Waiñ thymmai.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, haba u Petros u la ïeng lem bad ki khatwei ngut, u la pynjam la ka ktien, bad u la ïathuh ha ki: “Ko phi ki rangbah Judia, bad phi baroh kiba shong ha Jerusalem, to phin tip ïa kane, bad to shahshkor ïa ki ktien jong nga:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> naba kine, kim buaid kumba tharai ma phi, namar ka dang shi por ka sngi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, kane ka long kata ba la ong da u Joel u nongïathuhlypa:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “ ‘Kan jia ruh ha ki sngi ki bakhatduh,’ ong U Blei, ‘ba ngan theh noh na U Mynsiem jong nga halor ka doh baroh; te ki khun shynrang jong phi bad ki khun kynthei jong phi kin ïathuhlypa, bad ki samla jong phi kin ïohi ïa ki jingithuhpaw, bad ki tymmen jong phi ruh kin phohsniew ki jingphohsniew:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad halor ki shakri jong nga ruh shynrang bad kynthei ha kita ki sngi ngan theh noh na U Mynsiem jong nga, bad kin ïathuhlypa.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ngan pyni ïa ki jingphylla ha bneng sha jrong, bad ïa ki dak ha ka khyndew sha tbian, ka snam, bad ka ding, bad u lyoh tdem;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> ïa ka sngi yn pynkylla dum, bad ïa u bnai yn pynkylla snam, mynshuwa ban wan kata ka sngi ka jong U Trai kaba khraw bad ba-itriem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad kan jia ba uno uno baroh u ban khot kyrpad ïa ka kyrteng U Trai, yn pynim ïa u.’",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> “Ko ki rangbah Israel, to sngew ïa kine ki ktien: ïa U Jisu uba na Nasaret, u briew ba U Blei u la pynithuh shynna ha phi da ki kambah, bad da ki jingphylla, bad da ki dak khyllah de, kiba U Blei u la leh da u hapdeng jong phi, kumba phi hi ruh phi tip,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ïa une, ba la aiti noh da ka jingthmu ba la buh, bad da ka jingtip lypa U Blei; ma phi da ki kti pop phi la sahnarphna, phi la pynïap ruh;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> ïa uba U Blei u la pynmih pat, da kaba u la law noh ïa ki jingkhum ka jingïap; namar kam lah long ban bat ma ka, ïa u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Namar u Dabid u ong shaphang jong u, “ ‘Nga la ïohi ïa U Trai ha khmat jong nga khlem da pud, naba u long sha kamon jong nga, ba yn ym pynkhih ïa nga:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> namar kata, ka dohnud jong nga ka la sngewkmen, bad u thylliej jong nga u la kmen; bad ka doh jong nga ruh putet kan shong ha ka jingkyrmen:",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> namar men ym iehnoh ïa ka mynsiem jong nga ha Hades, lymne men ym shah ïa U Bakhuid jong me ban shem ïa kaba pyut.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Me la pyntip ïa nga ïa ki lynti ka jingim; men pyndap ïa nga da ka jingkmen ha khmat jong me.’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Ko para, nga lah ban ong shynna ha phi shaphang u Dabid u kthaw tymmen, ba u la ïap noh bad ba la tep ruh ïa u, bad ka jingtep jong u, ka don bad ngi haduh kane ka sngi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Namar kata, ba u long u nongïathuhlypa, bad ba u tip ba U Blei u la lah kular da ka jingsmai ha u, ba na u soh ka syngkai jong u, un pynmih ïa uwei u ban shong ha ka khet jong u;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> haba u la ïohi lypa, u kren shaphang kata ka jingmihpat U Khrist, ba ym shym la iehnoh ïa ka mynsiem jong U ha Hades, ka doh jong U ruh kam shym shem ïa kaba pyut.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ïa une U Jisu keiñ, U Blei u la pynmih pat; shaphang kata, ma ngi baroh ngi long ki nongphla.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Namar kata, haba la kyntiew ïa u da ka kti kamon U Blei, bad haba u la ïoh diang na U Kpa ïa ka jingkular ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid, u la theh noh ïa kane, ïa kaba phi mynta phi ïohi bad phi ïohsngew.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Namar u Dabid um shym la kiew sha ki bneng; hynrei u ong hi, “ ‘U Trai u la ong ha U Trai jong nga: “To shong sha ka kti kamon jong nga,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> tad ynda ngan pynlong ïa kiba shun ïa me, ka jingïuh kjat jong me.” ’",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “To ka ïing Israel baroh kawei, namar kata, kan tip skhem, ba U Blei u la pynlong U Trai bad U Khrist ïa une ujuh U Jisu, ïa uba la sahnarphna ma phi.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te haba ki la ïohsngew ïa kane, la dung ngak ïa ki ha la ka dohnud, bad ki la ong ha u Petros, bad ha kita kiwei ki apostol, “A para, kumno ngin leh?”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te u Petros u la ïathuh ha ki, “To phin kylla-ka-bamut, bad yn pynbaptis ïa phi uwei pa uwei ha ka kyrteng U Jisu Khrist, ïa ka ban ïohmap ki pop; bad phin ïoh diang ïa ka jingai U Mynsiem Bakhuid.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Namar ka jingkular ka long ïa phi, bad ïa ki khun jong phi, bad ïa baroh kiba sha jngai, kat kiba U Trai uba U Blei jong ngi un khot ha u.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Da ki shibun kiwei pat ki ktien u la pyni, bad u la kyntu ïa ki, u da ong, “To pynim ïa lade na kane ka pateng bynriew bakynriang.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Namar kata, ïa kita kiba la pdiang ïa ka ktien jong u, la pynbaptis; kumta la pynïasoh ha kata ka sngi sha ka balang kumba lai hajar ki mynsiem.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Bad ki la ïaineh skhem ha ka jinghikai jong ki apostol, bad ha ka jingïasyllok, bad ha kaba kdiah kpu, bad ha ki jingduwai de.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te ka jingsheptieng ka la jia ha ki mynsiem baroh, bad bun ki jingphylla bad ki dak khyllah la leh da ki apostol.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Te baroh kiba la ngeit ki la ïalong hajuh, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh ki la ïaleh lang;",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> bad ki la ïadie noh ïa la ki bri, ïa la ki ïing, bad ïa la ki mar, bad ki la ïasam ïa ki ha baroh, kat ha kiba donkam.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ha la ka sngi ruh ki da ïaineh skhem ha kawei ka jingmut ha ka templ; bad haba ki da kdiah kpu ha ka ïing ka ïing, ki la ïabam da ka jingkmen bad da ka jingsngewbeit ka dohnud,",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> ki da ïaroh ïa U Blei, bad ki da shem ka jingsngewbha na ki briew baroh. Bad U Trai ruh u la nang pynïasoh ha ki ha la ka sngi ïa kita kiba la lait im."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Petros bad u Ïoannis ki dang ïaleit kiew sha ka templ ha ka por jingduwai, ha kaba khyndai baje.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad la don uwei u briew u ba-dkoh naduh ka kpoh ka kmie jong u, uba ki la bah, ïa uba ki ju buh ha la ka sngi ha ka khyrdop ka templ kaba ki khot “Ka Baitynnad”, ban pan ka jingai isynei na kita kiba ïaleit rung shapoh kata ka templ;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> uta, haba u la ïohi ïa u Petros bad u Ïoannis ba kin sa leit rung shapoh ka templ, u la pan ban ïoh ka jingai isynei.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U Petros te, haba u la khmih shaiñ ha u, lem bad u Ïoannis, u la ong, “To khmih ha ngi.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta, u la khmih dngong ïa ki, ba u da kyrmen ban ïoh ei ei na ki.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, u Petros u la ong, “Ka rupa bad ka ksiar ngam don, hynrei, ïa kaba nga don, nga ai ïa me. Ha ka kyrteng U Jisu Khrist uba na Nasaret, to ïaid.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad u la shim ïa u na ka kti kamon, bad u la pynïeng ïa u; te kumne kumne ruh ki kjat bad ki matsohlah jong u ki la khlaiñ.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad haba u la kynrong joit u la ïeng, bad u la sdang ïaid, bad u la leit rung lem bad ki shapoh ka templ, u da ïaid, u da rynsied, bad u da ïaroh ïa U Blei.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad u paidbah baroh u la ïohi ïa u ba u ïaid, bad ba u ïaroh ïa U Blei;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad ki la ithuh ïa u, ba u la long uta uba ju shong ban ïoh ka jingai isynei ha kata ka khyrdop “Ka Baitynnad” jong ka templ; te ki la dap da ka jingsngewphylla, bad da ka jingsngewlyngngoh ïa kata ba la jia ha u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te katba u dang bat ïa u Petros bad ïa u Ïoannis, uta u paidbah baroh u la ïaphet lang sha ki, sha kata ka baranda kaba ki khot “Ka jong u Solomon”, ba ki da sngewkyndit eh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Haba u Petros te u la ïohi, u la ong ha uta u paidbah, “Ko ki rangbah Israel, balei phi sngewphylla ïa kane? lane balei phi ïakhmih shaiñ ïa ngi, kumba da ka bor lane da ka jingriewblei jong ngi hi, ba ngi la pynïaid ïa une u briew?",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U Blei u Abraham, bad u Isaak, bad u Jakob, U Blei ki kpa jong ngi, u la pyndonburom ïa U Khun jong U, U Jisu, ïa uba phi la aiti noh, bad phi la len ha khmat u Pilat, mynba u la lah thmu ban pyllait noh ïa U.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, phi, phi la len ïa uta U Bakhuid bad U Bahok; bad phi la ïapan ban pyllait ha phi ïa u nongpynïap briew:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> bad ïa U Syiem ka jingim, phi la pynïap noh; ïa uba U Blei u la pynmih pat na ki baïap; shaphang kata, ngi, ngi long ki nongphla.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad da ka jingngeit ha ka kyrteng jong U, ïa une u briew uba phi ïohi bad ba phi ithuh, ka kyrteng jong U, ka la pynkhlaiñ: kata ka jingngeit keiñ kaba da U, ka la ai ha une, ïa kane ka jingkhiah khran ha khmat jong phi baroh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Hynrei mynta, ko para, nga tip ba na ka jingbymtip phi la leh ïa kata, kumjuh kumba ki nongsynshar jong phi ruh ki la leh.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, ïa kita kiei kiei kiba U Blei u la lah pyni lypa da ka shyntur ki nongïathuhlypa baroh, ba un shah U Khrist jong U, U la pyndep kumta.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Namar kata, to kylla-ka-bamut, to wan phai khmat ruh, ban ïoh pyndam noh ïa ki pop jong phi, ba kumta kin ïoh wan ki aïom shong pyngngad na khmat U Trai,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad ba un ïoh phah ïa uta U Khrist, ïa uba la thung khnang ïa phi, U Jisu keiñ,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> ïa uba ka dei ïa ka bneng ban pdiang haduh ki aïom ka jingpynthymmai ïa kiei kiei baroh, ïa kiba U Blei u la kren da ka shyntur ki nongïathuhlypa bakhuid jong U kiba naduh mynbarim.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> U Moses shisha u la ong, ‘U Trai uba U Blei jong phi, un pynmih ïa u nongïathuhlypa ha phi na ki para jong phi, uba kum ma nga; ïa u, phin shahshkor ha kiei kiei baroh katba un kren ha phi.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Bad kan jia ruh, ba ïa ka mynsiem baroh ka ban ym shahshkor ïa uta u nongïathuhlypa, yn pynduh noh khoit napdeng u paidlang.’",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Shisha keiñ ki nongïathuhlypa baroh ruh naduh u Samuel, bad kita kiba bud hadien, kat kiba la kren, ki ruh ki la ïathuh shaphang kine ki sngi.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Phi long ki khun kita ki nongïathuhlypa, bad ki jong kata ka jutang ïa kaba U Blei u la pynlong bad ki kpa jong phi, ba U ong ha u Abraham, ‘Ha u symbai jong me yn kyrkhu ïa ki jaid bynriew jong ka pyrthei baroh.’",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ha phi nyngkong, U Blei u la pynmih ïa la U Khun, bad U la phah ïa u, ban kyrkhu ïa phi, da kaba pynphai noh ïa uwei pa uwei na phi na ki jingbymhok jong phi.”"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba ki dang kren ha uta u paidlang, ki lyngdoh, bad u rangbah ka templ, bad ki Saddusi, ki la wan kyndit ha ki,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ba ki da sngewsih sat namar ba ki hikai ïa u paidlang, bad ba ki ïalap da U Jisu ïa ka jingmihpat na ki baïap.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ki la kem ïa ki, bad ki la set byndi ïa ki haduh lashai, namar ka la long la janmiet lypa.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, bun na kita kiba la lah ïohsngew ïa kata ka ktien, ki la ngeit, bad ka jingkheiñ ïa ki rangbah ka la long kumba san hajar.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ka la jia te ynda kum lashai, ba ki nongsynshar jong ki, bad ki tymmen basan, bad ki nongthoh de, ki la ïalum lang ha Jerusalem,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> bad u Annas u rangbah lyngdoh, bad u Kaïaphas, bad u Ïoannis, bad u Aleksander, bad kat kiba la long na ka jaid rangbah lyngdoh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba ki la pynïeng ïa ki hapdeng, ki la kylli, “Da ka bor aïu, lane da ka kyrteng aïu, phi la leh ïa kane?”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ynda kumta, u Petros, uba la dap da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, u la ong ha ki, “Ko phi ki nongsynshar jong u paidlang, bad ki tymmen basan,",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> lada yn kylli ïit ïa ngi ha kane ka sngi shaphang kata ka kam babha ïa uta u briew u ba-dkoh, kumno ba la pynkhiah ïa u,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> to tip phi baroh, bad u paidlang Israel baroh, ba da ka kyrteng U Jisu Khrist uba na Nasaret, ïa uba la sahnarphna ma phi, ïa uba U Blei u la pynmih pat na ki baïap, da uta keiñ, une u ïeng hangne ha khmat jong phi uba la khiah khran.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Une u long uta u maw ïa uba la kyntait beiñ noh da phi ki nongtei, ïa uba la pynlong ha khlieh ka dong.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ym don ka jingpynim hano hano ha uwei pat: naba ym don kawei pat ka kyrteng hapoh ka bneng, ïa kaba la ai hapdeng ki briew, da kaba ka dei ba yn pynim ïa ngi.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te haba ki la khmih thuh ïa kata ka jingshlur jong u Petros bad u Ïoannis, bad ki la sngewthuh ruh ba ki long ki briew kiba khlem jinghikai bad kiba bieit, ki la ïasngewphylla; hynrei, ki la ithuh ïa ki, ba ki la ju don lem bad U Jisu.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Haba ki da ïohi te ïa uta u briew ïa uba la pynkhiah, ba u da ïeng lem bad ki, kim don ei ei ruh em ban ïasaid kylliang.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, haba ki la hukum ïa ki ban kynriah noh shabar ka dorbar, ki la ïasylla paralok hi,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> ki da ong, “Aïu ngin leh ïa kine ki briew? namar shisha ba ïa ka dak khyllah ba-donnam la leh da ki, ka la paw shai ha baroh kiba shong ha Jerusalem; bad ïa kata ngim lah ban len.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, ba kan ym phriang shuh hapdeng u paidbah, to ngin ïabyrngem ïa ki, ba naduh mynta kin ym kren shuh hano hano ruh ha kane ka kyrteng.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kumta, haba ki la khot ïa ki, ki la hukum ïa ki ban ym kren satia lymne hikai ha ka kyrteng U Jisu.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, u Petros bad u Ïoannis ki la ïathuh bad ki la ong ha ki, “La ka shong hok ha khmat U Blei ban sngap ïa phi kham tam ban ïa U Blei, to khan ma phi:",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> namar ngi ngim lah ban ym kren ïa kiei kiei ruh, ïa kiba ngi la ïohi bad ngi la ïohsngew.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta, ki, haba ki la nang byrngem shuh ïa ki, ki la pyllait noh ïa ki; ba kim shem lad ban pynshitom ïa ki, namar uta u paidlang, naba ki briew baroh ki la ïa-pyndonburom ïa U Blei na ka bynta kata kaba la leh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Namar uta u briew u la palat sawphew snem ka rta, ha uba la leh ïa kane ka dak khyllah jong ka jingkhiah khran.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba la pyllait noh ïa ki, ki la wan sha la ki lok, bad ki la ïathuh baroh ïa kaba ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki tymmen basan ki la ong ha ki.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ki te haba ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki la ïa-pynjam ïa la ka ktien ha U Blei da kawei ka jingmut, bad ki la ïa-ong, “A Trai Kynrad, me U Blei uba la thaw ïa ka bneng, bad ïa ka khyndew, bad ïa ka duriaw, bad ïa baroh kat kiba don ha ki,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> uba da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, da ka shyntur u Dabid u kpa jong ngi u shakri jong me, me la ong: “ ‘Balei ba ki Jentil ki la ïabitar lep, bad ba ki paidbah ki la ïapyrkhat ïa kiei kiei kiba thala?",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ki syiem ka pyrthei ki la ïaïeng ïaleh, bad ki nongsynshar ki la ïalum lang pyrshah ïa U Trai, bad pyrshah ïa U Khrist jong u.’",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> “Namar da shisha ha kane ka shnong, u Herod bad u Pontios Pilat, lem bad ki Jentil bad ki paidbah Israel, ki la ïalum lang ïa ka ban ïaleh ïa U Jisu U Khun u bakhuid jong me, ïa uba me la pynsleh,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ïa ka ban leh ïa kiei kiei ruh katba ka kti jong me bad ka jingpyrkhat jong me, ki la lah thmu lypa ba kin jia.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te mynta, A Trai, to khmih ha ki jingbyrngem jong ki, to ai ruh ha ki shakri jong me ban kren ïa ka ktien jong me da ka jingsngewshlur suda,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> da kaba me kner noh ïa la ka kti ban pynkhiah; bad ba yn ïoh leh ïa ki dak khyllah bad ki jingphylla da ka kyrteng U Khun Bakhuid jong me U Jisu.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ynda ki la lah duwai te, la pynkhynñiuh ïa kata ka jaka ha kaba ki la ïaseng, bad la pyndap ïa ki baroh da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, bad ki la kren ïa ka ktien U Blei da ka jingsngewshlur.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te u paidbah jong kita kiba la ngeit, u la long da kawei ka dohnud bad kawei ka mynsiem; bad uwei ruh um ong shuh ba ka long ka jong u hi kaei kaei ruh na kita kiei kiei kiba u don; hynrei, kiei kiei baroh ki long kiba ïadei lang.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Bad da ka borbah, ki apostol ki la phla ïa ka jingmihpat jong U Trai Jisu: te ka jingaiei bakhraw ka la long ha ki baroh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Naba ym don uwei ruh u bakyrduh hapdeng jong ki; naba kat kiba la long ki trai ki bri lane ki ïing, ki la die noh bad ki la wallam ïa ki dor jong kita kiei kiei ba la lah die,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> bad ki la buh ïa ki ha kjat ki apostol; bad la sam ïa ki ha uwei pa uwei katba uno uno ruh u donkam.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Kumta, u Joseph, ïa uba la sin “Barnabas” da ki apostol (kaba haba la batai, ka long, “U Khun ka jingpyntngen”), u jaid Lebi, u kynja Kypros,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> ba u don ka bri, u la die noh ïa ka, bad u la wallam ïa ki sbai, bad u la buh ïa ki ha kjat ki apostol."
		},
		"5": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hynrei, uwei u briew uba kyrteng “u Ananias”, lem bad ka Saphira ka tnga jong u, u la die ïa ka bri,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad u la buhrieh ïa lade shi bynta na ka jong ka dor, ka tnga jong u ruh ka la ïabuit lem ïa kata; te u la wallam tang shi bynta, bad u la buh ïa ka ha kjat ki apostol.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, u Petros u la ong, “Ko Ananias, hato balei ba u Soitan u la pyndap ïa ka dohnud jong me, ïa ka ban shukor ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid, bad ban buhrieh noh shi bynta na ka dor kata ka bri?",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Katba ka dang sah, kam shym la long ka jong me hi? bad ynda la die noh ruh ïa ka, kam shym la don ha ka bor jong me hi? hato balei ba me la pun ïa kane ha ka dohnud jong me? mem shym la shukor ïa ki briew, hynrei, ïa U Blei.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba u Ananias u la ïohsngew ïa kine ki ktien, u la kyllon khram, bad u la dkut mynsiem. Ka jingsheptieng bakhraw te ka la hap ha kita baroh kiba la ïohsngew ïa kata.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki samla ki la ïeng joit, bad ki la ïasop spaiñ ïa u, bad haba ki la ïabah noh shabar, ki la tep ïa u.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ynda la dap kumba shi por, ka tnga jong u, haba kam pat tip ïa kaba la lah jia, ka la wan rung.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Petros u la ong ha ka, “To ïathuh ha nga, tang katta phi la ïadie noh ïa kata ka bri?” Ka la ïathuh te, “Ho-oid, tang katta keiñ.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, u Petros u la ong ha ka, “Hato balei ba phi la ïakut lem ban tynjuh ïa U Mynsiem U Trai? Ha khmih, ki kjat jong kita kiba la ïatep ïa u tnga jong pha, ki ha kato ka jingkhang, te kin ïabah noh shabar ïa pha ruh.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te shisyndon ka la kyllon ha ki kjat jong u, bad ka la dkut mynsiem. Te haba kita ki samla ki la rung, ki la shem ba ka la lah ïap; bad haba ki la ïabah noh shabar ïa ka, ki la ïatep ïa ka ha syndah u tnga jong ka.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ka jingsheptieng bakhraw te ka la ngat ha kata ka balang baroh kawei, bad ha baroh kiba la ïohsngew ïa kine kiei kiei.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad la leh bun ki dak khyllah bad ki jingphylla hapdeng uta u paidbah da ki kti kita ki apostol; baroh ruh ki la ïalong da kawei ka jingmut ha kata ka baranda u Solomon.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, na kita kiwei pat, ym don ba nud ban ïalok bad ki, pynban, uta u paidlang u pynkhraw ïa ki.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ïa kiba ngeit la nang pynïasoh kham bun kham bun ha U Trai, ki paidbah shynrang bad kynthei,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> kat ban bah shabar ïa ki bapang khrew ha ki lynti shnong, bad ban buh ïa ki ha ki palong bad ha ki khalti, ba ynda u Petros u wan ïaid, kan shu ïoh kah wat tang ka syrngiew jong u halor kiba na ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te u paidbah na ki shnong baroh sawdong, u la ïawan lang sha Jerusalem, ki ïawallam ïa ki bapang khrew bad ïa kiba la shitom eh da ki mynsiem bymkhuid, bad la pynkhiah ïa ki baroh.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te haba uta u rangbah lyngdoh u la ïeng joit, bad kita baroh kiba ïadon lem bad u, kiba long ka jaid niam ki Saddusi, la pyndap ïa ki da ka jingïa-ing;",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ki la kem ïa ki apostol, bad ki la set ïa ki ha ka ïing byndi.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, mynmiet, u angel U Trai u la plie wang ïa ki jingkhang kata ka ïing byndi, bad haba u la ïalam noh ïa ki shabar, u la ong,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> “To khie leit phi, da ïeng bad ïalap ruh ha ka templ ha u paidlang ïa ki ktien baroh jong kane Ka Jingim.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te haba ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki la ïarung shapoh ka templ la dang shu shai phar, bad ki la hikai. Hynrei, haba uta u rangbah lyngdoh u la wan, bad kita kiba bad u, ki la ïakhot lang ïa ka dorbar, bad ïa ki tymmen basan baroh jong ki khun Israel, bad ki la ïaphah sha ïing byndi ban wallam noh ïa ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, kita ki shakri kiba la wan, kim shem ïa ki ha ka ïing byndi: bad haba ki la leit phai, ki la ïathuh,",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> ki da ong, “Ïa kata ka ïing byndi, shisha ngi la shem ba la khang skhem, bad ki nongap ki ïeng ha ki jingkhang, hynrei, haba ngi la lah plie, ngim shym shem ïano ïano ruh hapoh.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba u rangbah ka templ, bad kita ki rangbah lyngdoh ki la ïohsngew ïa kine ki ktien, ki la sngewlyngngoh lyngngaiñ shaphang jong ki, aïu kane ka long.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te la wan uwei, bad u la ïathuh ha ki, “Ha khmih, kita ki briew ïa kiba phi la set ha ka ïing byndi, ki don ha ka templ, ki da ïeng, bad ki da hikai ïa u paidlang.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ynda kumta, haba uta u rangbah u la leit lem bad kita ki shakri, u la ïalam noh ïa ki, ym da ka bor, naba ki la sheptieng ïa uta u paidbah, ïoh ba yn lynthem maw ïa ki.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te haba ki la wallam ïa ki, ki la pynïeng ïa ki ha khmat ka dorbar, bad uta u rangbah lyngdoh u la kylli ïa ki,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> u da ong, “Ngi la hukum skhem ïa phi ban ym hikai ha kane ka kyrteng, te ha khmih, phi la pyndap ïa ka Jerusalem da ka jinghikai jong phi, bad phi ïathmu ban pynkit ha ngi ïa ka snam jong une u briew.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te u Petros bad ki apostol, ki la ïathuh bad ki la ïa-ong, “Ngi dei ban kohnguh ïa U Blei kham tam ban ïa ki briew.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U Blei ki kpa jong ngi u la pynmih pat ïa U Jisu, ïa uba phi la pynïap da kaba sdien ïa u ha u dieng.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ïa une, U Blei u la kyntiew sha ka kti kamon jong u, ban long U Syiem bad U Nongpynim, ïa ka ban ai ka jingkylla-ka-bamut ha u Israel, bad ka jingmap ki pop.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ngi te ngi long ki sakhi ïa kine kiei kiei ruh; kumjuh ruh U Mynsiem Bakhuid, ïa uba U Blei u la ai ha kita kiba kohnguh ïa u.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Hynrei, haba ki la ïohsngew ïa kane, ki la bitar eh lep, bad ki la thmu ban pynïap noh ïa ki.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hynrei, haba la ïeng joit uwei ha kata ka dorbar, u Pharisi, uba kyrteng “u Gamaliel”, u nonghikai ka hukum, uba la donburom na u paidbah baroh, u la hukum ban pynmih habar shiphang ïa kita ki briew.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Bad u la ong ha ki, “Ko phi ki rangbah Israel, to sumar ïa lade shaphang kine ki briew, aïu ba phin leh.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Namar mynshuwa kine ki sngi, la mih u Theudas, u da kren sarong ïa lade ba u long ma u uwei; ha u, la ïasoh lang kumba sawspah ki rangbah, ïa uba la pynïap noh; bad ïa kita baroh kat kiba la kohnguh ïa u, la pynsakma noh, bad kim shym long ei ei ruh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Hadien une, la mih u Judas uba na Galilaïa, ha kita ki sngi jong ka jingkheiñ ïa ka hima, bad u la ring noh ïa u paidbah hadien jong u; u ruh u la ïap noh, bad ïa kita baroh kat kiba la kohnguh ïa u, la pynsakma noh.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te mynta nga ong ha phi, To kynran noh na kine ki briew, to iehnoh noh ïa ki; naba lada kane ka jingsylla, lane kane ka jingleh, ka long na ki briew, kan dam noh;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> hynrei, lada ka long na U Blei, phim lah ban pyndam noh ïa ki; ïoh ba yn shem ïa phi pynban, ki nongïaleh ïa U Blei.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Bad ki la ïakohnguh ha u; te haba ki la lah khot ha ki ïa ki apostol, ki la sympat ïa ki, bad ki la adong ïa ki ban ïalap ha ka kyrteng jong U Jisu, bad ki la pyllait noh ïa ki.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Ki te, ki la ïamih noh na khmat kata ka dorbar, ki da ïakmen namar ba la ñiew ïa ki, kiba bit ban shah jahburom na ka bynta kata ka Kyrteng.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Ha la ka sngi ruh, ha ka templ, bad ha la ïing, kim wai noh ban hikai, bad ban ïathuhkhana ïa U Jisu ba u long U Khrist."
		},
		"6": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ha kita ki sngi, haba la man bun ki synran, la mih ka jingkhñium na ki Jiw Grik ïa ki Hebru, naba la kham leh lyndet ïa ki riewkynthei jong ki ha kaba sam ïa ka jingai isynei kaba ha la ka sngi.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki khat-ar ngut, haba ki la khot sha ki ïa u paidbah ki synran, ki la ong, “Kam long kaba bit ïa ngi ban iehnoh ïa ka jingïalap ïa ka ktien U Blei, bad ban shakri ïa ki miej.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Namar kata, ko para, phin ïakhmih hynñiew ngut ki rangbah na phi, kiba don ka nam babha, kiba dap da U Mynsiem bad da ka jingstad, ba ngin thung ïa ki halor kane ka kam.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, ngi ngin ïaineh ha ka jingduwai, bad ha ka jingïalap ïa ka ktien.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te kata ka jingong ka la pynsngewbha ïa uta u paidbah baroh; kumta, ki la ïajied ïa u Stephan, u briew uba dap da ka jingngeit bad da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, bad ïa u Philip, bad ïa u Prokhoros, bad ïa u Nikanor, bad ïa u Timon, bad ïa u Parmena, bad ïa u Nikolas uba la kylla niam, uba na Antiok;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ïa kiba ki la pynïeng ha khmat ki apostol, bad haba ki la duwai, ki la buh ïa la ki kti ha ki.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ka ktien U Blei ka la roi; bad la man bun shikatdei ki synran ha Jerusalem, bad u paidbah babun na ki lyngdoh, u la kohnguh ha kata ka jingngeit.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad u Stephan, uba dap da ka jingaiei bad ka bor, u la leh ki jingphylla bad ki dak khyllah bakhraw hapdeng u paidbah.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, la mih kiba na ka synagog, ba la khot “ka synagog ki Libertin”, bad na ki nong Kyrini, bad na ki nong Aleksandria, bad na kiba na Kilikia bad Asia, ki da ïasaid bad u Stephan,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> hynrei, kim ju lah ban ïaleh ïa ka jingstad bad ïa U Mynsiem, da kiba u la kren.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la pynïeng sakhi lamler, kiba la ong, “Ngi la ïohsngew ïa u ba u kren ki ktien beiñ blei ïa u Moses bad ïa U Blei.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki la ïapynkhih ïa uta u paidbah, bad ïa ki tymmen basan, bad ïa ki nongthoh, bad haba ki la lah ïawan buk ha u, ki la kem ïa u, bad ki la ïalam noh sha ka dorbar.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ki la pynïeng ïa ki sakhi lamler, kiba la ong, “Une u briew, um keiñ noh shuh ban kren ki ktien pyrshah ïa kane ka jaka bakhuid, bad ïa Ka Hukum:",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> namar ngi la ïohsngew ïa u ba u ong ba une U Jisu uba na Nasaret un sa pynjot ïa kane ka jaka, bad un sa pynkylla ïa ki niam ki rukom kiba u Moses u la aiti ha ngi.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te baroh kiba la ïashong ha kata ka dorbar, haba ki la khmih shaiñ ha u, ki la ïohi ïa ka khmat jong u kum ka khmat u angel."
		},
		"7": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda kumta, u rangbah lyngdoh u la kylli, “Hato kine kiei kiei ki long kumta shisha?”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u la ïathuh, “Ko para bad ko kpa, ha sngap, U Blei ka burom u la mihpaw ha u kpa jong ngi u Abraham, mynba u don ha Mesopotamia, mynba um pat leit shong ha Haran,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> bad U la ong ha u: ‘To khie leit noh na la ka ri, bad na la ki kur, bad to ale sha ka ri ïa kaba ngan kdew ha me.’",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda kumta, u la mih noh na ka ri Khaldia, bad u la leit shong ha Haran: nangta ruh, ynda la ïap noh u kpa jong u, U Blei u la pynkynriah ïa u sha kane ka ri, ha kaba phi mynta phi shong.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te um shym la ai ha u ka bynta ha ka, em, wat kat shi sien ïuh kjat; toi U la kular ban ai kynti ïa ka ha u, bad ha u symbai jong u hadien jong u, mynba um pat don khun.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te U Blei u la kren kumne: ‘U symbai jong u un leit shong ha ka ri nongwei; bad kin ïa-pynlong mraw ïa ki, bad kin ïa-pynshitom ïa ki, sawspah snem.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ïa kata ka jaid bynriew ha kaba kin shong mraw, ngan bishar ma nga,’ ong U Blei, ‘bad hadien kata kin ïoh wan noh, bad kin shakri ïa nga ha kane ka jaka.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te U la ai ha u, ïa ka jutang ka jingotsher. Kumta, u Abraham u la pynkha ïa u Isaak, bad u la otsher ïa u ha ka baphra sngi; u Isaak ruh u la pynkha ïa u Jakob, u Jakob de ïa ki khat-ar ngut ki kthaw tymmen.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Te kita ki kthaw tymmen, ba ki da ïasngewpihuiñ ïa u Joseph, ki la die noh ïa u sha Ijipt; hynrei, U Blei u la don ryngkat bad u,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad U la pyllait ïa u na ki jingjynjar jong u baroh, bad U la ai ha u, ka jingpynieit bad ka jingstad ha khmat u Pharaoh u syiem ka Ijipt, bad u la thung nongsynshar ïa u halor ka Ijipt, bad halor ka ïing jong u baroh.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te la jia ka 'nemsniew ha Ijipt bad ha Kanaan baroh, bad ka jynjar bakhraw; ki kpa jong ngi te kim shym la shem jingbam shuh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, u Jakob, haba u la ïohsngew ba don Kew ha Ijipt, u la phah shi sien phah ïa ki kpa jong ngi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad ha ka ba-ar sien phah, la pynithuh ïa u Joseph ha ki para jong u, bad ïa ka jaid u Joseph la pyntip ha u Pharaoh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Joseph ruh u la phah khot ha u ïa la u kpa, u Jakob, bad ïa la ki kur baroh, hynñiewphew san ki mynsiem.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Kumta, u Jakob u la leit hiar sha Ijipt. Haba u la ïap noh ma u bad ki kpa jong ngi ruh,",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> la leit bah ïa ki te, sha Shekhem, bad la buh ha u maw jingtep, ïa uba u Abraham u la thied da ka dor ka rupa na ki khun u Hammor ha Shekhem.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Hynrei, katba ka Ïa jong kata ka jingkular, ïa kaba U Blei u la kular ha u Abraham, ka la nang jan, kita ki briew ki la roi bad ki la man bun ha Ijipt,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> tad ynda la mih uwei pat u syiem halor ka ri Ijipt, u bym ju ithuh ïa u Joseph.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Une, u la leh shukor ïa ka jaid jong ngi, bad u la pynshitom ïa ki kpa jong ngi, ba kin bred noh ïa ki khunlung jong ki, khnang ba kin ym im.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ha kata ka por, la kha ïa u Moses, bad u la long uba bhabriew shikatdei eh. Bad la ri ïa u, lai bnai, ha ka ïing u kpa jong u;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> te mynba la bred noh ïa u, ka khun u Pharaoh ka la shim noh ïa u, bad ka la ri ïa u ba un ïoh long u khun jong ka hi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te la hikai ïa u Moses ha ka jingstad ki Ijipt baroh; bad u la long uba don bor ha ki ktien bad ha ki kam jong u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> “Hynrei, mynba u la dap sawphew snem ka rta, ka la jia ha ka dohnud jong u ban leit khmih ïa ki para jong u, ki khun Israel.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba u la ïohi ïa uwei ba u shah bymdei, u la da ïa u, bad u la pynhiar kput na ka bynta uta uba la shah lehbeiñ, u da shoh ïa uta u nong Ijipt;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> naba u la mut ba ki para jong u, ki la sngewthuh kumno ba U Blei un sa ai ha ki, ïa ka jingïohlait da ka kti jong u, hynrei ki, kim shym la sngewthuh.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te ha ka sngi kaba bud, u la paw ha ki haba ki dang ïashoh, bad u la mut ban pynïasuk pat ïa ki, u da ong, ‘Ko rangbah, phi, phi ïalong shipara; balei ba phi ïaleh bymdei paralok hi?’",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, uta uba la leh bymdei ïa la u paramarjan, u la khynñiat noh ïa u, u da ong, ‘Uei ba la pynlong ïa me u nongsynshar bad u nongbishar halor jong ngi?",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Me mut ban pynïap noh ïa nga, kumba me la pynïap ïa uto u nong Ijipt mynhynnin?’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te namar kane ka jingong, u Moses u la phet noh; bad u la long u nongwanwir wanhap ha ka ri Midian, ha kaba u la pynkha ar ngut ki khun shynrang.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> “Te ynda la dap sawphew snem, u angel u la mihpaw ha u ha ka ri khlaw u lum Sinai, ha ka thylliej ding ha ka 'law lynnong.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> U Moses te haba u la ïohi ïa ka, u la sngewphylla ïa kata ka jingïohi; te katba u la nang leit hajan ban khmih, ka ktien U Trai ka la mih,",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> ‘Nga long U Blei ki kpa jong me, U Blei u Abraham, bad u Isaak, bad u Jakob.’ U Moses te u la khynñiuh, bad um nud ban khmih.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u, ‘To loit noh ïa ki juti na ki kjat jong me, naba ka jaka ha kaba me ïeng, ka long ka khyndew ka bakhuid.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Shisha nga la ïohi ïa ka jingshahshitom ki briew jong nga kiba ha Ijipt, bad nga la ïohsngew ïa ka jingud jong ki, bad nga la wan hiar ban pyllait noh ïa ki. Mynta, to ale, ngan phah ïa me sha Ijipt.’",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Ïa une u Moses, ïa uba ki la kyntait noh, ki da ong, ‘Uei ba la pynlong ïa me u nongsynshar bad u nongbishar?’ ïa u keiñ, U Blei u la phah ban long u nongsynshar bad u nongpyllait, da ka kti uta u angel uba la mihpaw ha u ha kata ka 'law lynnong.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Une u briew, u la ïalam noh ïa ki, ynda u la leh ki jingphylla bad ki dak khyllah ha Ijipt, bad ha ka Duriaw Basaw, bad ha ka ri khlaw ruh sawphew snem.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Une, u long uta u Moses, uba la ong ha ki khun Israel, ‘U Blei un pynmih ïa u nongïathuhlypa ha phi napdeng ki para jong phi, uba kum ma nga.’",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Une, u long uta uba la ju don ha kata ka balang ha ka ri khlaw, lem bad uta u angel uba la kren ha u ha u lum Sinai, bad lem bad ki kpa jong ngi; uba la pdiang ïa ki orakl ki ba-im, ïa ka ban aiti pateng ha ngi.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Ïa uba kita ki kpa jong ngi kim shym la ïamon ban kohnguh; hynrei, ki la khynñiat noh ïa u na ki, bad ki la phai dien noh ruh ha ki dohnud jong ki sha ka ri Ijipt,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> ki da ong ha u Aaron, ‘To thaw ki blei ïa ngi, ki ban leit ha shuwa jong ngi; namar ïa u Moses, une uba la ïalam noh ïa ngi na ka ri Ijipt, ngim tip kaei kaba la jia ha u.’",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te ki la ïathaw dur khun masi ha kita ki sngi, bad ki la ïawallam ka jingkñia ha uta u bleithaw, bad ki la ïalehkmen de ha ki jingleh ki kti jong ki hi.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Hynrei, U Blei u la phai dien noh, bad U la iehnoh noh ïa ki ban mane ïa u paid ka bneng, kumba la thoh ha ka kitab jong ki nongïathuhlypa, “ ‘Shisha phi la ïakñia ki mrad kñia bad ki jingkñia ha nga sawphew snem ha kata ka ri khlaw, A phi ka ïing Israel?",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Bad phi la ïabah ïa ita i ïingmane jong u Molok, bad ïa u khlur jong u blei Rephan, ki dur ïa kiba phi la thaw ban mane ïa ki. Te ngan pynwir noh ïa phi sha lyndet ka Babilon.’",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> “Ki kpa jong ngi ki la don kata Ka Tabernakl ka jingphla, ha ka ri khlaw, kumba la hukum uta uba la kren ha u Moses, ba un thaw ïa ka katba kum kata ka dur ïa kaba u la lah ïohi.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Ïa kata ruh, ki kpa jong ngi pat de ki la wallam shapoh lem bad u Joshua, mynba ki la leit rung sha kata ka bynta jong kita ki jaid bynriew, ïa kiba U Blei u la beh noh na khmat ki kpa jong ngi, haduh ki sngi jong u Dabid;",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> uba la shem ka jingaiei ha khmat U Blei, bad u la pan ban shem ka jaka shongneh ïa U Blei u Jakob.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Hynrei, u Solomon u la tei ka ïing ïa U.",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Te uta U Bahakhlieh Tam Eh um ju shong keiñ ha ki ïing ba la thaw da ki kti; kumba ong u nongïathuhlypa,",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> “ ‘Ka bneng ka long ka khet jong nga, bad ka khyndew, ka jingïuh ki kjat jong nga; ka ïing kaba kumno te phin tei ïa nga?’ ong U Trai; ‘lane kaba kumno ka jaka shongthait jong nga?",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Hato ka kti jong nga kam shym la thaw ïa kine kiei kiei baroh?’",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> “Phi kiba eh ryndang, bad kiba khlem otsher ha ka dohnud bad ha ki shkor, khlem da pud phi ïaleh pyrshah ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid! kumba ki kpa jong phi ki la leh, kumta phi ruh phi leh!",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Ïano na ki nongïathuhlypa ba ki kpa jong phi kim shym la pynshitombeiñ? bad ki la ïa-pynïap noh ïa kita kiba la pyni lypa shaphang ka jingwan jong uta U Bahok, ïa uba phi mynta phi la long ki nongdie bad ki nongpynïap;",
			"53": "<sup>53</sup> ma phi kiba la pdiang ïa ka hukum kumba la buh ïa ka da ki angel, bad ki bym shym la sumar ïa ka.”",
			"54": "<sup>54</sup> Te haba ki la ïohsngew ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, ki la otshla ha ki dohnud, bad ki la kyr-iat bniat ïa u.",
			"55": "<sup>55</sup> Hynrei, ba u long uba dap da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, haba u la khmied shaiñ sha bneng, u la ïohi ïa ka burom U Blei, bad ïa U Jisu ba U ïeng sha ka kti kamon U Blei,",
			"56": "<sup>56</sup> bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, nga ïohi ïa ki bneng ba la plie, bad ïa U Khun u briew ba U da ïeng sha ka kti kamon U Blei.”",
			"57": "<sup>57</sup> Hynrei, ki la ïapyrta da ka ktien bajam, bad ki la set ïa la ki shkor, bad ki la ïaphet kyrthep da kawei ka jingmut ha u,",
			"58": "<sup>58</sup> bad ki la ïashop noh ïa u shabar kata ka shnong, bad ki la ïalynthem maw ïa u: kita ki nongphla te, ki la buh noh ïa la ki jaiñ ha ki kjat uwei u samla, uba kyrteng “u Saul”.",
			"59": "<sup>59</sup> Te ki la ïalynthem maw ïa u Stephan, haba u dang duwai, u da ong, “A Trai Jisu, to pdiang noh ïa ka mynsiem jong nga!”",
			"60": "<sup>60</sup> Te u la dem la ki khohsiew, bad u la pyrta da ka ktien bajam, “A Trai, wat thew ha ki ïa kane ka pop.” Te ynda u la lah ong ïa kane, u la ïohthiah noh."
		},
		"8": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Saul u la ïamynjur lem ïa ka jingpynïap ïa u. Ha kata ka sngi te, la jia ka jingpynshitom beiñ bakhraw ïa ka balang kaba ha Jerusalem, te la pynsakma ïa ki baroh, kylleng ki ri Judia bad Samaria, lait sa tang ki apostol.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ki rangbah bariewblei ki la ïatep ïa u Stephan, bad ki la ïa-pynlong ka jingïambriew kaba khraw na ka bynta jong u.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, u Saul u la pynjot ïa ka balang, u da leit rung man la ka ïing, bad haba u la ring noh ïa ki briew shynrang bad kynthei, u la ai noh ïa ki sha ka ïing byndi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Namar kata, kita ïa kiba la pynsakma, ki la leit kylleng kylleng, ki da ïalap ïa kata ka ktien.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Bad u Philip u la leit hiar sha ka shnong Samaria, bad u la ïalap ïa U Khrist ha ki.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki paidbah ki la shahshkor da kawei ka jingmut, ïa kita kiei kiei ruh kiba la kren da u Philip, haba ki la ïohsngew bad ki la ïohi ïa kita ki dak khyllah kiba u la leh.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Namar ki mynsiem bymkhuid haba ki la pyrta da ka ktien bajam, ki la mih noh na shibun ha kiba ki la ju shong; shibun kiba la pang ïapshiliang, bad ki ba-dkoh, la pynkhiah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te la don ka jingkmen bakhraw ha kata ka shnong.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, la don uwei u briew, uba kyrteng “u Simon”, uba ju leh byrtong mynshuwa ha kata ka shnong, bad u la pynmaïa ïa ki briew jong ka Samaria; u da kren sarong ïa lade, ba u long uwei u bakhraw.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ha u, baroh ki la ïa-pynleit jingmut, naduh u barit tam haduh u bakhraw tam, ki da ong, “Une u briew u long kata ka bor U Blei ïa kaba la khot ‘Bakhraw’.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ha u te, ki la ïa-pynshahshkor, namar la mynslem bah, da ki jingleh byrtong u la pynmaïa ïa ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Hynrei, ynda ki la ngeit ïa u Philip, ba u da ïalap ïa ka khubor babha shaphang ka hima U Blei bad ka kyrteng U Jisu Khrist, la pynbaptis ïa ki, bad shynrang bad kynthei.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Simon hi ruh u la ngeit, bad haba la pynbaptis ïa u, u la sah lem bad u Philip, bad u la sngewlyngngoh haba u la khmih ïa ki dak khyllah, bad ki kambah bakhraw ïa kiba la leh.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba ki apostol kiba ha Jerusalem ki la ïohsngew ba ka Samaria ka la lah pdiang ïa ka ktien U Blei, ki la phah ha ki ïa u Petros bad ïa u Ïoannis;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> kiba, ynda ki la leit hiar, ki la ïaduwai na ka bynta jong ki, ba kin ïoh pdiang ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> (Namar um pat shym la hap hano hano ruh na ki; hynrei, tang ba la pynbaptis ïa ki ha ka kyrteng U Trai Jisu.)",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, ki la ïabuh la ki kti ha ki, bad ki la pdiang ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ynda u Simon u la ïohi ba da kaba buh ki kti ki apostol, la ai ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid, u la tyrwa sbai ha ki,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> u da ong, “To ai ha nga ruh ïa kane ka bor, ba hano hano ruh ba ngan buh ïa la ki kti, un ïoh pdiang ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid.”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, u Petros u la ong ha u, “Ka rupa jong me to kan jot noh lem bad me, naba me la mut ban ïoh ïa ka jingai jong U Blei da u sbai!",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Mem don ka bynta, lymne ka pakai ha kane ka kam; namar ka dohnud jong me kam long kaba beit ha khmat U Blei.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Namar kata, to kylla-ka-bamut noh na kane ka bymman jong me, bad to duwai ha U Blei, lehse yn dang map ïa me ïa kane ka buit ka dohnud jong me.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar nga ïohi ba me long u ksang ka jingkthang, bad ka jingkhum ka jingbymman.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> U Simon te u la ïathuh bad u la ong, “To duwai ma phi na ka bynta jong nga ha U Trai, ba kawei ruh na kita ïa kiba phi la kren, kan ym jia ha nga!”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ki te namar kata, ynda ki la ïaphla bad ïalap ïa ka ktien U Trai, ki la ïaleit phai pat sha Jerusalem, bad ki la ïalap ïa ka gospel ha bun ki shnong jong ki Samaria.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei u angel U Trai u la kren ha u Philip, u da ong, “To ïeng joit, khie leit ruh shaphang shathie, sha kata ka lynti kaba leit hiar na Jerusalem sha Gasa” (kata ka long ka ri khlaw).",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Kumta, u la ïeng bad u la leit; te ha khmih, u briew na Ithiopia, u Ïunukh uba khraw bor hapoh ka Kandasi, ka syiem ki nong Ithiopia, uba la long halor ka jingkynshew jong ka baroh, uba la wan ban mane sha Jerusalem;",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> te u dang leit phai, u da shong ha ka kali jong u, bad u dang pule ïa u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U Mynsiem te, u la ong ha u Philip, “Khie leit hajan, to snoh ruh ha kane ka kali.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te u Philip u la phet sha u, bad u la ïohsngew ba u pule ïa u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa, bad u la ong, “Me shemphang ïa kata kaba me pule?”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> U la ïathuh te, “Kumno nga lah, lymda don uno uno u ban ïalam ïa nga?” Bad u la kyrpad ïa u Philip ban wan kiew bad shong ryngkat bad u.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te ka jaka jong kata Ka Jingthoh kaba u la pule, ka la long kane: “Kum ka langbrot la ïalam noh ïa u sha ka jingpynïap, bad kum i khun langbrot ba sngap jar ha khmat u nongot shñiuh jong i, kumta um ang la ka shyntur.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ha ka jinglong rit jong u la shim noh ïa ka jingbishar jong u; hynrei, uei u ban ïathuh ïa ka jingkha pateng jong u? naba la shim noh ïa ka jingim jong u na ka khyndew.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te uta u Ïunukh u la ïathuh ha u Philip, bad u la ong, “Nga kyrpad ïa me, shaphang jongno u nongïathuhlypa u kren ïa kane? shaphang ïa lade hi, ne shaphang uwei pat?”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ynda kumta, u Philip u la ang la ka shyntur, bad da kaba sdang na kane ka jingthoh, u la ïalap ha u ïa U Jisu.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te katba ki nang ïaleit ha kata ka lynti, ki la ïapoi ha kawei ka um; te uta u Ïunukh u la ong, “Ha khmih ka um; kaei ba pynpep ban pynbaptis ïa nga?”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te u Philip u la ong, “Lada me ngeit na la ka dohnud baroh, me lah.” U la ïathuh bad u la ong, “Nga ngeit ba U Jisu Khrist u long U Khun U Blei.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te u la hukum ban pynsangeh ïa ka kali: bad ki la ïaleit hiar baroh ar ngut sha kata ka um, u Philip bad uta u Ïunukh de, bad u la pynbaptis ïa u.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te haba ki la ïawan kiew noh na kata ka um, U Mynsiem U Trai u la rah noh ïa u Philip, bad uta u Ïunukh um shym la ïohi shuh ïa u, naba u la nang leit ha ka lynti jong u da kaba kmen.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Hynrei, ïa u Philip la shem ha Asotos; te katba u dang ïaid lyngba, u la ïalap ïa ka gospel ha ki shnong baroh, haduh ba u la poi sha Kaisaria."
		},
		"9": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Saul, haba u dang pyrsad ki jingbyrngem bad ka jingpynïap ïa ki synran jong U Trai, u la leit ha u rangbah lyngdoh,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad u la pan na u ki shithi sha Damaskos sha ki synagog, ba lada un shem ïa kino kino ruh kiba na kane “ka Lynti”, la ki shynrang ne ki kynthei, un ïoh leit lam ïa ki ba la khum sha Jerusalem.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te katba u dang leit, ka la jia ba u la poi hajan Damaskos, bad kyndit kyndit la tyngshaiñ lep sawdong ïa u ka jingshai na bneng:",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> te u la kyllon kram ha khyndew, bad u la ïohsngew ïa ka ktien kaba ong ha u, “A Saul, Saul, balei me pynshitombeiñ ïa nga?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U te u la ong, “Me long uei, A Trai?” Te U la ong, “Nga long U Jisu, ïa uba me pynshitombeiñ: ka long kaba eh ïa me ban kynjat pyrshah ïa ki dieng tyndung.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Haba u la khynñiuh bad la sngewmaïan, u la ong, “A Trai, aïu me mon ïa nga ban leh?” Ynda kumta U Trai u la ong ha u, “To ïeng, khie leit ruh shapoh kata ka shnong, te yn sa ïathuh ha me aïu ba ka dei ïa me ban leh.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ki rangbah te kiba la leit jingleit ryngkat bad u, ki la ïaïeng khlem nang kren, ki da ïohsngew ïa ka jingsawa, hynrei, kim da ïohi ïano ïano ruh.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Saul u la ïeng na ka khyndew, bad ynda u la khyllie la ki khmat, um ïohi ei ei shuh; bad ki la btin ïa u na ka kti, ki la ïalam ruh ïa u shapoh Damaskos.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te u la long lai sngi khlem imat, bad um shym la bam lymne dih.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te la don uwei u synran ha Damaskos, uba kyrteng “u Ananias”; bad U Trai u la ong ha u ha ka jingithuhpaw, “Ko Ananias.” U ruh u la ong, “Ha khmih, nga hangne, ko Trai.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te U Trai u la ong ha u, “To ïeng, khie leit ruh sha kata ka lynti shnong ïa kaba khot ‘Ba-beit’, to wad ruh ha ka ïing u Judas, ïa u briew uba kyrteng ‘u Saul’, u nong Tarsos; naba, ha khmih, u duwai,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> bad u la ïohi ïa u briew uba kyrteng ‘u Ananias’ ba u wan hapoh, bad ba u buh ïa la ki kti ha u, ba un ïoh peit pat.”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, u Ananias u la ïathuh, “A Trai, nga la ïohsngew na kiba bun shaphang une u briew, kaba katno ka basniew ba u la leh ïa ki riewkhuid jong me ha Jerusalem!",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hangne ruh putet u la ïoh ka bor na ki rangbah lyngdoh, ban khum ïa baroh kiba khot kyrpad ha ka kyrteng jong me!”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, U Trai u la ong ha u, “To khie leit noh; naba uta u long u atiar ba la jied ha nga, ïa ka ban kit ïa ka kyrteng jong nga ha khmat ki Jentil, bad ki syiem, bad ki khun Israel de;",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> namar ngan pyni ha u kaba katno bun kiei kiei ba u dei ban shah na ka bynta ka kyrteng jong nga.”",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kumta u Ananias u la leit noh, bad u la rung hapoh kata ka ïing; te haba u la buh ïa la ki kti ha u, u la ong, “Ko Saul, u para jong nga, uta U Trai, U Jisu keiñ, uba la mihpaw ha me ha kata ka lynti ha kaba me la wan, U la phah ïa nga ba men ïoh peit pat, bad ba yn pyndap ïa me da U Mynsiem Bakhuid.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh la hap noh na ki khmat jong u kum ki sarew, bad u la ïoh peit pat; te u la ïeng joit, bad la pynbaptis ïa u.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ynda u la bam jingbam, la pynshait ïa u. Te u la don katto katne ki sngi ryngkat bad ki synran kiba ha Damaskos.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te kumne kumne ruh u la ïalap ïa U Khrist ha ki synagog, ba u long U Khun U Blei.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Baroh te kiba la ïohsngew ïa u, ki la sngewkyndit, bad ki la ïa-ong, “Une um dei uta uba la pynjot ha Jerusalem ïa kita kiba la ju khot kyrpad ha kane ka Kyrteng? Bad u la wan hangne ruh ïa kane khnang, ba un ïoh ïalam noh ïa ki ba la khum ha khmat ki rangbah lyngdoh.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, u Saul u la nang khraw bor, bad u la pynduh nia ïa kita ki Jiw kiba shong ha Damaskos, u da pyni biang biang ba une u long U Khrist.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba la dap bun sngi, ki Jiw ki la ïasylla lang ban pynïap noh ïa u;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> hynrei, u Saul u la ïoh tip ïa ka jingïashet jong ki. Te ki la ïa-ap ïa ki khyrdop ruh mynsngi bad mynmiet, ba kin ïoh pynïap noh ïa u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, ki synran jong u ki la shim ïa u mynmiet, bad ki la ïa-pynhiar noh lyngba ka kynroh, ki da ïa-pynhiar ïa u ha ka tukri.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te haba u la poi ha Jerusalem, u la pyrshang ban pynïasoh ïa lade bad ki synran; te baroh ki la sheptieng ïa u, ba kim ngeit satia ba u long u synran.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, u Barnabas u la shim ïa u, bad u la wallam ïa u ha ki apostol, bad u la ïathuh ha ki kumno ba u la lah ïohi ïa U Trai ha kata ka lynti, bad ba U la lah kren bad u, bad kumno ha Damaskos ba u la lah ïalap shlur ha ka kyrteng U Jisu.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad u la long ryngkat bad ki, u da ïarung hapoh bad u da ïamih habar ruh ha Jerusalem,",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> u da ïalap shlur ha ka kyrteng U Trai, u la ïakren ruh bad u la ïasaid bad kita ki Jiw Grik; hynrei, ki la wad lad ban pynïap noh ïa u.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te haba ki parabangeit ki la tip ïa kata, ki la ïalam noh arsut ïa u sha Kaisaria, bad ki la phah noh ïa u sha Tarsos.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Kumta, ka balang ha Judia bad Galilaïa bad Samaria baroh ka la suk, ba la tei ïa ka; bad da kaba ïaid ha ka jingsheptieng ïa U Trai, bad ha ka jingpyntngen U Mynsiem Bakhuid, ka la roi kyrhai.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ka la jia ruh, katba u Petros u la leit lyngba ïa ki phang baroh, ba u la wan hiar ruh ha kita ki riewkhuid kiba shong ha Lydda.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u la shem hangta ïa uwei u briew, uba kyrteng “u Inias”, uba la thiah ha ka jingthiah la phra snem, naba u la pang ïapshiliang.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te u Petros u la ong ha u, “Ko Inias, U Jisu Khrist u pynkhiah ïa me; to ïeng joit, bad shna ïa la ka jingthiah.” Te kumne kumne ruh u la ïeng joit.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Baroh te kiba shong ha Lydda bad ha Sharon ki la ïohi ïa u, bad ki la phai sha U Trai.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te la don ha Joppa kawei ka synran, kaba kyrteng “ka Tabitha”, kaba haba la batai, la khot “ka Dorkas”; kane ka kynthei, ka la dap da ki jingleh babha bad ki jingai isynei kiba ka la ju leh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te ka la jia ha kita ki sngi, ba ka la pang, bad ka la ïap noh; bad ynda ki la ïa-pynsum ïa ka, ki la ïabuh ïa ka ha kawei ka kamra kaba haneng.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te namar ba ka Lydda ka long hajan Joppa, kita ki synran haba ki la ïohsngew ba u Petros u don hangta, ki la phah ar ngut ki briew sha u, ki da kyrpad ïa u, “Wat pyntud ban wan haduh ha ngi.”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te u Petros u la ïeng joit, bad u la leit lem bad ki. Bad ynda u la poi, ki la ïalam ïa u sha kata ka kamra kaba haneng; ki riewkynthei baroh te ki la ïaïeng hajan jong u, ki da ïaïam, bad ki da ïa-pyni ïa ki sopti, bad ïa ki jaiñkup, kiba ka Dorkas ka la thaw, mynba ka dang don bad ki.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Hynrei, u Petros, u la pynmih noh shabar ïa ki baroh, bad u la dem khohsiew, bad u la duwai; bad haba u la phai sha kata ka met, u la ong, “Ko Tabitha, to ïeng.” Te ka la khyllie ïa la ki khmat; bad haba ka la ïohi ïa u Petros, ka la khie shong.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te u la ai la ka kti ha ka, bad u la pynïeng ïa ka; te ynda u la khot ïa kita ki riewkhuid bad ïa ki riewkynthei, u la aiti ïa ka, kaba la im pat.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te la bna ïa kata ha Joppa baroh kawei, bad shibun ki la ngeit ha U Trai.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ka la jia ruh, ba u la ïaishong bun sngi ha Joppa bad uwei u Simon, u nongshna snieh."
		},
		"10": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te la don ha Kaisaria uwei u briew uba kyrteng “u Kornilios”, u rangbah shispah na ka kynhun shipai ba la khot “Ka Italia”,",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> u briew bariewblei, bad uba sheptieng ïa U Blei, lem bad ka ïing jong u baroh, uba la ai shibun ki jingai isynei ïa ki briew, bad uba duwai de ha U Blei khlem da pud.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> U la ïohi shynna ha ka jingithuhpaw, hamar kaba khyndai baje mynsngi, ïa u angel U Blei ba u wan hapoh ha u, bad ba u ong ha u, “Ko Kornilios.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> U te, haba u la khmih shaiñ ha u, bad ba u dang kyndit, u la ong, “Kumno, Kynrad?” Te u la ïathuh ha u, “Ki jingduwai jong me bad ki jingai isynei jong me, ki la ïakiew soit kum ka jingkynmaw ha khmat U Blei.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Mynta te to phah briew sha Joppa, bad khot ïa u Simon, ïa uba sin ‘Petros’;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> u shong basa bad uwei u Simon, u nongshna snieh, uba ka ïing jong u ka don harud duriaw.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ynda uta u angel uba la kren ha u, u la leit noh, u la khot ar ngut na ki shakri ïing jong u, bad ïa u shipai bariewblei na kita kiba ju ïa-ap ïa u;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> te haba u la bthah ha ki, ïa kiei kiei baroh, u la phah noh ïa ki sha Joppa.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te kum lashai, katba kita ki dang ha lynti, bad ba ki la poi hajan kata ka shnong, u Petros u la leit kiew shalor ïing ban duwai, hamar kaba hynriew baje.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te u la sngewthngan, bad u la kwah ban ïoh jingbam: hynrei, katba ki dang pynkhreh, la ngat ka jinglong rngai ha u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Bad u ïohi ïa ka bneng ba la plie, bad uwei u khiew ba u da hiar, kum ka jingsiang bakhraw ba la pynhiar na ki sawdong ha khyndew,",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> ha kaba la don ki kynja mrad ba saw kjat baroh, bad ki kynja bapar jong ka khyndew, bad ki sim jong ka bneng de.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te la wan ka ktien ha u, “To ïeng, ko Petros, to pynïap to bam ruh.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, u Petros u la ong, “Ym kumta, A Trai; namar ngam ju bam mynno mynno ruh kaei kaei kaba sang lane ka bymkhuid.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ka ktien ka la wan pat ha u ka ba-ar sien, “Ïa kaba U Blei u la pynkhuid, wat ñiew sang ma me.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad la leh ïa kane lai sien; te la pdiang soit pat ïa uta u khiew sha bneng.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te katba u Petros u dang sngewlyngngoh shibun ha lade, kata ka jingithuhpaw kaba u la ïohi ka lah ban mut aïu, ha khmih ruh, kita ki briew ïa kiba la phah da u Kornilios, ynda ki la lah wad ïa ka ïing u Simon, ki la ïaïeng ha khmat ka khyrdop,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad ki la khot, bad ki la ïakylli, la u Simon ïa uba sin “Petros”, u shong basa hangta ne em.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te katba u Petros u dang pyrkhat shaphang kata ka jingithuhpaw, U Mynsiem u la ïathuh ha u, “Ha khmih, lai ngut ki briew ki ïawad ïa me.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei to ïeng, to leit hiar noh, bad to leit ryngkat bad ki khlem da sngew-artatien, namar la phah ma nga ïa ki.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Kumta, u Petros u la leit hiar sha kita ki briew, bad u la ong, “Ha khmih, nga long uta ïa uba phi ïawad. Na ka daw aïu phi la wan?”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ki la ïathuh, “U Kornilios, u rangbah shispah, u briew u bahok, bad uba sheptieng ïa U Blei, bad uba la ïoh ka jingïaroh na ka jaid Jiw baroh, la sneng ïa u da u angel bakhuid ban phah khot ïa me shapoh ka ïing jong u, bad ban ïohsngew ïa ki ktien na me.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, u la khot ïa ki shapoh, bad u la khot basa ïa ki. Te ha kaba lashai u la ïeng bad u la leit noh lem bad ki, bad don ruh ki parabangeit kiba na Joppa kiba la ïaleit ryngkat bad u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te kum lashai ki la ïawan poi shapoh Kaisaria. U Kornilios te u la lah khot lang ïa ki kur jong u, bad ïa ki lok ba-ieit jong u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ka la jia katba u Petros u dang rung, ba u Kornilios u la leit tan ïa u, bad u la dem khrup ha ki kjat jong u, bad u la mane ïa u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, u Petros u la pynïeng pat ïa u, u da ong, “To ïeng joit, nga hi ruh nga long u briew.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te katba u la nang ïakren bad u, u la rung, bad u la shem shibun kiba la ïawan lang.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> U la ong te ha ki, “Phi hi phi tip kumno ba ka long kaba sang ïa u briew uba long u Jiw ban ïalok lane ban ïajan bad uba na kawei pat ka jaid bynriew; pynban, U Blei u la pyni ha nga ba ngan ym ñiew uba sang lane u bymkhuid ïa uno uno u briew;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> namar kata te, haba la phah khot ïa nga, nga la wan khlem da ïasaid. Namar kata, nga kylli: ïa ka ban lei phi la phah khot ïa nga?”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U Kornilios te u la ong, “Mynta la saw sngi haduh kane ka por, haba nga dang duwai ïa ka jingduwai kaba khyndai baje ha ka ïing jong nga, ha khmih, uwei u briew u la ïeng ha khmat jong nga ha ka jaiñkup baphyrnai,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> bad u ong, ‘Ko Kornilios, la shahshkor ïa ka jingduwai jong me, bad ïa ki jingai isynei jong me la buh jingkynmaw ha khmat U Blei.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Namar kata, to phah sha Joppa, bad khot ha me ïa u Simon ïa uba la sin “Petros”, u shong basa ha ka ïing u Simon, u nongshna snieh, harud ka duriaw.’",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Namar kata, mar mar nga la phah ktien sha me, me ruh me la leh bha ba me la poi. Mynta, namar kata, ngi baroh ngi ïadon hangne ha khmat U Blei, khnang ïa ka ban ïohsngew ïa kiei kiei baroh, ïa kiba la hukum ha me da U Trai.”",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Ynda kumta, u Petros u la ang la ka shyntur, bad u la ong, “Shisha nga sngewthuh ba U Blei um long uba ñiew shiliang khmat,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> hynrei, ha kano kano ka jaid bynriew, jar uba sheptieng ïa U, bad uba ïai-leh ïa ka hok, u long keiñ uba la pdiang sngewbha da U.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Kata ka ktien ïa kaba U la phah ha ki khun Israel, da kaba ïalap ïa ka gospel ka jingsuk da U Jisu Khrist (long ma u, U Trai halor baroh),",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> ïa kata ka ktien, phi hi phi tip ïa kaba la pynbna ha Judia baroh, haba la sdang na Galilaïa hadien kata ka jingpynbaptis kaba la ïalap u Ïoannis;",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> shaphang U Jisu uba na Nasaret, kumno ba U Blei u la pynsleh ïa u da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, bad da ka bor, uba la ïaid kylleng u da leh babha, bad u da pynkhiah ïa kita baroh kiba la ban shitom da u Soitan; naba U Blei u long ryngkat bad u.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Bad ngi long ki sakhi ïa kiei kiei baroh kat kiba u la leh ha ka ri ki Jiw, bad ha Jerusalem; ïa uba ki la pynïap noh ruh, da kaba sdien ïa u ha u dieng.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Ïa une, U Blei u la pynmih pat ha ka balai sngi, bad u la shah ïa u ban long uba paw shynna,",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> ym ha u paidbah baroh, hynrei, ha ki sakhi ïa kiba la jied mynshuwa da U Blei, ha ngi keiñ, kiba la ïabam ïadih ryngkat bad u, ynda u la mihpat na ki baïap.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> U la hukum te ïa ngi ban ïalap ha u paidbah, bad ban phla ba une, u long uta uba la thung da U Blei ban long U Nongbishar ki ba-im bad ki baïap.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Ïa une, ki nongïathuhlypa baroh ki ïaphla, ba da ka kyrteng jong u, uno uno baroh uba ngeit ha u, un ïoh kaba map ki pop.”",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Katba u Petros u dang kren ïa kine ki ktien, U Mynsiem Bakhuid u la hap ha kita baroh kiba la ïohsngew ïa kata ka ktien.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Te kiba na ka jingotsher kiba la ngeit, kat kiba la ïawan lem bad u Petros, ki la sngewkyndit, namar ba ha ki Jentil ruh la theh noh ïa ka jingai U Mynsiem Bakhuid,",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> namar ki la ïohsngew ba ki ïakren da ki thylliej, bad ba ki ïapynkhraw ïa U Blei. Kumta u Petros u la ïathuh,",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> “Don mano mano uba lah ban adong ïa ka um, kat ban ym pynbaptis ïa kine kiba la ïoh pdiang ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid, kumjuh kum ngi?”",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Te u la hukum ba yn pynbaptis ïa ki ha ka kyrteng U Jisu Khrist. Ynda kumta, ki la ïakyrpad ïa u ban sah sa khyndiat sngi."
		},
		"11": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ki apostol bad ki parabangeit kiba la don ha Judia ki la ïohsngew ba ki Jentil ruh ki la lah pdiang ïa ka ktien U Blei.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad haba u Petros u la wan kiew sha Jerusalem, kita kiba na ka jingotsher ki la ïasaid bad u,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ki da ong, “Me la leit sha ki briew kiba khlem otsher, bad me la bam ryngkat bad ki.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, u Petros u la sdang, bad u la batai ha ki ter ter, u da ong,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Nga la don ha ka shnong Joppa ba nga dang duwai; te ha ka jinglong rngai nga la ïohi ïa ka jingithuhpaw, ïa uwei u khiew ba u hiar kum ka jingsiang bakhraw, ba la pynhiar na bneng da ki sawdong; bad ka la poi haduh ha nga;",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> sha kaba haba nga la khmih shaiñ, nga la pyrkhat bad nga la ïohi ïa ki mrad ba saw kjat jong ka khyndew, bad ïa ki mrad khlaw, bad ïa ki kynja bapar, bad ïa ki sim ka bneng de.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Bad nga la ïohsngew ruh ka ktien kaba ong ha nga, ‘To ïeng joit, ko Petros, to pynïap, to bam ruh.’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, nga la ong, ‘Ym kumta A Trai; namar kaei kaei ruh kaba sang lane ka bymkhuid kam ju rung mynno mynno ruh shapoh ka shyntur jong nga.’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ka ktien ka la kren ha nga sa shi wat pat na bneng, ‘Ïa kaba U Blei u la pynkhuid, wat ñiew sang ma me.’",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te la leh haduh lai sien ïa kane; ynda kumta, la ring noh pat ïa kita baroh sha bneng.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Ha khmih ruh, kumne kumne lai ngut ki briew ki la ïaïeng ha khmat kata ka ïing ha kaba ngi la don, ba la phah ïa ki na Kaisaria sha nga.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad U Mynsiem u la hukum ïa nga ban leit ryngkat bad ki, khlem da sngew-artatien; bad kine ki hynriew ngut ki parabangeit ruh ki la ïawan lem bad nga, bad ngi la ïaleit ruh shapoh ka ïing uta u briew.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> U ruh u la ïathuh ha ngi kumno ba u la ïohi ïa u angel ba u da ïeng ha ka ïing jong u, bad ba u da ong, ‘To phah sha Joppa, bad khot ïa u Simon, ïa uba la sin “Petros”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> u ban kren ki ktien ha me, da kiba yn pynim ïa me, ma me bad ka ïing jong me baroh ruh.’",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te katba nga la sdang ban kren, U Mynsiem Bakhuid u la hap ha ki, kumjuh kumba ha ngi hi ha kaba mynnyngkong:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> te nga la kynmaw ïa kata ka jingong U Trai, kumno ba u la ong, ‘U Ïoannis shisha u la pynbaptis da ka um, hynrei, yn pynbaptis ïa phi da U Mynsiem Bakhuid.’",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Lada U Blei te u la ai ha ki ïa kajuh ka jingai, kum kaba u la ai ha ngi ruh, mynba ngi la ngeit ha U Jisu Khrist uba U Trai, nga long uei ba ngan lah ban ïaleh pyrshah ïa U Blei?”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te haba ki la ïohsngew ïa kine kiei kiei, ki la ïasngap jar, bad ki la ïa-pyndonburom ïa U Blei, ki da ong, “Kumta te ha ki Jentil ruh U Blei u la ai ïa ka jingkylla-ka-bamut sha ka jingim.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Kita te ïa kiba la pynsakma kylleng namar kata ka jingjynjar kaba la mih hadien u Stephan, ki la leit poi haduh Phoiniki, bad Kypros, bad Antiok de, ki da ïalap ïa kata ka ktien hano hano ruh em, hynrei, tang ha ki Jiw hi.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, la don na ki, ki briew kiba na Kypros, bad na Kyrini, kiba haba ki la poi sha Antiok, ki la kren ha ki Grik ruh, ki da ïalap ïa U Jisu uba U Trai.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad ka kti U Trai ka la long lem bad ki, bad bun byllien kiba la ngeit ki la wan phai sha U Trai.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ka jingbna shaphang jong ki, ka la poi sha ki shkor jong ka balang kaba ha Jerusalem, bad ki la ïaphah ïa u Barnabas ban leit haduh Antiok;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> uba haba u la poi, bad ba u la ïohi ïa ka jingaiei ka jong U Blei, u la sngewkmen, bad u la kyntu ïa ki baroh, ba da ka jingthmu skhem ka dohnud kin snoh ha U Trai:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> naba u la long u briew u babha, bad uba dap da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, bad da ka jingngeit. Te shibun u paidbah la pynïasoh ha U Trai.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u la leit noh sha Tarsos ban wad ïa u Saul, bad ynda u la shem ïa u, u la ïalam ïa u sha Antiok.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Ka la jia ruh ba baroh shi snem ki la ïaseng lem bad kata ka balang, bad ki la ïahikai ïa shibun u paidbah. Bad la khot “Khristan” ïa ki synran nyngkong eh ha Antiok.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ha kine ki sngi, ki la wan hiar ki nongïathuhlypa na Jerusalem sha Antiok.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te uwei na ki, uba kyrteng “u Agabos” u la ïeng joit, bad u la ïathuhlypa da U Mynsiem, ba ka 'nemsniew bakhraw kan sa long ha ka pyrthei baroh, kaba la jia ruh ha ki sngi u Klaudios.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te kita ki synran, uwei pa uwei na ki katba u don la ka bor, ki la ïathmu skhem ban phah ka jingïarap ha ki parabangeit kiba shong ha Judia:",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> ïa kata ruh ki la leh, ki da phah lam ïa ka, sha ki tymmen basan da ka kti u Barnabas bad u Saul."
		},
		"12": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te hamar kata ka por, u Herod syiem u la sei ïa la ki kti ban pynjynjar ïa kiba na ka balang.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u la pynïap ïa u Jakob u para u Ïoannis da ka waitlam.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad haba u la ïohi ba ka la pynsngewbha ïa ki Jiw, u la thew ban kem sa ïa u Petros ruh. (Te ki la dei ki sngi U Kpu Bakhlem Thiat.)",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad haba u la lah kem ïa u, u la set ïa u ha ka ïing byndi, bad u la aiti ïa u ha ki khathynriew ngut ki shipai ban ap phira ïa u, ba u da mut, ynda lah Ka Niam Ka Jinglait ban pynmih ïa u ha u paidbah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Namar kata, la pynsah ïa u Petros ha kata ka ïing byndi, hynrei, la pynlong ka jingduwai bashitrhem da ka balang ha U Blei na ka bynta jong u.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba u Herod un sa pynmih noh ïa u; ha kata hi ka miet, u Petros u dang ïohthiah hapdeng ar ngut ki shipai, ba la khum da ki ar tylli ki kynjri, bad ki nongap ha khmat ka jingkhang ki la ap phira ïa kata ka ïing byndi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ha khmih, u angel U Trai u la ïeng hajan jong u, bad ka jingshai ka la tyngshaiñ ha kata ka kamra; te u la kyntuit na ka krung jong u Petros, bad u la kyrsiew ïa u, u da ong, “To ïeng kloi kloi!” Te ki kynjri jong u ki la hap noh na ki kti jong u.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Uta u angel u la ong ruh ha u, “To panpoh ïa lade, to pyndait ruh ïa la ki juti.” Bad u la leh kumta. Ynda kumta, u la ong ha u, “To tabah ïa la ka jingkup, to bud ruh ïa nga.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kumta u la mih noh, bad u la bud, te um tip ba ka la long kaba shisha kaba la leh da uta u angel, hynrei, u la mut ba u la ïohi ka jingithuhpaw.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba ki la ïaid lyngba ïa ka jingap phira ka banyngkong, bad ka ba-ar, ki la poi ha ka khyrdop nar kaba lam shapoh kata ka shnong, kata ka la plie hi ïa ki; bad haba ki la ïamih noh, ki la ïa-ïaid lyngba ïa kawei ka lynti shnong, te kumta hi uta u angel u la leit noh na u.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u Petros haba u la kyndit bynriew, u la ong, “Mynta nga tip da shisha, ba U Trai u la phah ïa u angel jong u, bad u la pyllait noh ïa nga na ka kti u Herod, bad na baroh ka jingkhmih lynti jong uta u paidbah Jiw.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ynda u la lah pyrkhat, u la poi sha ka ïing ka Mari ka kmie u Ïoannis, ïa uba la sin “Markos”; hangta, shibun ki la wan ïaseng lang, bad ki dang ïaduwai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te haba u la tied ïa ka jingkhang ka khyrdop, kawei ka shakri ka la leit ïa ka ban sngap, kaba kyrteng “ka Rhoda.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba ka la sngewthuh ïa ka ktien u Petros, namar ka jingkmen kam shym la plie ïa kata ka khyrdop, hynrei, ka la phet shapoh, bad ka la ïathuh ba u Petros u ïeng ha khmat ka khyrdop.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ki la ïa-ong ha ka, “Pha lamwir.” Hynrei, ka la ïathuh skhem ba ka long kumta. Te ki la ïa-ong, “Kata dei u angel jong u.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, u Petros u la nang tied, te ynda ki la lah plie, ki la ïohi ïa u, bad ki la ïasngewkyndit.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Hynrei, haba u la kaweh da la ka kti ha ki ban sngap jar, u la ïathuh ha ki, kumno ba U Trai u la ïalam noh ïa u na kata ka ïing byndi. Bad u la ong, “To ïathuh ïa kine kiei kiei ha u Jakob, bad ha ki parabangeit.” Ynda kumta, u la mih bad u la leit noh sha kawei pat ka jaka.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te tang shu shai ka sngi, la long ka jingkhihwin ym khyndiat hapdeng kita ki shipai, aïu ba la jia ïa u Petros.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te haba u Herod u la lah wad ïa u, bad ba um shem, u la tohkit ïa kita ki nongap phira, bad u la hukum ban pynïap noh ïa ki. Ynda kumta, u la leit hiar noh na Judia sha Kaisaria, bad u la shong sah hangta.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u Herod u dang buhnud eh ïa kiba na Tyros bad na Sidon; te ki la ïawan ha u da kawei ka jingmut, bad haba ki la ïaïoh lok bad u Blastos, u rangbah halor ka kamra thiah u syiem, ki la ïapan ïasuk, namar ka ri jong ki ka ïoh la ka bsa na ka ri jong uta u syiem.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ha kawei ka sngi ba la ïabuh, u Herod u la kup ïa ka jaiñkup syiem, bad haba u la shong halor ka khet bishar, u la saidthma ha ki.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te uta u paidbah u la risa, u da ong, “Ka jingkren u blei, ym ka jong u briew.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te kumne kumne u angel U Trai u la shoh ïa u, namar um shym la ai ka burom ha U Blei; te la bam ka ksaiñ ïa u, bad u la dkut mynsiem noh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei, ka ktien jong U Blei ka la nang roi, bad ka la man bun.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te u Barnabas bad u Saul, ynda ki la lah ïa-pyndep ïa la ka kam, ki la ïawan phai noh na Jerusalem, ki da wan ïalam lem bad ki, ïa u Ïoannis, uba la sin “Markos”."
		},
		"13": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te la don ha Antiok, ha ka balang kaba la don hangta, ki nongïathuhlypa bad ki nonghikai, u Barnabas, bad u Simeon ïa uba la khot “Niger”, bad u Loukios uba na Kyrini, bad u Manain u para ba la ïoh jingbsa lem bad u Herod u Tetrark, bad u Saul de.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te katba ki la shakri ïa U Trai, bad ba ki la shah jingit, U Mynsiem Bakhuid u la ong, “To pynkyrpang ha nga ïa u Barnabas bad ïa u Saul sha kata ka kam sha kaba nga la khot ïa ki.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te haba ki la ïashah jingit bad duwai, bad ba ki la buh ïa la ki kti ha ki, ki la phah noh ïa ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ki te haba la phah noh ïa ki da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, ki la ïaleit hiar sha Selukia, bad nangta ki la ïaleit da ka lieng sha Kypros.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te mynba ki la don ha Salamis, ki la ïalap ïa ka ktien U Blei ha ki synagog ki Jiw: te ki la ïadon ruh u Ïoannis kum u nongïarap jong ki.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba ki la lah ïa-ïaid lyngba ïa kata ka 'dewlynnong baroh kawei haduh Paphos, ki la shem ïa uwei u nongleh byrtong, u nongïathuhlypa balamler, u Jiw, uba kyrteng “u Bar-Jisu”;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> uba la don lem bad u Serjios Paulos, u lyngskor, u briew u bashemphang; une, haba u la khot ha u ïa u Barnabas bad u Saul, u la kwah ban ïohsngew ïa ka ktien U Blei.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Hynrei, uta u Elimas u nongleh byrtong (naba kumta la batai ïa ka kyrteng jong u), u la ïaleh pyrshah ïa ki, u da pyrshang ban pynphai noh ïa uta u lyngskor na kata ka jingngeit.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei u Saul, ïa uba la khot “Paul” ruh, uba la dap da U Mynsiem Bakhuid, u la peit shaiñ ha u,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad u la ong, “A uba dap da ka buit arsap suda, bad da ka buit bymman suda, me u khun u Soitan, me u nongshun ka hok baroh, men ym wai shuh ban pynbakla ïa ki lynti babeit jong U Trai?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Mynta te ha khmih, ka kti U Trai ka long halor jong me, bad men sa matlah, khlem da ïohi ïa ka sngi katto katne por.” Te shisyndon la hap ha u, u lyoh bad ka jingdum; te u la leit kylleng u da wad ïa ki ban btin ïa u na ka kti.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te uta u lyngskor, haba u la ïohi ïa kaba la leh, u la ngeit, u da sngewkyndit namar kata ka jinghikai jong U Trai.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te u Paul bad ki lok jong u ki la mih noh da ka lieng na Paphos, bad ki la ïapoi sha Perga ha Pamphilia; u Ïoannis te haba u la ïakhlad na ki, u la leit phai pat sha Jerusalem.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, ma ki, haba ki la ïaleit noh na Perga, ki la ïapoi ha Antiok jong ka Pisidia; te ki la ïaleit hapoh ka synagog ha ka sngi Sabbaton, bad ki la ïashong.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ynda la lah kaba pule ïa Ka Hukum bad Ki Nongïathuhlypa, ki nongsynshar ka synagog ki la ïaphah ha ki, ki da ong, “Ko para, lada phi don kano kano ka ktien sneng ïa u paidbah, to kren.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ynda kumta, u Paul u la ïeng joit, bad haba u la kaweh da la ka kti, u la ong, “Ko rangbah Israel bad phi kiba sheptieng ïa U Blei, to sngew.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Blei jong une u paidlang Israel, u la jied ïa ki kpa jong ngi; bad u la pynkyntiew ïa une u paidlang mynba ki la shong basa ha ka ri Ijipt, bad da ka ksang'ti badonbor u la ïalam noh ïa ki na ka.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te kumba sawphew snem u la ïaishah ïa ki jingleh jong ki ha kata ka ri khlaw.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad haba u la lah pynjot ïa ki hynñiew ki jaid bynriew ha ka ri Kanaan, u la ai ha ki, ïa ka ri jong ki ban long ka jingïoh kynti, kumba sawspah sanphew snem.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te hadien kine kiei kiei, u la ai ki nongbishar ha ki, haduh u Samuel u nongïathuhlypa.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad hadien kata, ki la ïapan ban ïoh syiem: te U Blei u la ai ha ki, ïa u Saul u khun u Kish, u briew na ka jaid Benjamin, jin sawphew snem.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ynda u la pynduh syiem ïa u, u la pynmih ïa u Dabid ban long u syiem jong ki, ïa uba u la phla ruh bad u la ong, ‘Nga la shem ïa u Dabid u khun u Jesse, u briew uba kum ka dohnud jong nga, u ban leh ïa ka mon jong nga baroh.’",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Na u symbai jong une u briew, U Blei, katba kum ka jingkular, u la pynmih ha ki Israel ïa U Nongpynim, U Jisu keiñ,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> mynba u Ïoannis u la ïalap nyngkong ha shuwa kata ka jingwan jong U, ïa ka jingbaptis ka jingkylla-ka-bamut ha u paidbah Israel baroh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te katba u Ïoannis u dang pyndep ïa la ka jingphet, u la ong, ‘Phi tharai ba nga long uei? Ngam long uta; hynrei, ha khmih, don uba wan nadien jong nga, wat ïa ki juti ki kjat jong U ngam long uba bit nam ïa ka ban loit noh.’",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “Ko para, ki khun ki ksiew u Abraham, bad kita kiba sheptieng ïa U Blei hapdeng jong phi, ha ngi keiñ la phah ïa ka ktien jong kane ka jingpynim.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Namar kita kiba shong ha Jerusalem, bad ki nongsynshar jong ki, naba kim shym la ithuh ïa une, lymne ïa ki ktien jong ki nongïathuhlypa ïa kiba ju pule man la ka sngi Sabbaton, ki la ïa-pyndep noh ïa ki da kaba ïa-pynrem ïa U.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad la kim shym la shem ka daw ban ïap, ki la ïakyrpad pynban ïa u Pilat ba yn pynïap noh ïa U.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Bad haba ki la lah pyndep ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba la thoh shaphang jong U, ki la ïa-pynhiar ïa U na u dieng, bad ki la buh ïa U ha ka jingtep.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Hynrei, U Blei u la pynmih pat ïa U na ki baïap.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad la ïohi ïa U bun sngi da kita kiba la ïawan kiew lem bad U na Galilaïa sha Jerusalem; kiba long mynta ki nongphla jong U ha u paidbah.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Bad ngi wallam ha phi ïa ka khubor babha, kata ka jingkular ba la kular ha ki kpa, kumno ba U Blei u la pyndep noh ïa kata ha ki khun jong ngi, ha kaba u la pynmih pat ïa U Jisu.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Kumba la thoh ruh ha ka Salm ka ba-ar; “ ‘Me long U Khun jong nga, ha kane ka sngi nga la pynkha ïa me.’",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> “Te shaphang ba u la pynmih pat ïa U na ki baïap, ban ym leit phai shuh sha kaba pyut, u la kren kumne: “ ‘Ngan ai ha phi ïa kita ki jingaiei bakhuid bad baskhem jong u Dabid.’",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Namar u ong ruh ha kawei pat ka Salm: “ ‘Men ym shah ïa U Bakhuid jong me ban shem ïa kaba pyut.’",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> “Namar, u Dabid ynda u la lah shakri ïa ka mon U Blei ha la ka jong ka pateng bynriew, u la ïohthiah noh, bad la pynbuh lang ïa u bad ki kpa jong u; bad u la shem ïa kaba pyut,",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> hynrei, une, ïa uba U Blei u la pynmih pat, um shym la shem ïa kaba pyut.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Namar kata, to tip phi, A ki para, ba da une u briew keiñ, ïa kaba map ki pop la ïalap ha phi:",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> bad da une, ba pynksan ïa u briew baroh uba ngeit, na kiei kiei baroh na kiba phim lah ban ïoh ksan da ka hukum u Moses.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Namar kata, to sumar ïoh kan jia ha phi, kata ïa kaba la kren ha Ki Nongïathuhlypa:",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> “ ‘Ha khmih, A phi ki nongibeiñ, to sngewphylla ruh, bad to jah noh jar ruh; naba nga, nga leh ïa ka jingleh ha ki sngi jong phi, ka jingleh keiñ kaba phin ym ngeit da kumno kumno ruh, wat lada uno uno ruh u batai ïa ka ha phi.’ ”",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te katba ki ïamih noh, ki la ïakyrpad ba yn ïoh ïalap ha ki, ïa kine ki ktien ha ka sngi Sabbaton kaba bud.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Te haba la pynwai noh ïa kata ka jingïaseng synagog, shibun ki Jiw bad kiba la kylla niam ki bariewblei ki la ïabud ïa u Paul bad u Barnabas; kiba, haba ki ïakren ha ki, ki la kyntu ïa ki ban ïaineh ha ka jingaiei jong U Blei.",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> Te ha ka sngi Sabbaton kaba bud, la jan baroh shi shnong ki la ïalang ban ïohsngew ïa ka ktien U Blei.",
			"45": "<sup>45</sup> Hynrei, haba ki Jiw ki la ïohi ïa kita ki paidbah, la pyndap ïa ki da ka jingpihuiñ; bad ki la ïasaid pyrshah ïa kita kiei kiei ruh ba la kren da u Paul, bad ki la ïakrenbeiñ ruh.",
			"46": "<sup>46</sup> Ynda kumta, u Paul bad u Barnabas ki la kren shlur, bad ki la ong, “La donkam ban ïalap ha phi nyngkong ïa ka ktien U Blei; hynrei, namar ba phi kyntait noh ïa ka, bad ba phi rai ïa lade ki bymbit ïa ka jingim bymjukut, ha khmih, ngi phai noh sha ki Jentil.",
			"47": "<sup>47</sup> Naba kumta, U Trai u la hukum ïa ngi, u da ong: “Nga la buh ïa me ban long ka jingshai ïa ki Jentil, ba men long ka jingpynim shaduh ka bakut ka pyrthei.”",
			"48": "<sup>48</sup> Te haba ki Jentil ki la ïohsngew ïa kane, ki la sngewkmen, bad ki la pyndonburom ïa ka ktien U Blei, bad kat kiba la thung sha ka jingim bymjukut, ki la ngeit;",
			"49": "<sup>49</sup> te la pynphriang ïa ka ktien U Trai kylleng sawdong kata ka ri baroh.",
			"50": "<sup>50</sup> Hynrei, kita ki Jiw ki la ïa-pynshoi ïa ki kynthei ki bariewblei ki bakhraw batri, bad ïa ki rangbah jong kata ka shnong, bad ki la ïapynkhih ka jinglehbeiñ ïa u Paul bad u Barnabas, bad ki la beh noh ïa ki na ki phang jong ki.",
			"51": "<sup>51</sup> Hynrei, ki la ïakynther noh ïa ka 'dewmet na ki kjat jong ki sha ki, bad ki la poi sha Ikoniom.",
			"52": "<sup>52</sup> Te la pyndap ïa kita ki synran da ka jingkmen, bad da U Mynsiem Bakhuid."
		},
		"14": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia te ha Ikoniom, ba ki la rung lang hapoh ka synagog jong ki Jiw, bad ki la ïalap ha kata ka rukom katba u paidbah byllien ki Jiw ruh bad ki Grik ki la ngeit.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Hynrei, kita ki Jiw ki bymngeit, ki la pynkhih buk ïa ki mynsiem jong ki Jentil, bad ki la pynsniew jingmut ïa ki pyrshah ïa kita ki parabangeit.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Namar kata, ki la shong kham slem hangta, ki da kren shlur ha U Trai, uba phla pynskhem ïa ka ktien ka jingaiei jong u, da kaba u ai ban leh ki dak khyllah bad ki jingphylla da ki kti jong ki.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, u paidbah kata ka shnong u la ïakad ar liang; shi bynta ki la ïashah sha ki Jiw, bad shi bynta sha ki apostol.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te haba la tur pyrshah da kita ki Jentil ruh bad da ki Jiw, lem bad ki nongsynshar jong ki, ban lehbeiñ, bad ban lynthem maw ïa ki,",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> ki la tip ïa kata, bad ki la ïaphet sha ki shnong jong ka Lykaonia, sha Lystra bad Derbi, bad kylleng kata ka ri;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> hangta ruh ki la ïalap ïa ka gospel.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ha Lystra la don uwei u briew uba shu shong, ba u khlem bor ha ki kjat, u ba-dkoh naduh ka kpoh ka kmie jong u, u bym ju lah ïaid.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Une u la ïohsngew ïa u Paul ba u kren; uba haba u la khmih shaiñ ïa u, bad ba u la ïohi ba u don ka jingngeit ïa ka ban ïoh khiah,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> u la ong da ka ktien bajam, “To ïeng beit da la ki kjat.” Te u la rynsied bad u la ïaid.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te haba kita ki paidbah ki la ïohi ïa kaba u Paul u la leh, ki la pynjam ïa la ka ktien, ki da ong ha ka ktien Lykaonia, “Ki blei ki la wan hiar ha ngi ha ka dur briew.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ki la ïakhot ïa u Barnabas, “Jupiter”, bad ïa u Paul, “Merkuri”, namar ba u long u nongkren ba kham rangbah.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Bad u lyngdoh u Jupiter, uba ka ïingmane jong u ka don ha khmat kata ka shnong, haba u la wallam ïa ki masi dab bad ïa ki pansngiat syntiew ha ki khyrdop, u la mut ban kñia lem bad kita ki paidbah.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, haba kita ki apostol – u Barnabas bad u Paul – ki la ïohsngew ïa kata, ki la kad la ki jaiñkup, bad ki la ïarynsied kynsan hapdeng uta u paidbah, ki da pyrta,",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ki da ong ruh, “Ko rangbah, balei phi leh ïa kine kiei kiei ruh! Ngi ruh ngi long tang ki briew kiba kum phi hi, bad ngi ïathuhkhana babha ha phi ba phin phai noh na kine ki jingmane thala sha U Blei u ba-im, uba la thaw ïa ka bneng, bad ïa ka khyndew, bad ïa ka duriaw, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba don ha ki.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ha kita ki pateng bynriew kiba la leit noh, u la shah ïa ki jaid bynriew baroh ban ïaid ha ki lynti la ki jong hi:",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> la kumta ruh, um shym la iehnoh ïa lade khlem sakhi, ba u da leh ïa ka babha, bad u la ai ha phi na bneng ïa u slap, bad ïa ki aïom basei soh, u da pyndap ïa ki dohnud jong phi da ka jingbam bad ka jingkmen.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te da kine ki jingong, da kaba eh ki la ïa-pynpep noh ïa kita ki paidbah na ka ban kñia ha ki.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, la poi hangta ki Jiw na Antiok bad na Ikoniom, kiba haba ki la ïakhroh ïa kita ki paidbah, ki la ïalynthem maw ïa u Paul bad ki la ïaring noh ïa u shabar kata ka shnong, ba ki da tharai ba u la lah ïap.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Hynrei, haba kita ki synran ki la ïeng tawiar ïa u, u la khie joit, bad u la leit shapoh kata ka shnong. Te ha kaba lashai u la leit noh lem bad u Barnabas sha Derbi.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ynda ki la lah ïalap ïa ka gospel ha kata ka shnong, bad ba ki la ïa-pynlong bun synran, ki la ïaleit phai pat sha Lystra, bad sha Ikoniom bad sha Antiok,",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> ki da pynskhem ïa ki mynsiem jong ki synran, da kaba sneng ïa ki ban ïaineh ha kata ka jingngeit, bad ba ka dei ïa ngi ban bsut shapoh ka hima U Blei lyngba shibun ki jynjar.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ynda ki la thung ha ki, ki tymmen basan ha la ka balang balang baroh, bad ba ki la ïaduwai lem bad ka jingshah jingit, ki la ïa-aiti ïa ki ha U Trai ha uba ki la lah ngeit.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba ki la ïaleit lyngba ïa ka Pisidia, ki la ïapoi ha Pamphilia.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad ynda ki la ïalap ïa ka ktien ha Perga, ki la ïaleit hiar noh sha Attalia;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> nangta ruh ki la ïaleit noh da ka lieng sha Antiok, na kaba la lah aiti noh ïa ki ha ka jingaiei jong U Blei ïa kata ka kam ïa kaba ki la lah ïa-pyndep noh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ynda ki la lah ïapoi te, bad ba ki la lah ïalum lang ïa kata ka balang, ki la ïathuh naduh haduh ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba U Blei u la lah leh da ki, bad kumno ba u la lah plie wang ha ki Jentil ïa ka jingkhang ka jingngeit.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Bad ki la ïashong ym khyndiat por lem bad kita ki synran."
		},
		"15": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te la don ki briew kiba la wan hiar na Judia, bad ki la hikai ïa ki parabangeit, ki ong, “Lymda otsher ïa phi kat kum ka niam ka rukom u Moses, phim lah ban ïohlait im.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ynda u Paul bad u Barnabas ki la ïa-pyneh bad ki la ïasaid bad ki ym khyndiat, ki parabangeit ki la ïakut ba u Paul bad u Barnabas, bad kiwei de na ki, kin leit kiew sha Jerusalem ha ki apostol bad ki tymmen basan shaphang kane ka jingïasaid.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ki, namar kata, haba la leit on lynti ïa ki da kata ka balang, ki la ïaleit lyngba ïa ka Phoiniki bad ka Samaria, ki da ïathuh ïa ka jingkylla jong ki Jentil, bad ki la pynlong ka jingkmen bakhraw ha ki parabangeit baroh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Ynda ki la poi te ha Jerusalem, la pdiang ïa ki da ka balang, bad da ki apostol, bad da ki tymmen basan de; te ki la ïathuh naduh haduh ïa kiei kiei ruh ba U Blei u la lah leh da ki.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, la ïeng kiba na ki kynja Pharisi kiba la ngeit, ki da ong, “Ka dei ban otsher ïa ki, bad ban hukum ïa ki ban sumar ïa ka hukum u Moses.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki apostol bad ki tymmen basan ki la ïalum lang ïa ka ban ïapyrkhat shaphang kane ka kam.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ynda la long bun ka jingïasaid, u Petros u la ïeng joit, bad u la ong ha ki: “Ko parabangeit, phi, phi tip kumno ba la kham slem mynta U Blei u la jied hapdeng jong phi, ba ki Jentil da ka shyntur jong nga kin ïohsngew ïa ka ktien ka gospel, bad ba kin ngeit.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Blei ruh, uba tip ïa ka dohnud, u la phla babha ïa ki, da kaba u la ai ha ki, ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid, kumba u la leh ha ngi ruh:",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> te um shym la pynïapher ei ei ruh hapdeng jong ngi bad jong ki, ba u da pynkhuid ïa ki dohnud jong ki da ka jingngeit.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te mynta, balei phi ïatynjuh ïa U Blei, ba phin buh ka lyngkor ha ka ryndang kita ki synran, ïa kaba ki kpa jong ngi lymne ma ngi ngim ju lah ban bah?",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, ngi ngeit ba da ka jingaiei ka jong U Trai Jisu, yn pynim ïa ngi ha kajuh ka rukom, kum ma ki ruh.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te u paidlang baroh u la sngap jar, bad ki la ïashahshkor ruh ïa u Barnabas bad u Paul katba ki ïathuh ïa kiba katno ki dak khyllah bad ki jingphylla ba U Blei u la lah leh hapdeng ki Jentil da ki.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ynda ki la lah sngap jar, u Jakob u la ïathuh, u da ong, “Ko parabangeit, to sngew ïa nga.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U Simeon u la ïathuh kumno ha kaba nyngkong ba U Blei u la leit khmih ïa ki Jentil, ban shim na ki u paidlang ïa ka kyrteng jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad kane ka ïadei bad kita ki ktien jong ki nongïathuhlypa; kumba la thoh:",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> “ ‘Hadien kine kiei kiei ngan wan phai pat bad ngan tei pat ïa Ka Tabernakl u Dabid kaba la kyllon noh, bad ngan tei pat ïa kiba jot jong ka bad ngan pynïeng pat ïa ka,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> ba ki basah na ki briew kin ïoh wad ïa U Trai, bad kita ki Jentil baroh keiñ ha kiba la buh ïa ka kyrteng jong nga,’ ong U Trai,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> uba pyntip ïa kine kiei kiei ruh naduh ka basdang ka pyrthei.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Naba kumta, ka jingkut jingmut jong nga ka long, ban ym pynkhuslai shuh ïa kiba napdeng ki Jentil kiba phai sha U Blei,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> hynrei, ba ngin thoh sha ki, ba kin kyndiah noh na ki jingbit-tngit ki bleithaw, bad na kaba klim, bad na kaba la khyrwait, bad na ka snam de;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> namar u Moses na mynhyndai eh, u la don man la ka shnong kita kiba ïalap ïa u, da kaba ki pule ïa u ha ki synagog man ka sngi Sabbaton.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, ka la ibit ïa ki apostol bad ïa ki tymmen basan, lem bad baroh kawei ka balang, ban jied ki rangbah napdeng jong ki bad ban phah ïa ki sha Antiok lem bad u Paul bad u Barnabas; kata ka long, ïa u Judas ïa uba sin “Barsabbas”, bad ïa u Silas, ki rangbah baïalam phrang hapdeng kita ki parabangeit.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ki la thoh lem bad ki kumne: “Ki apostol bad ki tymmen basan, ha kita ki parabangeit kiba na ki Jentil ha Antiok bad Syria bad Kilikia de, Khublei.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Namar kumba ngi la ïohsngew, ba don kiba la leit noh na ngi kiba la ïapynkhuslai ïa phi da ki ktien, da kaba pynsuhsat ïa ki mynsiem jong phi, ha kiba ngim shym la ai hukum kumno kumno ruh,",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> ka la ibit ïa ngi, haba ngi la ïakut jingmut kawei, ban jied ki rangbah bad ban phah ïa ki ha phi lem bad kita kiba ieit jong ngi, u Barnabas bad u Paul,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> ki briew kiba la kheiñduh ïa la ka jingim na ka bynta ka kyrteng U Trai jong ngi U Jisu Khrist.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Namar kata, ngi la ïaphah noh ïa u Judas bad u Silas, kiba da la ka shyntur jong ki hi kin ïathuh ha phi ïa kita kijuh kiei kiei ruh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Naba ka la ibit ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid, bad ïa ngi, ban ym pynkit halor jong phi ka jingkit kaba kham khia nalor kine kiei kiei ruh kiba donkam;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> ba phin kyndiah noh na kiei kiei ba la kñia ïa ki bleithaw, bad na ka snam, bad na kiei kiei kiba la khyrwait, bad na kiba klim. Na kine, lada phi sumar kyndong ïa lade, phin man bha keiñ. Khublei.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Kumta, kita, ynda la pyllait noh ïa ki, ki la ïapoi sha Antiok; te ynda ki la ïalum lang ïa u paidlang, ki la ïa-ai noh ïa kata ka shithi.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Bad haba ki la lah pule ïa ka, ki la ïasngewkmen namar kata ka jingpyntngen.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> U Judas te bad u Silas, ba ki long hi ki nongïathuhlypa ruh, ki la ïakyntu ïa ki parabangeit da shibun ki ktien, bad ki la pynskhem ïa ki.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ynda ki la ïaishong kham slem, la pyllait noh ïa ki da kaba suk na kita ki parabangeit sha kita kiba la lah phah ïa ki.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hynrei, ka la ibit ïa u Silas ban dang sah shuh hangta.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> U Paul te bad u Barnabas ki la ïashong ha Antiok, ki da ïahikai bad ki da ïalap ïa ka ktien U Trai, lem bad shibun kiwei kiwei ruh.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te ynda khyndiat sngi, u Paul u la ong ha u Barnabas, “Ïa ngin ïaleit phai pat mynta, ba ngin ïakhmih ïa kita ki parabangeit ha man la ka shnong ha kaba ngi la ïalap ïa ka ktien U Trai, kumno ki ïalong.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te u Barnabas u la imon ban shim lok lem ïa u Ïoannis ruh, ïa uba khot “Markos”,",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> hynrei, u Paul um sngewdei ban shim lok lem ïa une, uba la kynriah noh na ki na Pamphilia, bad u bym shym la leit lem bad ki sha kata ka kam.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Kumta te la mih ka jingïasaid kaba jur haduh ba ki la ïakhlad lok noh; kumta, u Barnabas haba u la shim ha u ïa u Markos, u la leit mih noh da ka lieng sha Kypros,",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> hynrei, u Paul u la jied ïa u Silas bad u la leit noh ynda la aiti noh ïa u ha ka jingaiei jong U Trai da kita ki parabangeit.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Bad u la leit lyngba ïa ka Syria bad ka Kilikia, u da pynskhem ïa kita ki balang."
		},
		"16": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u la wan sha Derbi bad Lystra: ha khmih ruh, la don hangta uwei u synran uba kyrteng “u Timothi”, u khun kawei ka Jiw kaba ngeit, hynrei, u kpa jong u, u Grik:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> ïa uba la phla babha da kita ki parabangeit kiba ha Lystra bad ha Ikoniom.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ïa une, u Paul u la imon ba un leit ryngkat bad u; te haba u la shim u la otsher ïa u, na ka bynta kita ki Jiw kiba don ha kita ki phang; naba baroh ki la tip ba u kpa jong u, u long u Grik.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te katba ki dang ïaleit lyngba ïa kita ki shnong, ki la aiti ha ki ban sumar ïa kita ki jingrai kiba la lah ïakut da ki apostol bad ki tymmen basan kiba ha Jerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Kumta, la pynskhem ïa kita ki balang ha kata ka jingngeit, bad ki la man bun ha ka jingkheiñ ha la ka sngi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ki la ïaleit lyngba ïa ka ri Phrygia bad Galatia, ba la pynpep ïa ki da U Mynsiem Bakhuid ban ïalap ïa kata ka ktien ha Asia;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> bad haba ki la ïapoi haduh Mysia, ki la ïapyrshang ban leit sha Bithynia; te U Mynsiem jong U Jisu um shah ïa ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Bad ynda ki la ïa-ïaid kiar ïa ka Mysia, ki la ïaleit hiar sha Troas.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ka jingithuhpaw ka la paw ha u Paul mynmiet; uwei u briew uba na Makedonia u la ïeng, u da kyrpad ïa u, bad u da ong, “To wan sha shiliang sha Makedonia bad to ïarap ïa ngi.”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba u la ïohi ïa kata ka jingithuhpaw, shisyndon ngi la ïapyrshang ban leit noh sha Makedonia, ngi da ïarai jingmut ba U Blei u la lah khot khnang ïa ngi ïa ka ban ïalap ïa ka gospel ha ki.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Namar kata, ynda ngi la ïaid lieng na Troas, ngi la leit beit sha Samothraki, bad kum lashai sha Neapolis;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> nangta ruh sha Philipi, kaba long ka nongbah ka banyngkong ha kata ka bynta ka jong ka Makedonia, kaba la buhai ki Rom: te ngi la ïashong ha kata ka nongbah katto katne sngi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ha ka sngi Sabbaton ngi la ïaleit shabar shnong harud ka wah, ha kaba ngi la tharai ba la don ka jaka duwai; bad ynda ngi la ïashong, ngi la kren ha ki kynthei kiba la wan ïaseng lang.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te kawei ka briew kaba kyrteng “ka Lydia”, ka nongdie jaiñ saw bthuh na ka shnong Thiateira, kaba mane ïa U Blei, ka la sngew ïa ngi; ïa ka dohnud jong ka U Trai u la plie wang, ban shahshkor ïa kita kiei kiei ruh ïa kiba la ïalap da u Paul.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te ynda la pynbaptis ïa ka, bad ïa ki ba-ha-ïing jong ka, ka la kyrpad ïa ngi, ka da ong, “Lada phi la rai ba nga long kaba ngeit ha U Trai, to wan shong ha ïing jong nga.” Ka la pynkohnguh ruh ïa ngi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ka la jia ruh, haba ngi dang ïaleit sha ka jaka duwai, ba kawei ka shakri kaba shong ksuid ba kren blei ka la ïakynduh bad ngi, kaba ju pynïoh shibun ka jingmyntoi ïa ki kynrad jong ka da kaba kren byrtong.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kane, haba ka bud jan ïa u Paul bad ïa ngi, ka la pyrta, ka da ong, “Kine ki briew ki long ki shakri jong U Blei U Bahakhlieh Tam Eh, kiba pynbna ha phi ïa ka lynti ka jingpynim!”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ïa kane te ka la leh bun sngi. Hynrei, u Paul, haba u la sngewsatia eh, u la phai dien, bad u la ong ha uta u ksuid, “Nga hukum ïa me ha ka kyrteng U Jisu Khrist ban mih noh na ka.” Bad ha kata kajuh ka por u la mih noh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, haba kita ki kynrad jong ka ki la ïohi ba ka jingkyrmen kata ka nong jong ki ka la duh noh, ki la kem ïa u Paul bad ïa u Silas, bad ki la ïaring noh ïa ki sha ka jaka ïew, ha khmat ki nongsynshar;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> te ynda ki la ïalam ïa ki ha ki majistor, ki la ong, “Kine ki briew, kiba long ki Jiw, ki ïa-pynkhihwin jlang ïa ka shnong jong ngi:",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> bad ki ïalap ïa ki niam ki rukom ki bymdei ïa ngi kiba long ki Rom ban pdiang lymne ban leh.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Uta u paidbah te u la ïeng lang ban ïaleh ïa ki: bad kita ki majistor haba ki la ïapatar ïa ki jaiñ jong ki, ki la hukum ban shoh da ki thri ïa ki.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ynda ki la lah sympat ïa ki bun thri, ki la set ïa ki ha ka ïing byndi, ki da hukum skhem ïa u nongap byndi ban ap phira bha ïa ki;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> uba haba u la ïoh ka hukum kat kata, u la set ïa ki ha kata ka ïing byndi kaba kham shapoh, bad u la pynskhem ïa ki kjat jong ki ha ki dieng song.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, hamar kaba shiteng synñia, u Paul bad u Silas ki la ïaduwai, bad ki la ïarwai ïaroh ïa U Blei, bad ki nongsah byndi ki la shahshkor ïa ki.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te shisyndon la jia ka jingkhynñiuh jumai kaba khraw, kat ban pynkhynñiuh noh ïa ki nongrim jong kata ka ïing byndi; te kumne kumne ruh la plie wang ïa ki jingkhang baroh, bad ïa ki kynjri jong ki baroh la loit noh ruh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te uta u nongap byndi, haba la pynkyndit ïa u na kaba ïohthiah, bad ba u la ïohi ba la plie wang ïa ki jingkhang jong kata ka ïing byndi, u la sei noh ïa la ka waitlam sa ban pynïap noh ïa lade, u da tharai ba kita ki nongsah byndi ki la ïaphet noh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Hynrei, u Paul u la pyrta noh da ka ktien bajam, u da ong, “Wat pynmynsaw ïa lade, naba ngi don hangne baroh!”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U te u la pan ïa ki jingshai, bad u la rynsied kynsan shapoh, bad ba u la khynñiuh namar kaba sheptieng, u la dem khop ha khmat u Paul bad u Silas,",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> bad u la ïalam noh ïa ki shabar, bad u la ong, “A kynrad, aïu ka dei ïa nga ban leh ba yn pynim ïa nga?”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ki te ki la ïathuh, “To men ngeit ha U Jisu uba U Trai, bad yn sa pynim ïa me bad ïa ka ïing jong me.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ki la ïalap ruh ïa ka ktien U Trai ha u, bad ha baroh kiba ha ïing jong u.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u la shim ïa ki ha kata kajuh ka por mynmiet, bad u la sait noh ïa ki jingmong jong ki; bad la pynbaptis ïa u, ma u bad ki jong u baroh, kumne kumne ruh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad u la ïalam ïa ki sha ka ïing jong u, bad u la buh jingbam ha khmat jong ki, bad u la sngewkmen eh lem bad ka ïing jong u baroh kawei ba ki la ïangeit ha U Blei.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te haba la mih ka sngi, ki majistor ki la phah da ki piada, ki da ong, “Pyllait noh ïa kita ki briew.”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Uta u nongap byndi te u la ïathuh ïa kine ki ktien ha u Paul, “Ki majistor ki la phah pyllait noh ïa phi: mynta namar kata ale mih noh, bad leit noh ha kaba suk.”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Hynrei, u Paul u la ong ha ki, “Ki la sympat ïa ngi ha kaba paw khlem da bishar, haba ngi long ki trai-shnong Rom, bad ki la set ïa ngi ha byndi; te mynta ki shu pyllait jar jar ïa ngi? Ym kumta phi; hynrei, ai kin da wan hi bad ïalam noh ïa ngi shabar.”",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te kita ki piada, ki la ïathuh pat ïa kine ki ktien ha ki majistor; te ki la sheptieng haba ki la ïohsngew ba ki long ki trai-shnong Rom;",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> bad ki la wan bad ki la ïakyrpad noh ïa ki; bad haba ki la ïalam noh ïa ki shabar, ki la ïakyrpad ïa ki ban leit noh na kata ka shnong.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te ki la ïaleit noh na kata ka ïing byndi, bad ki la leit rung ha ka ïing ka Lydia: bad haba ki la lah ïohi ïa ki parabangeit, ki la pyntngen ïa ki, bad ki la leit noh."
		},
		"17": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba ki la leit lyngba ïa ka Amphipolis bad ka Appollonia, ki la poi ha Thessaloni, ha kaba la don ka synagog jong ki Jiw.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te u Paul, kumba u ju leh, u la leit rung ha ki, bad lai sngi Sabbaton u la pyni nia ha ki na Ki Jingthoh,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> da kaba batai bad da kaba ong skhem, ba ka la dei ïa U Khrist ban shah, bad ban mihpat na ki baïap; bad ba “une U Jisu, ïa uba nga, nga ïalap ha phi, u long uta U Khrist.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te don na ki, kiba la ngeit, bad ki la ïasoh lok bad u Paul bad u Silas, bad u paidbah babun na ki Grik bariewblei, bad na ki kynthei ki bakhraw batri ym khyndiat.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, kita ki Jiw da kaba sngewpihuiñ, ki la ïakhot lok ïa ki briew bathala na ki kynja bapoh, bad haba ki la pynlang paidbah, ki la ïa-pynkhihwin jlang ïa kata ka nongbah; bad haba ki la ïeng ïaleh ïa ka ïing u Jason, ki la ïapyrshang ban pynmih noh ïa ki sha uta u paidbah.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba kim shym la shem ïa ki, ki la ïaring noh ïa uta u Jason bad ïa kiba na ki parabangeit ha khmat ki nongsynshar ka shnong, ki da pyrta, “Kine kiba la pynkylla khongpong ïa ka pyrthei ki la wan poi hangne ruh!",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> ïa kiba u Jason u la khot ïing: bad kine baroh ki ïaleh pyrshah ïa ki hukum u Kaisar, ki da ong ba don uwei pat u syiem, U Jisu.”",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te ki la ïa-pynlyngngoh ïa uta u paidbah bad ïa ki nongsynshar ka shnong haba ki la ïohsngew ïa kine kiei kiei ruh.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, ynda ki la lah shim ka jingbahkhlieh na uta u Jason bad na kita kiwei pat, ki la pyllait noh ïa ki.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te kita ki parabangeit kumne kumne ruh ki la phah noh ïa u Paul bad u Silas mynmiet sha Beria; kiba haba ki la lah poi hangta, ki la ïaleit sha ka synagog ki Jiw.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Kine te ki la long kiba kham don akor ban ïa kita kiba ha Thessaloni, kiba la pdiang ïa kata ka ktien da ka jingsngew-la-kloi baroh, ha la ka sngi ki da ïitbniah ïa Ki Jingthoh, la kine kiei kiei ruh ki lah long kumta ne em.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Namar kata keiñ, bun na ki, ki la ngeit; na ki kynthei Grik ruh ki bakhraw batri, bad na ki rangbah de ym khyndiat.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, ynda ki Jiw kiba na Thessaloni ki la bna ba ha Beria ruh la ïalap da u Paul ïa ka ktien U Blei, ki la ïawan hangta ruh, ki da ïapynkhih bad pynkulmar ïa ki paidbah.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te kumta, mar mar kita ki parabangeit ki la ïaphah noh ïa u Paul ban leit shaduh rud duriaw; hynrei, u Silas bad u Timothi ki la ïanangsah hangta.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Hynrei, kita kiba la leit on ïa u Paul, ki la ïalam ïa u haduh Athen; bad haba ki la ïoh ka hukum ïa u Silas bad ïa u Timothi ba kin wan ha u kloi kloi katba lah, ki la ïaleit wan noh.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te katba u Paul u ap khmih lynti ïa ki ha Athen, la pynkhih buk ïa ka mynsiem jong u hapoh jong u haba u khmih ïa kata ka nongbah ba ka dap da ki bleithaw.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Kumta, u la ïa-pyni nia ha ka synagog bad ki Jiw bad kita ki bariewblei ruh, bad ha ka jaka ïew ha la ka sngi ruh bad kita kiba ïakynduh bad u.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Bad la don ki riewstad na ki Epikuri bad na ki Stoik kiba la ïaleh nia bad u: te don kiba la ïa-ong, “Ine iba blab blab i mon ban ong aïu?” Hynrei, kiwei pat, “U i kumba u long u nongïalap ïa ki blei khyllah”; naba u la ïalap ïa U Jisu bad ïa ka jingmihpat.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ynda ki la kem ïa u, ki la ïalam noh ïa u sha u lum Ariopagos, ki da ong, “Ngi lah ban tip kaei kane ka jinghikai bathymmai ïa kaba me ïalap?",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Namar me wallam ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba khyllah sha ki shkor jong ngi; namar kata, ngi kwah ban tip, ki mut aïu kine kiei kiei ruh.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> (Te ki nong Athen baroh bad ki sohshnong kiba shong basa hangta, kim ju kloi ïa kaei kaei ruh kawei pat, hynrei, tang ban ïathuh lane ban ïohsngew ïa kaei kaei kaba kham thymmai.)",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te u Paul u la ïeng hapdeng uta u lum Ariopagos, bad u la ong, “Ko rangbah Athen, nga ïohi ha kiei kiei baroh ba phi long kiba kham shait mane blei:",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> namar haba nga ïaid bad nga khmih thuh ïa kiei kiei ruh ki jingmane jong phi, nga la shem ka duwan ha kaba la don ka jingthoh kum kane, ‘Ha U Blei ïa u bymithuh.’ Ïa uba phi ïamane namar kata khlem da ithuh, ïa une keiñ nga ïalap ha phi:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> uta U Blei keiñ uba la thaw ïa ka pyrthei, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba don ha ka, uba haba u long U Trai ka bneng bad ka khyndew, um shong ha ki ïing blei ba la thaw da ki kti;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> lymne ym ju shakri ïa u da ki kti ki briew, kumba u da kyrduh ei ei ruh, haba u hi u ai ha ki baroh ïa ka jingim, bad ka mynsiem, bad ïa kiei kiei baroh ruh;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> u la thaw ruh na kawei ka snam ïa u kynja bynriew baroh, ïa ka ban shong halor ka khyndew baroh, haba u la pynthikna ïa ki aïom ba la buh, bad ïa ki pud ka jaka shong jong ki;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> ïa ka ban wad khnang ïa U Blei, ïoh lehse kumno kumno kin da ïoh tare nadien jong u, bad shem ïa u, la um long jngai na uwei pa uwei na ngi:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> namar, “ ‘ha u ngi im, bad ngi khih, bad ngi long de;’ “kumba kiba na ki nongthaw jingrwai jong phi hi ruh ki la ong, “ ‘Namar ngi long ruh ki khun ki ksiew jong u.’",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> “Te haba ngi long ki khun ki ksiew jong U Blei, ym dei ïa ngi ban mut ba Ka Jinglong Blei ka long syriem ïa ka ksiar lane ïa ka rupa lane ïa u maw, ba la pynlong dur da ka kam stad bad ka buit jong u briew.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U Blei, namar kata, u la leh kum bym khmih ïa ki aïom ka jingbymtip, hynrei, mynta, u hukum ïa ki briew baroh kylleng la kylleng ban kylla-ka-bamut;",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> naba u la buh ka sngi ha kaba un sa bishar ïa ka pyrthei ha ka hok da uta u briew ïa uba u la thung; shaphang kata, u la ai ka jingpynskhem ha ki briew baroh, da kaba u la pynmih pat ïa u na ki baïap.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te haba ki la ïohsngew shaphang ka jingmihpat ki baïap, don kiba la beiñ; hynrei, kiwei pat ki la ong, “Ngin ïasngew ïa me pat shaphang kane.”",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Kumta te u Paul u la leit noh napdeng jong ki.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hynrei, don ki rangbah kiba la ïasnoh lok ha u bad ki la ngeit; hapdeng kita don u Dionisios ruh, uwei u rangbah ka dorbar Ariopagos, bad ka kynthei kaba kyrteng “ka Damaris”, bad kiwei pat lem bad ki."
		},
		"18": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hadien kine kiei kiei ruh, u la kynriah noh na Athen bad u la wan sha Korinth.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Haba u la shem ïa uwei u Jiw uba kyrteng “u Akwila”, u briew uba na Pontos ha ka jaid, uba la wan dang shibit na Itali, bad ka Priskila ka tnga jong u, namar u Klaudios u la lah hukum ïa ki Jiw baroh ban kynriah noh na Rom, u la wan ha ki.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te namar ba u la long uba ju trei kajuh ka kam, u la ïaisah bad ki, bad ki la ïatrei; namar ha la ka kam ki la long ki nongthaw ïingjaiñ.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u la ju pyni nia ha ka synagog man la ka sngi Sabbaton, bad u la ju pyrshang pynkohnguh ïa ki Jiw ruh bad ïa ki Grik.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te mynba u Silas bad u Timothi ki la ïawan hiar na Makedonia, la pynshit rhem ïa u Paul da kata ka ktien, u da phla ha kita ki Jiw ba U Jisu u long uta U Khrist.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te haba ki la ïeng ïaleh pyrshah bad krenbeiñ, u la kynther noh ïa la ki jaiñ, bad u la ong ha ki, “Ka snam jong phi kan long halor ka khlieh jong phi hi! nga khuid: naduh mynta ngan leit sha ki Jentil.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te u la leit noh nangta, bad u la leit hapoh ka ïing jong uwei u briew uba kyrteng “u Titos Justos”, uba mane ïa U Blei, uba ka ïing jong u ka la long ha syndah kata ka synagog.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u Krispos, u nongsynshar ka synagog u la ngeit ha U Trai lem bad ka ïing jong u baroh; bun ruh na ki nong Korinth haba ki la ïohsngew, ki la ngeit, bad la pynbaptis ïa ki.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Ynda kumta, U Trai u la ong ha u Paul da ka jingithuhpaw mynmiet, “Wat sheptieng, hynrei, to kren, bad wat sngap jar ruh;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> naba nga long ryngkat bad me, bad ym don u briew u ban ïaleh ïa me ïa ka ban pynsniew ïa me; naba nga don bun briew ha kane ka nongbah.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te u la ïaishong shi snem hynriew bnai, u da hikai ïa ka ktien U Blei hapdeng jong ki.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te mynba u Gallio u la long lyngskor ha Akhaïa, ki Jiw da kawei ka jingmut ki la ïeng ïaleh pyrshah ïa u Paul, bad ki la wallam ïa u ha ka khet bishar,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> ki da ong, “Une u briew u pynkohnguh ïa ki briew ban mane ïa U Blei pyrshah ïa ka hukum.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, haba u Paul un sa ang la ka shyntur, u Gallio u la ong ha kita ki Jiw, “Lada shisha ka la long ka kam bymdei lane ka kam runar, A phi ki Jiw, kan da shongnia ba ngan shahshkor ïa phi:",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> hynrei, lada ka jingïasaid ka long shaphang ki ktien, bad ki kyrteng, bad ka hukum jong phi, khmih hi ma phi ïa kata; nga ngam mon ban long u nongbishar shaphang kine kiei kiei ruh.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad u la beh noh ïa ki na kata ka khet bishar.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ynda kumta, ki baroh ki la kem ïa u Sosthenis, u nongsynshar ka synagog, bad ki la shoh ïa u ha khmat kata ka khet bishar. U Gallio te um suidñiew ei ei ruh ïa kita kiei kiei.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Hynrei, u Paul ynda u la nang sah bun sngi hadien kane, u la ïabidai ïa ki parabangeit, bad u la leit noh nangta da ka lieng sha Syria lem bad ka Priskila bad u Akwila uba u la lah khi ïa la ka khlieh ha Kenkhria, namar u la bat ka kular.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te ki la wan sha Ephesos, bad u la iehnoh sah ïa ki hangta: hynrei, u hi haba u la leit rung shapoh ka synagog, u la pyni nia ha ki Jiw.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Haba ki te ki la ïakyrpad ïa u ban sah kham slem, u, um treh;",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> hynrei, u la bidai ïa ki, u da ong, “Ngan wan phai pat ha phi lada mon U Blei.” Kumta, u la mih noh da ka lieng na Ephesos.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Bad ynda u la lah hiar lieng ha Kaisaria, u la leit kiew bad u la khublei ïa kata ka balang, bad u la leit hiar sha Antiok.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te ynda u la lah shong katto katne hangta, u la leit noh, u da ïaid ïa ka ri Galatia bad Phrygia ter ter, u da pynskhem ïa ki synran baroh.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te uwei u Jiw uba kyrteng “u Apollos”, uba dei u nong Aleksandria, u briew uba pnah, u la wan sha Ephesos; bad u la long uba nang eh ha Ki Jingthoh Bakhuid.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Ïa une, la hikai ha ka lynti U Trai; bad namar ba u long uba shitrhem ha ka mynsiem, u la kren bad u la hikai biang biang ïa kiei kiei ruh shaphang U Jisu, u da sngewthuh tang ïa ka jingbaptis u Ïoannis.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Une te, u la sdang ban kren shlur ha ka synagog; hynrei, haba u Akwila bad ka Priskila ki la lah sngew ïa u, ki la ïakhot ïa u sha ki, bad ki la batai kham bniah ha u ïa ka lynti U Blei.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te haba u la kwah ban leit sha shiliang sha Akhaïa, kita ki parabangeit ki la pynshlur ïa u, bad ki la ïathoh sha ki synran ban pdiang ïa u; bad ynda u la lah poi, u la ïarap lem shibun ïa kita kiba da ka jingaiei U Blei ki la lah ngeit:",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> namar da ka borbah u la pynduh nia khoit ïa ki Jiw ha kaba paw ruh, u da pyni na Ki Jingthoh ba U Jisu u long uta U Khrist."
		},
		"19": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia mynba u Apollos u don ha Korinth, ba u Paul, ynda u la leit lyngba ïa kita ki phang kiba shaneng, u la wan sha Ephesos, bad u la shem ïa kiba long synran:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> bad u la kylli ïa ki, “Phi la pdiang ne em ïa U Mynsiem Bakhuid mynba phi la ngeit?” Bad ki la ïathuh ha u, “Em, ngim shym la ïohsngew wat lada la don ne em U Mynsiem Bakhuid.”",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ynda kumta, u la kylli ïa ki, “Ha kaei te la pynbaptis ïa phi?” Ki te ki la ïathuh, “Ha ka jingbaptis u Ïoannis.”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te u Paul u la ong, “U Ïoannis u la pynbaptis da ka jingbaptis ka jingkylla-ka-bamut, u da ong ha u paidbah ba ki dei ban ngeit ha uta u ban sa wan hadien jong u, kata, ha U Jisu.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Ynda ki la ïohsngew te ïa kane, la pynbaptis ïa ki ha ka kyrteng U Trai Jisu.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ynda u Paul u la lah buh ïa la ki kti ha ki, U Mynsiem Bakhuid u la wan ha ki, bad ki la kren da ki thylliej bad ki la ïathuhlypa.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ki la don baroh kumba khat-ar ngut ki rangbah.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te u la leit rung shapoh ka synagog, bad u la kren shlur jin lai bnai, u da pyni nia bad pynkohnguh shaphang kiei kiei ki jong ka hima U Blei.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, mynba don kiba la pyneh ïa lade, bad kim ngeit, ki da kren sniew ïa kata “ka Lynti” ha khmat u paidbah, u la kynriah noh na ki, bad u la pynkyrpang ïa ki synran, ha la ka sngi u da pyni nia ha ka skul u Turannos.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Bad kane ka la long ruh haduh ar snem; kumta, kita baroh kiba shong ha Asia ki la ïohsngew ïa ka ktien U Trai, ki Jiw ruh bad ki Grik.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te U Blei u la ju leh ki kambah kiba kham khyllah da ki kti u Paul;",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> kat haduh ba ki la leit lam ha ki bapang ïa ki rumar lane ki jaiñ kyrshah na ka met jong u, ki jingpang te ki la jah noh na ki, bad ki mynsiem bymman ki la mih noh.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, don kiba na ki Jiw kiba shang kylleng, ki nongbeh ksuid, ki la leh mynkhot halor kita kiba shong ki mynsiem bymman ïa ka kyrteng U Trai Jisu, ki da ong, “Nga pynsmai ïa phi ha uta U Jisu, ïa uba u Paul u ïalap.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te la don hynñiew ngut ki khun uwei u Skeba, u Jiw, u rangbah lyngdoh ruh, kiba la leh ïa kane.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te uta u mynsiem bymman u la ïathuh bad u la ong ha ki, “Ïa U Jisu nga ithuh, bad ïa u Paul nga ithuh, hynrei, ma phi, phi long kiei?”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te uta u briew, ha uba la shong uta u mynsiem bymman u la sied ha ki, bad u la leh jubor ïa ki, bad u la jop ïa ki, katba ki la ïaphet ïap noh na kata ka ïing lyngboit bad ba la mong.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te baroh ki la bna ïa kane, bad Jiw bad Grik, kiba shong ha Ephesos; ka jingsheptieng te ka la kem ïa ki baroh, bad ïa ka kyrteng U Trai Jisu la pynkhraw.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Shibun te na kita kiba la lah ngeit ki la ïawan, ki da ïaphla bad ki da ïathuh ïa la ki jingleh.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Bad ym khyndiat na kita kiba ju leh ïa ki jingleh myntor, ki la ïawallam lang ïa la ki kitab, bad ki la ïathang ïa ki ha khmat ki briew baroh: te ki la ïakheiñ lang ïa ka dor jong ki, bad ki la shem ba ka long sanphew hajar ki sbai rupa.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Kumta, da ka bor bah eh ka ktien jong U Trai ka la roi, bad ka la jop ruh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Te ynda la dep kine kiei kiei ruh, u Paul u la thmu ha la ka mynsiem, ynda u la leit lyngba ïa ka Makedonia bad ka Akhaïa, ban leit sha Jerusalem, u da ong, “Ynda nga la poi hangta, ka dei ïa nga ban ïohi ïa ka Rom ruh.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ynda u la phah noh sha Makedonia ar ngut na kita kiba ju synran ïa u, u Timothi bad u Erastos, u hi u la nang sah ha Asia katto katne.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Mynkata te, la mih ka jingkhihwin ym khyndiat shaphang kata Ka Lynti.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Namar uwei u briew uba kyrteng “u Dimetrios” u bania, uba ju thaw da ka rupa ïa ki dur ïingmane jong ka Diana, u la ju pynïoh kam ym khyndiat ïa ki nongtrei;",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> ïa kiba u la pynïalum lang, lem bad ki para nongtrei kiba trei kajuh ka kam, bad u la ong, “Ko rangbah, phi tip ba na kane ka kam ka long ka spah jong ngi.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Bad phi ïohi bad phi ïohsngew ruh, ba ym tang ha Ephesos hi, hynrei, la jan ha baroh kawei ka Asia, une u Paul u la pynkohnguh bad u la pynkylla noh ïa u paidbah babun, u da ong, ba kim long ki blei kita kiba la thaw da ki kti;",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> kumta, ym tang ba la don jingma ba kane ka kam jong ngi kan kylla kaba ibeiñ, hynrei, ba yn ym ñiew ei ei ruh em ïa ka ïingmane ka Diana ruh, kane ka blei kaba khraw, bad yn pynduh noh ruh ïa ka jinglong khraw jong ka, ïa kaba ka Asia baroh kawei bad ka pyrthei ki ïamane.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te haba ki la ïohsngew ïa kane, la pyndap ïa ki da ka jingbitar, bad ki la ïapyrta noh, ki da ong, “Kaba khraw ka Diana ka jong ki Ephesos!”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te la pyndap ïa kata ka nongbah da ka jingkhihwin; haba ki la kem ñiat te ïa u Gaïos bad ïa u Aristarkhos, kiba na Makedonia, ki para ba ïaleit lem bad u Paul, ki la ïaphet kyrthep ruh da kawei ka jingmut sha ka ïing seng ka shnong.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te mynba u Paul u da thew ban leit hapoh sha uta u paidbah, ki synran kim shah ïa u.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te don ruh ki rangbah Asia, ba ki long ki lok jong u, ki la ïaphah ha u, bad ki la ïakyrpad ïa u ban ym nud leit ha kata ka ïing seng ka shnong.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Hangta te don kiba la ïapyrta ïa kane, bad kiwei pat ïa kata: namar la pynkulmar ïa uta u paidbah; te kiba kham bun kim shym tip na ka bynta aïu ki la ïawan lang.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te ki la ïa-pynmih na uta u paidbah ïa u Aleksander, ki Jiw ki da ïakyntuit sha khmat ïa u. Te u Aleksander u la kaweh da ka kti bad u la mut ban ïasaid-da ha uta u paidbah.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Hynrei, ynda ki la tip ba u long u Jiw, la mih buk kawei ka jingpyrta na ki baroh, jin haduh ar kynta, ki da ïapyrta jam, “Kaba khraw ka Diana ka jong ki Ephesos!”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te ynda u nongthoh ka shnong u la lah pynjar jar ïa uta u paidbah, u la ong, “Ko phi ki rangbah Ephesos, uno u briew u bymtip ba kane ka nongbah ki Ephesos ka long ka nongsumar ïa ka templ jong ka Diana kaba khraw, bad ïa kata ka durblei kaba la hap na u Jupiter?",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Namar kata te, haba ïa kine kiei kiei ruh ym lah ban len, ka dei ba phin long jar jar, bad ban ym leh thurmur ei ei ruh em.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Namar phi la wallam hangne ïa kine ki rangbah, ki bymlong kiba tuh kyntang, lymne kiba ïakrenbeiñ ïa ka blei jong ngi.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Namar kata, lada u Dimetrios, bad kita ki nongtrei lem bad u, ki ïadon ka jingmudui pyrshah ïano ïano ruh, ki don ki ïing kashari, ki don ruh ki lyngskor; to kin ïatian bishar paralok hi.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Hynrei, lada phi ïawad ei ei ruh shaphang kiwei pat ki kam, yn pyndep ïa ki ha ka jingïaseng kaba katba kum ka aiñ.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Namar la dei sa ban mudui ïa ngi namar ka jingkhihwin ha kane ka sngi, ba ka long kaba khlem daw, bad ngin ym lah ban sei nia na ka bynta kane ka jingïalang bakhynwin.”",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Te ynda u la lah kren kumne, u la pynpra noh ïa kata ka jingïaseng."
		},
		"20": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te haba la wai noh kata ka jingkhihwin, ynda u Paul u la lah phah khot ïa ki synran, bad ba u la lah sneng ïa ki, u la khublei ïa ki bad u la mih noh ban leit sha Makedonia.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ynda u la lah leit lyngba ïa kita ki phang, bad ba u la lah ai jingsneng shibun ïa ki, u la wan sha ka ri Grik.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Bad haba u la shong hangta lai bnai, bad ba la pynlong ka jingthap ïa u da ki Jiw, haba un sa mih noh da ka lieng sha Syria, u la kut jingmut ïa ka ban leit phai pat lyngba ïa ka Makedonia.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te la leit lem bad u haduh Asia, u Sopater u nong Beria, u khun u Pyrrhos; bad na ki Thessaloni, u Aristarkhos bad u Sekundos; bad u Gaïos u nong Derbi, bad u Timothi: bad na Asia, u Tukhikos bad u Trophimos.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, kine ki la lah leit sha shuwa, bad ki ïa-ap ïa ngi ha Troas.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ngi, ngi la ïaleit mih noh da ka lieng na Philipi, hadien ki sngi U Kpu Bakhlem Thiat, bad ngi la wan poi ha ki sha Troas ha ki san sngi; hangta ngi la shong hynñiew sngi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ha ka sngi nyngkong ka taïew, mynba ngi la wan ïaseng ïa ka ban kdiah kpu, u Paul u la ïalap ha ki, ba un sa leit noh lashai; te u la pynslem ïa la ka jingïalap haduh shiteng synñia.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te la don shibun ki sharak ha kata ka kamra ba sha jrong, ha kaba ngi la ïaseng.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te uwei u samla uba kyrteng “u Eutikhos” uba la shong ha ka jingkhang ïit, ba la shoh samthiah lyngngai ïa u, katba u Paul u kham ïalap slem, u la kyllon na kata kaba ïohthiah, bad u la hap arsut na ka balai mala bad la rah ïap ïa u.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> U Paul te ynda u la leit hiar u la dem halor jong u, bad haba u la kynthup ïa u, u la ong, “Phi wat khuslai, namar ka mynsiem jong u ka don ha u.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te haba u la lah leit kiew pat, bad ba u la lah kdiah ïa uta u kpu, bad ba u la lah bam, bad ba u la lah ïakren bad ki kham slem ha ban da shai byrngut, kumta u la leit noh.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad ki la ïawallam im ïa uta u samla, te la pyntngen ïa ki ym khyndiat.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ngi te haba ngi la leit sha shuwa ha kata ka lieng, ngi la ïa-pynmih noh sha Assos, nangta ngi da ïamut ban kyntiew halor lieng ïa u Paul, namar kumta u la lah ïabuh, u da sngewbha hi ban ïaid ryngkew.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba u la ïashem bad ngi ha Assos, ngi la kyntiew lieng ïa u, bad ngi la ïawan poi sha Mitylini.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nangta ruh ynda ngi la ïamih noh da ka lieng, ngi la wan kum lashai ha pyrshah ka Khios; bad ha kawei pat ka sngi, ngi la ïapoi ryngkew ha Samos, bad ha ka sngi kaba bud ngi la ïawan poi sha Miletos.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Namar u Paul u la lah thmu bad ïaid kiar ïa ka Ephesos, ba un ym pynslem shuh ha Asia; namar u la pynkloi lada lah ïa ka ban don ha Jerusalem ha ka sngi Pentekost.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te na Miletos haba u la phah sha Ephesos, u la khot ha u ïa ki tymmen basan jong kata ka balang.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te ynda ki la lah poi ha u, u la ong ha ki, “Phi hi phi tip, naduh ka sngi ka banyngkong ba nga la wan sha Asia, kumno nga la leh ïa lade hapdeng jong phi baroh shi katta,",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> ba nga da shakri ïa U Trai da ka jingsngewrit baroh, bad ha ki jingjaw ummat bad ki jingtynjuh kiba la jia long ha nga da ki jingthap jong ki Jiw;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> kumno ba ngam shym la pep ban ïathuh ha phi ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba pynmyntoi, bad ban hikai ïa phi ha kaba paw, bad ha ki ïing ki ïing,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> da kaba phla ha ki Jiw bad ha ki Grik de ïa ka jingkylla-ka-bamut sha U Blei, bad ïa ka jingngeit ha U Jisu Khrist uba U Trai jong ngi.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Mynta te, ha khmih, nga, nga leit noh ba la khum ha ka mynsiem sha Jerusalem, ngam da tip ïa kiei kiei ruh ki ban jia ïa nga hangta;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> hynrei, tang ba U Mynsiem Bakhuid u phla shai ha nga ha kawei pa kawei ka shnong, u da ong, ba ki jingkhum bad ki jingshitom ki ïa-ap ïa nga.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Hynrei, nga kheiñduh ïa la ka jingim, bad ngam ñiewkor shuh ïa ka, ba kumta ngan ïoh pyndep noh ïa ka jingphet jong nga, bad ïa kata ka kam U Blei kaba nga la ïoh na U Trai Jisu, ïa ka ban phla ïa ka gospel ka jingaiei U Blei.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Mynta ruh, ha khmih nga tip ba phi baroh, hapdeng kiba nga la leit kylleng da kaba ïalap ïa kata ka hima, phin ym ïohi shuh ïa ka khmat jong nga.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Naba kumta, nga phla ha phi ha kane ka sngi, ba nga khuid na ka snam ki briew baroh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Namar ngam shym la pep ban ïathuh ha phi ïa ka mon ka jong U Blei baroh.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> To sumar shaphang ïa lade bad shaphang kata ka kynhun baroh, ha kaba U Mynsiem Bakhuid u la pynlong ïa phi ki nongsharai, ban bsa ïa ka balang U Blei, ïa kaba u la thied da ka snam jong u hi.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Nga tip ba hadien kane ka jingleit noh jong nga, ki suri barunar sat kin ïabsut hapdeng jong phi, kim da isynei ïa kata ka kynhun;",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> bad napdeng jong phi hi ruh, ki rangbah kin ïamih kiba ïalap ïa kiei kiei ruh kiba bakla, ïa ka ban ring pah ïa ki synran hadien jong ki.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Naba kumta, to ïasharai, da kynmaw ruh ba jin lai snem, mynmiet bad mynsngi, ngam shym la wai noh ban sneng ïa uwei pa uwei na phi da ki jingjaw ummat.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te mynta, nga aiti noh ïa phi ha U Blei, bad ha ka ktien ka jingaiei jong u, uba lah ban ïaitei ïa phi, bad ban ai ha phi ka bynta hapdeng kita baroh ïa kiba la pynkhuid.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Ka rupa, lane ka ksiar, lane ka jaiñkup jongno jongno ruh, ngam shym la ikwah;",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> phi hi phi tip ba kine ki kti ki la trei ban pyndap ïa ki jingdonkam jong nga, bad ki jong kita kiba don lem bad nga.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Ha kiei kiei baroh, nga la pyni rukom ha phi, ba da kaba trei minot kumta, ka dei ban shan bor ïa ki batlot, bad ban kynmaw ïa ki ktien U Trai Jisu ba u hi u la ong, ‘Ka kham suk ban ai ban ïa kaba pdiang.’ ”",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Te ynda u la lah kren kumne, u la dem la ki khohsiew, bad u la duwai lem bad ki baroh.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te ki la ïam shibun baroh, bad ki la dem ha ka ryndang u Paul, bad ki la ïadoh ïa u,",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> ki da ïasngewsih kham tam eh namar kata ka ktien ïa kaba u la lah ong, ba kin ym ïoh khmih shuh ïa ka khmat jong u. Te ki la ïaleit on lynti ïa u sha kata ka lieng."
		},
		"21": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ka la jia te, hadien ba ngi la ïakhlad noh na ki, bad ba la lah pynmih noh ïa ka lieng, ngi la ïawan poi da ka lynti kaba beit sha Kos, bad kum lashai sha Rhodos, nangta ruh sha Patara.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Haba ngi la shem te ïa ka lieng kaba leit sha shiliang sha Phoiniki, ngi la leit kiew ha ka bad ngi la ïa-pynmih noh.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te ynda la lah paw ka Kypros ha ngi, bad ba ngi la iehnoh ïa ka sha kadiang, ngi la nang leit sha Syria, bad ngi la kiew ryngkew ha Tyros; namar hangta kata ka lieng kan sa sei noh ïa ka jingkit jong ka.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te ynda ngi la shem ïa ki synran, ngi la sah hangta hynñiew sngi; te kine ki la ïa-ong ha u Paul da U Mynsiem, ba un ym leit kiew sha Jerusalem.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Hynrei, haba ngi la lah pyndep noh ïa kita ki sngi, ngi la ïamih noh bad ngi la nang leit la ka lynti; te ki baroh lem bad ki tnga bad ki khun, ki la ïaleit on lynti ïa ngi haduh bar shnong; te ynda ngi la ïadem la ki khohsiew harud duriaw ngi la ïaduwai.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Ynda ngi la lah ïakhublei paralok hi, ngi la ïaleit kiew noh sha kata ka lieng; ki te ki la ïaleit phai pat sha la ïing.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Ngi te, da kaba pyndep noh ïa la ka jingleit da ka lieng na Tyros, ngi la poi ha Ptolemais; bad haba ngi la ïakhublei ïa ki parabangeit, ngi la sah shi sngi bad ki.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Te kum lashai ynda ngi la leit noh, ngi la ïapoi sha Kaisaria: bad haba ngi la ïarung hapoh ka ïing u Philip u nongïathuhkhana, uba la long uwei na kita ki hynñiew ngut, ngi la ïasah bad u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Une te, u la don saw ngut ki khun kynthei, ki theisotti, kiba ïathuhlypa.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te haba ngi la ïaisah hangta bun sngi, la wan hiar na Judia uwei u nongïathuhlypa, uba kyrteng “u Agabos”.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te ynda u la wan ha ngi, bad ba u la shim ïa ka panpoh jong u Paul, u la khum ïa la ki jong ki kti bad kjat, bad u la ong, “Kumne u ong U Mynsiem Bakhuid: ‘Ïa uta u briew uba dei trai kane ka panpoh, kita ki Jiw kin ïakhum kumne ha Jerusalem, bad kin ïa-ai noh ha ki kti ki Jentil.’ ”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te mynba ngi la ïohsngew ïa kine kiei kiei ruh, ma ngi bad kita kiba shong sah hangta, ngi la ïakyrpad ïa u ban ym leit kiew sha Jerusalem.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Hynrei, u Paul u la ïathuh, “Phin lei da kaba ïam bad da kaba pynpait ïa ka dohnud jong nga? Namar nga, nga la kloi ym tang ban shah khum, hynrei, ban ïap ruh ha Jerusalem na ka bynta ka kyrteng U Trai Jisu.”",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te haba um kohnguh, ngi la keiñ noh, da kaba ong, “Ïa ka mon U Trai yn leh.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te hadien kita ki sngi, ngi la ïakhreh la ki jingkit jingbah, bad ngi la ïaleit kiew noh sha Jerusalem.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> La don ruh ki synran na Kaisaria kiba la ïawan ryngkat bad ngi, ki da wallam ryngkat bad ki, ïa uwei u Mnason na Kypros, u synran barim, bad uba ngi la dei ban shong basa.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te mynba ngi la lah poi ha Jerusalem, ki parabangeit da kaba kmen ki la ïa-pdiang ïa ngi.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Ha ka sngi kaba bud te, u Paul u la leit rung lem bad ngi sha u Jakob; te ki tymmen basan baroh ki la ïadon hangta.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te haba u la lah ïakhublei ïa ki, u la ïathuh kawei pa kawei ïa kita kiei kiei kiba U Blei u la lah leh hapdeng ki Jentil da ka jingtrei jong u.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Ki te haba ki la ïohsngew, ki la pyndonburom ïa U Blei, bad ki la ong ha u, “Me ïohi, ko para, katno phew hajar ki Jiw ki don kiba la ngeit, baroh ruh ki ïalong kiba sngew-shitrhem shaphang ka hukum.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Bad la pynbna ha ki shaphang jong me, ba me hikai ïa ki Jiw baroh kiba hapdeng ki Jentil, ïa ka ban lyndet ïa u Moses; me da hukum ïa ki, ban ym otsher ïa la ki khun, lymne ban ïaid katba kum ki niam ki rukom.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Namar kata te, kumno? Khlem pep kin ïohsngew ba me la wan.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar kata, to men leh ïa kane kaba ngi ong ïa me. Don bad ngi saw ngut ki rangbah kiba la teh ïa lade da ka jingsmai;",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> shim ïa kine, bad pynkhuid ïa lade lem bad ki, bad men siew ruh na ka bynta jong ki, ba kin ïoh khi ïa la ki khlieh; kumta baroh kin ïoh tip, ba kim long ei ei ruh em kita kiei kiei kiba ki la ïabna shaphang jong me, hynrei, ba me hi ruh me ïaid beit, da kaba sumar ïa ka hukum.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, shaphang kita ki Jentil kiba la ngeit, ngi la ïathoh, ba ngi la ïarai ba kin kyndiah noh na kita kiei kiei ba la kñia ïa ki bleithaw, bad na ka snam, bad na kaba la khyrwait, bad na kaba klim.”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hangta u Paul u la shim ïa kita ki briew; te kum lashai haba u la pynkhuid ïa lade lem bad ki, u la leit shapoh ka templ, u da pynbna ïa ka jingpyndep ïa ki sngi ka jingpynkhuid, tad ynda la ainguh ïa ka jingainguh na ka bynta uwei pa uwei na ki.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te hamar ban sa kut kita ki hynñiew sngi, kita ki Jiw na Asia, haba ki la ïohi ïa u ha ka templ, ki la ïa-pynkynroi buk ïa uta u paidbah baroh, bad ki la kem ïa u,",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> ki da ïapyrta noh, “Ko rangbah Israel, to ïarap kloi! Dei une u briew uba hikai kylleng la kylleng ruh ïa ki briew baroh ban ïaleh ïa u paidlang, bad ïa ka hukum, bad ïa kane ka jaka! Bad nalor kata, u la ïalam ïa ki Grik ruh hapoh ka templ, bad u la pyntngit ïa kane ka jaka bakyntang!”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> (Namar ki la lah ïohi mynshuwa ha kata ka nongbah lem bad u ïa u Trophimos u nong Ephesos, ïa uba ki la ïatharai ba u Paul u la lah ïalam hapoh ka templ.)",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ka la khihwin jlang baroh kawei ka nongbah. Bad u paidbah u la ïaphet kyrthep lang, bad haba ki la kem ïa u Paul, ki la ïaring noh ïa u shabar ka templ; bad kumne kumne la khang noh ïa ki jingkhang.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te katba ki dang pyrshang ban pynïap noh ïa u, la wan ka khubor ha u rangbah shihajar jong ka kynhun ki shipai, ba la khihwin jlang baroh kawei ka Jerusalem.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Kumne kumne ruh, u la shim ïa ki shipai bad ïa ki rangbah shispah, bad u la phet arsut sha ki, ki te haba ki la ïohi ïa uta u rangbah shihajar bad ïa ki shipai, ki la sangeh na kaba shoh ïa u Paul.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te u rangbah shihajar u la wan hajan, bad u la kem ïa u; bad u la hukum ban khum ïa u da ki ar tylli ki kynjri, bad u la ïakylli u long uei, bad aïu ba u la leh.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Te kiwei ki la ïapyrta ïa kane, kiwei pat ïa kata, hapdeng uta u paidbah, te haba um lah ban tip ïa kaba shisha namar kata ka jingkhihwin, u la hukum ban ïalam noh ïa u shapoh ka kut.",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Mynba u la poi te ha ki kyrdon, ka la jia ban bah ïa u da kita ki shipai, namar ka jingleh-jubor jong uta u paidbah,",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> namar u paidbah byllien jong uta u paidlang u la bud nadien, u da ïapyrta, “To da shim duh noh ïa u!”",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te ha ban sa ïalam ïa u Paul shapoh kata ka kut, u la kylli ïa uta u rangbah shihajar, “Ka bit ne em ïa nga ban ong ei ei ha me?” U te u la kylli, “Me nang kren Grik!",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Me mem long shisha uta u nong Ijipt, uba mynshuwa kine ki sngi u la shet ïa kita ki saw hajar ki dakaid bad u la ïalam noh sha ka ri khlaw?”",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> U Paul u la ïathuh te, “Nga, nga long u Jiw uba na Tarsos ha Kilikia, u trai-shnong ka nongbah kaba donnam. Nga kyrpad ïa me, to shah ïa nga ban kren ha u paidbah.”",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Te ynda u la lah shah ïa u, u Paul u da ïeng ha kita ki kyrdon, u la kaweh ha uta u paidlang; te ynda la long ka jingsngap jar jak, u la kren ha ki ha ka ktien Hebru kumne:"
		},
		"22": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> “Ko ki para, bad ko ki kpa, to sngew ïa ka jingïasaid-da jong nga mynta ha phi.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te haba ki la ïohsngew ba u la kren ha ki ha ka ktien Hebru, ki la kham sngap jar; bad u la ong,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Nga, nga long u Jiw, ïa uba la kha ha Tarsos ha Kilikia, hynrei, la pynnang ïa nga ha kane ka nongbah ha kjat u Gamaliel, ba la hikai ïa nga kat ka rukom babniah jong ka hukum ki kpa tymmen, nga da sngew-shitrhem shaphang U Blei, kat kumba phi baroh phi long ha kane ka sngi.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Bad nga uba la pynshitombeiñ ïa kane ‘Ka Lynti’ haduh ka jingïap, da kaba khum bad da kaba ai noh sha ki ïing byndi ïa ki briew shynrang bad kynthei,",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> kumba uta u rangbah lyngdoh ruh, bad kata ka jingïaseng tymmen basan baroh, kin ïaphla shaphang jong nga. Na ki ruh, nga la ïoh ki shithi ha ki parabangeit, bad nga la leit noh sha Damaskos, ban sa wallam ruh ïa kita kiba don hangta kiba la khum sha Jerusalem, ïa ka ban ïoh pynshitom ïa ki.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> “Te ka la jia, katba nga nang leit lynti bad nang poi hajan Damaskos, hamar shiteng sngi, ba kyndit kyndit la tyngshaiñ lep na bneng ka jingshai bakhraw baroh sawdong ïa nga.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te nga la kyllon kram ha khyndew, bad nga la ïohsngew ka ktien ba ong ha nga, ‘Saul, Saul, balei me pynshitombeiñ ïa nga?’",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Nga te nga la ïathuh, ‘Me long uei, A Trai?’ Te u la ïathuh ha nga, ‘Nga long U Jisu uba na Nasaret, ïa uba pynshitombeiñ ma me.’",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Kita ruh kiba don lem bad nga ki la ïohi shisha ïa kata ka jingshai, hynrei, kim shym la ïohsngew ïa kata ka ktien jong uta uba la kren bad nga.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te nga la ong, ‘Aïu ngan leh, A Trai?’ Ynda kumta, U Trai u la ïathuh ha nga, ‘To ïeng joit, to khie leit ruh sha Damaskos; bad yn ïathuh ha me hangta shaphang kiei kiei baroh kiba la buh khnang ïa me ban leh.’",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te haba ngam imat namar ka jingtyngshaiñ jong kata ka jingshai, da kaba btin na ka kti ïa nga da kita kiba ïadon bad nga, nga la poi ha Damaskos.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Te uwei u Ananias, u briew uba riewblei kat Ka Hukum, ïa uba la ïaphla babha da ki Jiw baroh kiba ïashong hangta,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> haba u la wan ha nga, bad u la ïeng hajan, u la ong ha nga, ‘Ko Saul, u para jong nga, to men ïoh peit pat!’ Nga te ha kata kajuh ka por nga la khmied sha u.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> U la ong ruh, ‘U Blei ki kpa jong ngi u la thung ïa me ban tip ïa ka mon jong u, bad ban ïohi ïa uta U Bahok, bad ban ïohsngew ïa ka ktien na ka shyntur jong u.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Naba men ïoh long u nongphla na ka bynta jong u ha ki briew baroh, shaphang kita kiba me la ïohi bad ba me la ïohsngew.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Mynta te, balei me pyntud? To ïeng, to shah ba yn pynbaptis ïa me bad sait noh ïa ki pop jong me, da kaba khot kyrpad ïa ka kyrteng jong u.’",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> “Te ka la jia, mynba nga la lah wan phai pat sha Jerusalem, bad katba nga dang duwai ha ka templ, ba nga la long ha ka jinglong rngai,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> bad nga la ïohi ïa u, ba u ong ha nga, ‘To pynkloi noh me, bad khie leit noh kyrkieh na Jerusalem, naba kin ym pdiang ïa ka jingphla jong me shaphang jong nga.’",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Nga te nga la ïathuh, ‘A Trai, ki hi ki ïatip ba nga la ju set byndi bad sympat ha ki synagog baroh ïa kita kiba la ngeit ha me,",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> bad mynba la pynmih noh ïa ka snam u Stephan u nongphla jong me, nga hi ruh nga la ïeng hajan, bad nga da kohnguh, bad nga da sumar ïa ki jaiñ jong kita kiba ïa-pynïap noh ïa u!’",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> U la ong te ha nga, ‘To khie leit noh; naba nga ngan phah noh ïa me jngai nangne sha ki Jentil.’ ”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Te ki la ïasngap ïa u haduh kane ka ktien. Ynda kumta, ki la ïa-pynjam noh ïa ka ktien jong ki, bad ki la ïa-ong, “To da shim duh noh kum ïa uta na ka khyndew! Kam dei ïa u ban ïoh im!”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba ki dang ïapyrta jam noh, bad ki bred noh bak ïa la ki jaiñkup, bad ki kynting pui pui sha ka suiñ,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> uta u rangbah shihajar u la hukum ban ïalam ïa u shapoh kata ka kut, u da hukum ban kylli ïit ïa u da ki jingsympat, ba un ïoh tip na kano ka daw ba ki la ïapyrta kumta pyrshah ïa u.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te ynda ki la lah khum ïa u da ki 'sai snieh, u Paul u la ong ha uta u rangbah shispah uba la ïeng hajan, “Ka dei ne em ïa phi ban sympat ïa u briew uba long u trai-shnong Rom, khlem da bishar ruh?”",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Te mynba uta u rangbah shispah u la lah ïohsngew ïa kata, u la leit ïathuh ha uta u rangbah shihajar, u da ong, “To khmih men sa leh aïu? Namar une u briew u long u trai-shnong Rom.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te uta u rangbah shihajar u la wan bad u la ong ha u, “To ïathuh ha nga, me long shisha u trai-shnong Rom?” U la ïathuh te, “Ho-oid.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te uta u rangbah shihajar u la ïathuh, “Da ka spah kaba bun nga la ïoh thied ïa kane ka jinglong trai-shnong.” U Paul u la ong, “Hynrei, ïa nga la kha kumta.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Kumne kumne ruh, namar kata, ki la kynriah noh na u kita ki ban sa tohkit ïa u; bad uta u rangbah shihajar ruh u la sheptieng haba u la tip ba u long u trai-shnong Rom, bad naba u la lah khum ïa u.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te kum lashai, ba u da kwah ban tip thikna namar balei la mudui ïa u da kita ki Jiw, u la loit noh ïa u na kita ki jingkhum, bad u la hukum ïa ki rangbah lyngdoh, bad ïa kata ka dorbar baroh ban ïawan lang; te haba u la ïalam arsut ïa u Paul, u la pynïeng ïa u ha khmat jong ki."
		},
		"23": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te u Paul haba u la khmih shaiñ ha kata ka dorbar u la ong, “Ko ki para, nga la ïaid beit ha ka jingïatiplem babha baroh ha khmat U Blei haduh kane ka sngi.”",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad u Ananias u rangbah lyngdoh, u la hukum ïa kita kiba la ïeng hajan jong u ban thab ïa u na ka shyntur.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Ynda kumta, u Paul u la ong ha u, “U Blei un sa shoh ïa me, me ka kynroh ba la pynlieh! kumta du shong bishar ma me ïa nga kat ka hukum, pynban, da kaba pynkheiñ ïa ka hukum me phah thab ïa nga?”",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te kita kiba la ïeng hajan ki la ïa-ong, “Me krenbeiñ ïa u rangbah lyngdoh jong U Blei?”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> U Paul u la ong, “Ngam shym la tip, ko ki para, ba u long u rangbah lyngdoh: naba la thoh, ‘Men ym kren sniew ïa u nongsynshar u paidlang jong me.’ ”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, haba u Paul u la ïohi ba kawei ka bynta ka long ki Saddusi, bad kawei pat ki Pharisi, u la pyrta noh ha ka dorbar, “Ko ki para, nga, nga long u Pharisi, u khun ki Pharisi; shaphang ka jingkyrmen bad ka jingmihpat ki baïap la bishar ïa nga.”",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ynda u la lah ong ïa kane, la mih buk ka jingïasaid hapdeng kita ki Pharisi bad kita ki Saddusi; bad uta u paidbah u la ïakad ar liang.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Namar ki Saddusi ki ïa-ong ba ym don ka jingmihpat, lymne ki angel, lymne ki mynsiem; hynrei, ki Pharisi ki ïaphla ïa ki baroh ar.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te la mih ka jingkhynwin jlang; bad haba la ïaïeng joit ki nongthoh kiba na ka liang ki Pharisi, ki la ïa-pyneh noh, ki da ong, “Ngim shem ka basniew ei ei ruh ha une u briew; hynrei, yn leh kumno lada ka mynsiem ka la kren ha u, lane u angel?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te mynba la mih ka jingïasaid khynwin bakhraw, uta u rangbah shihajar ba u la sngewsheptieng ïoh kin bthat lyngkhot lyngkhot ïa u Paul, u la hukum ïa ki shipai ban leit hiar noh bad ban knieh kynthet ïa u napdeng jong ki, bad ban wallam noh ïa u shapoh kata ka kut.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te kum lashai mynmiet, U Trai u la ïeng hajan jong u, u la ong ruh, “To sngewshlur! Namar kumba me la phla shaphang jong nga ha Jerusalem, kumjuh ka dei ïa me ban phla ha Rom ruh.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te ynda la mih ka sngi, kiba na ki Jiw haba ki la ïasylla lang, ki la ïateh jingsmai paralok hi ki da ïakut ban ym bam lymne dih haduh ba kin da ïoh pynïap noh ïa u Paul.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Ki la ïadon sawphew ngut tam kiba la ïa-pynlong ïa kane ka jingïashet.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Haba ki la ïawan ha ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki tymmen basan, ki la ïa-ong, “Ngi la ïateh paralok da ka jingtim bakhraw, ban ym mad ei ei ruh haduh ba ngin da ïoh pynïap noh ïa u Paul.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Mynta, namar kata, ma phi lem bad ka dorbar to phin ïaphah ktien ha uta u rangbah shihajar, ba un ïalam noh arsut ïa u ha phi, kumba phin sa bishar kham bniah ïa ka kam jong u. Ngi te katba um pat poi hajan, ngi la ïakloi lypa ïa ka ban pynïap noh ïa u.”",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, mynba u khun ka para u Paul u la ïohsngew shaphang kata ka jingïa-ap thap, u la wan bad u la leit rung sha kata ka kut, bad u la ïathuh ha u Paul.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> U Paul te haba u la khot ha u ïa uwei na kita ki rangbah shispah, u la ong, “To ïalam ïa une u samla ha u rangbah shihajar, namar u don ei ei ban ïathuh ha u.”",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Kumta, u la shim ïa u bad u la ïalam ïa u ha uta u rangbah shihajar bad u la ong, “U Paul u nongsah byndi, haba u la khot ha u ïa nga, u la kyrpad ïa nga ban ïalam ïa une u samla ha me, uba don ei ei ban ïathuh ha me.”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Te uta u rangbah shihajar haba u la shim ïa u na ka kti bad haba ki la ïaleit kyrpang, u la kylli ïa u jar jar, “Me don aïu ban ïathuh ha nga?”",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te u la ïathuh, “Ki Jiw ki la ïakut lem ban kyrpad ïa me ban ïalam arsut ïa u Paul lashai sha ka dorbar, kumba men sa kylli kham bniah shaphang jong u.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Me, namar kata, wat kohnguh ïa ki; namar don sawphew ngut tam ki rangbah na ki kiba ïa-ap thap ïa u, kiba la ïateh paralok da ka jingsmai ban ym bam lymne dih haduh ba kin da ïoh pynïap noh ïa u: mynta ruh ki la ïakloi lypa, ba ki da ïakhmih lynti ïa kata ka jingkular na me.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, uta u rangbah shihajar u la pyllait noh ïa uta u samla, u da hukum skhem ïa u ban ym ïathuh hano hano ruh ba u la lah pynpaw ïa kine kiei kiei ha u.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te haba u la khot ha u ar ngut na ki rangbah shispah u la ong, “Khreh arspah ngut ki shipai ba kin leit haduh Kaisaria, bad hynñiewphew ngut ki shipai shong kulai, bad arspah ngut ki nongbat sum, hamar kaba lai baje mynmiet:",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> bad khreh ruh ki kulai, ba kin pynshong ïa u Paul halor, ba kin ïalam biang biang ïa u ha u Pheliks, u lyngskor.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Bad u la thoh ka shithi kaba kum kane:",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> “U Klaudios Lusias, ha u Pheliks u lyngskor babha tam eh: khublei.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ïa une u briew la kem da ki Jiw, bad sa ba kin pynïap noh ïa u; te haba nga la wan lap ïa ki lem bad ki shipai, nga la pyllait noh ïa u, naba nga la ïoh tip skhem ba u long u trai-shnong Rom.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te ba nga da kwah ban tip ïa ka daw ba ki la mudui ïa u, nga la ïalam noh arsut ïa u sha ka dorbar jong ki;",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> nga la shem ba la mudui ïa u shaphang ki jingïasaid ka hukum jong ki, hynrei, ba ym don ei ei ruh ka jingmudui ba dei ïa ka ban ïap lane ïa ka ban khum.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te ynda nga la tip ba kan long ka jingthap ïa une u briew, shisyndon noh keiñ nga la phah ïa u sha me, nga da hukum skhem ruh ïa kita ki nongmudui jong u ban ïathuh ha khmat jong me ïa kiei kiei ba ki ïaleh ïa u.”",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Ynda kumta, kita ki shipai, kumba la hukum ïa ki, ki la shim ïa u Paul bad ki la ïalam noh ïa u mynmiet haduh Antipatris.",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Te ha kaba lashai, ynda ki la iehnoh ïa kita ki shipai shong kulai ïa ka ban nang leit lem bad u, ki la ïawan phai pat sha kata ka kut.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te kita, haba ki la lah poi ha Kaisaria bad ba ki la lah ai ïa kata ka shithi ha u lyngskor, ki la wallam ïa u Paul ruh ha khmat jong u.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Bad ynda u la lah pule ïa ka, u la kylli na kano ka muluk u long; te ynda u la tip ba u long na Kilikia,",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> “Ngan bishar ïa me,” u ong, “ynda ki nongmudui jong me ruh ki la poi.” U la hukum te ban ap ïa u ha ka ïingbah u Herod."
		},
		"24": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Hadien san sngi te, u Ananias u rangbah lyngdoh u la leit hiar lem bad ki tymmen basan, bad uwei u Tertullos, u riewsaid; te ki la ïa-mihpaw ha khmat uta u lyngskor ïa ka ban ïaleh ïa u Paul.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ynda ki la khot ïa u, u Tertullos u la sdang ban mudui ïa u, u da ong,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> “Namar ba ngi ïaïoh da me shibun ka jingsuk, bad ïa ki kam basniew la pynbeit ha kane ka jaid bynriew da ka jingsumar jong me, ha kaei kaei baroh ruh bad ha ki jaka baroh ngi ïakohnguh, A u Pheliks u babha tam eh, lem bad ka jingsngewnguh baroh.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, ba ngan ym pynbtai ïa me, nga kyrpad ïa me na la ki jingisynei ban sngew ïa ngi shikyntien ar kyntien.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Namar ngi la shem ïa une u briew u nongpynjot, bad uba shet ïa ka jingkhihwin hapdeng ki Jiw baroh kylleng ka pyrthei, u nongïalamphrang ruh ïa kata ka kynja niam jong ki Nasaret.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> U la pyrshang ruh ban pynsang ïa ka templ; ïa une te ngi la ïakem, bad ngi la ïakwah ban bishar kat kum ka hukum jong ngi.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Hynrei, haba u Lusias uta u rangbah shihajar u la poi tiap, u la knieh jubor ïa u na ki kti jong ngi,",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> u da hukum ïa ki nongmudui jong u ban wan ha me; na u, da kaba kylli ïit hi, me lah ban tip biang shaphang kine kiei kiei baroh kiba ngi ïamudui ïa u.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Bad kita ki Jiw ruh ki la ïakohnguh, ki da ïathuh skhem ba kine kiei kiei ruh ki la long kumta.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Te ynda uta u lyngskor u la kohnguh khlieh ïa u ban kren, u Paul u la ïathuh, “Namar ba nga tip ba me long la bun snem u nongbishar ha kane ka jaid bynriew, da kaba sngewbha nga ïasaid-da ïa lade,",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> namar me lah ban tip ba ym pat palat khat-ar sngi naduh ba nga la leit kiew ban mane ha Jerusalem.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Bad kim shym la shem ïa nga ba nga ïasaid nia ha ka templ badno badno ruh, lane pynkhihwin ïa u paidbah, lymne ha ki synagog, lymne ha kata ka nongbah;",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> lymne kim lah ban pynsabut ha me ïa kita kiei kiei ïa kiba ki ïamudui ïa nga mynta.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, ïa kane nga phla ha me, ba ha kata ‘ka Lynti’ ïa kaba ki ïakhot ‘Ka niam kylla jaid’, kumta keiñ nga shakri ïa U Blei ki kpa jong ngi, da kaba ngeit ïa kiei kiei baroh kiba long katba kum Ka Hukum, bad kiba la thoh ha Ki Nongïathuhlypa;",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> ba nga don ka jingkyrmen ha U Blei, ïa kaba kine hi ruh ki ïakhmih lynti, ba kan sa long ka jingmihpat ki baïap, ki bahok ruh bad ki bymhok.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ha kane, nga hi ruh nga pynmlien ïa lade, ban ïoh khlem da pud ka jingïatiplem ba khlem pynthut sha U Blei bad sha ki briew.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Te hadien bun snem, nga la wan ïa ka ban wallam ki jingai isynei ha ka para jaid jong nga, bad ki jingainguh:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> hapdeng kata, ki la shem ïa nga ba la pynkhuid ha ka templ, ym lem bad u paidbah, lymne bad ka jingkhihwin;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> hynrei, la don ki Jiw na Asia, kiba la dei ban don hangne ha khmat jong me, bad ban mudui lada ki la don ei ei pyrshah ïa nga.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Lane kine hi to kin ïathuh, lada ki la shem ei ei ka bymdei katba nga la ïeng ha khmat ka dorbar,",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> lymda tang namar kane kawei ka ktien ïa kaba nga la pyrta mynba nga ïeng hapdeng jong ki, ‘Shaphang ka jingmihpat ki baïap la bishar ïa nga ha kane ka sngi ha khmat jong phi.’ ”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, u Pheliks ba u la tip kham janai shaphang kata “ka Lynti”, u la buh teng noh ïa ki, u da ong, “Ynda u Lusias u rangbah shihajar un wan hiar, ngan sa bishar kut ïa ka kam jong phi.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te u la hukum ïa uta u rangbah shispah ba yn ap ïa u, hynrei, ban ym pyrkhing eh, bad ban ym khang ïano ïano ruh na ki lok jong u ban sumar ïa u.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Ynda katto katne sngi, u Pheliks u la wan poi lem bad ka Drosila ka tnga jong u, kaba long ka Jiw, bad u la phah khot ïa u Paul, bad u la ïohsngew ïa u shaphang kata ka jingngeit ha U Khrist Jisu.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te katba u dang ïalap shaphang ka hok, bad ka bor halor lade, bad ka jingbishar ka ban sa wan, u Pheliks u la sheptieng; bad u la ïathuh, “Mynta, to khie leit noh shuwa; te ynda nga la lait por, ngan sa phah khot ïa me”;",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> u la kyrmen ruh putet ban ïoh sbai na u Paul, naba kumta ruh u la phah khot ïa u kham bunsien, bad u la ïakren bad u.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Hynrei, ynda la dap ar snem, u Porkios Phistos u la wan ha ka jaka u Pheliks; te u Pheliks ba u da mon ban pynsngewbha ïa kita ki Jiw, u la pynsah ïa u Paul ha ki 'saikhum."
		},
		"25": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Ynda u Phistos, namar kata, u la wan ha kata ka muluk, hadien lai sngi u la leit kiew sha Jerusalem na Kaisaria.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad ki rangbah lyngdoh bad kita ki bakhraw batri jong ki Jiw ki la ïapaw ha khmat jong u, ïa ka ban ïaleh ïa u Paul, bad ki la ïakyrpad ïa u,",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> ki da ïapan sngewbha pyrshah ïa u, ba un phah khot ïa u sha Jerusalem; ki da ïa-ap thap ban pynïap noh ïa u ha lynti.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Hynrei, u Phistos u la ïathuh ba la ap phira ïa u Paul ha Kaisaria, bad ba u hi un sa leit noh shen hangta.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> “Namar kata, kita kiba lah hapdeng jong phi,” u ong, “ai kin ïaleit hiar lem bad nga, bad lada don kaei kaei ruh ka bymdei ha une u briew, kin ïamudui ïa u.”",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Te ynda u la lah sah hapdeng jong ki ym tam ïa ka phra ne shiphew sngi, u la leit hiar sha Kaisaria; bad ha kaba lashai u la shong halor ka khet bishar, bad u la hukum ban wallam ïa u Paul.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te ynda u la poi, kita ki Jiw kiba la wan hiar na Jerusalem ki la ïeng tawiar ïa u, ki da ïatian ki jingtian bishar babun bad bakhia pyrshah ïa u Paul, ïa kiba kim lah satia ban pynsabut.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> U Paul pat, ha ka jingïasaid-da ïa lade, u la ong, “Ngam shym la leh pop ei ei ruh ïa ka hukum jong ki Jiw, lymne ïa ka templ, lymne ïa u Kaisar.”",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Hynrei, u Phistos, ba u da mon ban pynsngewbha ïa kita ki Jiw, u la ïathuh ha u Paul, bad u la ong, “Me kwah leit kiew sha Jerusalem, ïa ka ban bishar ïa me hangta shaphang kine kiei kiei ha khmat jong nga?”",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Hynrei, u Paul u la ïathuh, “Nga ïeng keiñ ha khmat ka khet bishar u Kaisar, ha kaba ka dei ban bishar ïa nga. Ngam shym la leh bymdei ïa ki Jiw, kumba me hi ruh me tip bha.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Lada shisha nga la leh bymdei, bad nga la leh ei ei kaba dei ban ïap, ngam kyrngah ïa ka ban ïap; hynrei, lada kine kiei kiei ruh kim long kiba shisha ba kine ki mudui ïa nga, ym don uba lah ban aiti noh ïa nga ha ki. Nga appil ha u Kaisar.”",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Ynda kumta, u Phistos ynda u la lah ïasylla bad kiba ïabishar lem, u la ïathuh, “Me la appil ha u Kaisar? te ha u Kaisar men leit!”",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te ynda la lah khyndiat sngi, u Agrippa syiem, bad ka Berniki ki la ïawan hiar sha Kaisaria ki da khublei ïa u Phistos.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te ba ki la sah hangta kham bun sngi, u Phistos u la buh ïa ka kam u Paul ha khmat u syiem, u da ong, “Don u briew ba la iehnoh teng da u Pheliks ha byndi.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Shaphang jong u, mynba nga la don ha Jerusalem, ki rangbah lyngdoh bad ki tymmen basan jong ki Jiw ki la ïakren ha nga, ki da ïakyrpad ka jingkut bishar pyrshah ïa u.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Ha kiba nga la ïathuh, ba kam long ka rukom ki nong Rom ban aiti noh ïa uno uno ruh u briew, haba uta u nongshah mudui um pat ïoh ïashem markhmat bad kita ki nongmudui, ba un ïoh lad ban da ïa lade shaphang kata kaba ki ïamudui ïa u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Namar kata, mynba ki la lah ïawan lang shane, ngam shym pyntud ei ei, hynrei, kum lashai nga la shong ha ka khet bishar, bad nga la hukum ban wallam ïa uta u briew.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Shaphang jong u, haba kita ki nongmudui ki la mih, kim shym wallam ka jingmudui ïa u shaphang kita kiei kiei ruh ki basniew kumba nga la tharai ma nga.",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> Hynrei, ki la ïadon ki jingïasaid ïaleh ïa u shaphang ka niam jong ki hi, bad shaphang uwei U Jisu ba la ïap, ïa uba u Paul u la ïathuh skhem ba u im.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Nga te ba nga la sngewlyngngoh kumno ban tohkit shaphang kine kiei kiei ruh, nga la kylli lada un leit sha Jerusalem, bad ba hangta yn bishar ïa u shaphang kine kiei kiei.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, mynba u Paul u la lah appil ba yn iehnoh teng ïa u ïa ka jingbishar kut jong u Patsha, nga la hukum ban iehnoh teng ïa u tad ynda ngan ïoh phah ïa u ha u Kaisar.”",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Ynda kumta, u Agrippa u la ong ha u Phistos, “Nga hi ruh nga kwah ban ïohsngew ïa uta u briew.” U ruh u la ong, “Lashai men sa ïohsngew ïa u.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Kumta, kum lashai ynda la lah wan u Agrippa, bad ka Berniki, da ka jingpynpaw burom ka bakhraw, bad ba ki la lah rung sha ka kamra bishar lem bad ki rangbah shihajar bad ki rangbah kiba donnam jong kata ka nongbah, bad haba la hukum u Phistos, la wallam ïa u Paul ha khmat.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te u Phistos u la ong, “Ko syiem Agrippa, bad phi ki rangbah baroh kiba don ha khmat lem bad ngi, phi khmih ïa une u briew, shaphang uba u paidbah Jiw baroh u la wan ïakyrpad ha nga ha Jerusalem ruh bad hangne, ki da ïapyrta ba um dei ban im shuh.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, nga la shem ba um shym la leh ei ei ruh em kaba dei ban ïap, bad haba u hi u la lah appil ha u Patsha, nga la kut jingmut ban phah ïa u.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Shaphang jong u ngam don ei ei ruh kaba thikna ban thoh ha la u kynrad. Naba kumta, nga la wallam ïa u ha khmat jong phi, bad kham tam ha khmat jong me, ko syiem Agrippa, ba hadien kaba kylli bniah ïa u, nga lah ban ïoh ei ei ban thoh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Namar ha nga ka ibieit haba phah ïa u nongsah byndi, ban ym pyni ruh ïa ki jingmudui bapyrshah ïa u.”"
		},
		"26": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Bad u Agrippa u la ong ha u Paul, “La shah ïa me ban kren na ka bynta ïa lade.” Ynda kumta, u Paul u la kner ïa la ka kti, bad u la ïasaid-da ïa lade:",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> “Nga ñiew ïa lade uba suk, ko syiem Agrippa, ha ban sa ïasaid-da ïa lade ha khmat jong me ha kane ka sngi, shaphang kiei kiei baroh ïa kiba la tian bishar ïa nga da ki Jiw;",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> kham tam keiñ naba me long uba shemphang janai ïa ki niam ki rukom bad ïa ki jingïasaid baroh kiba hapdeng ki Jiw. Naba kumta, nga kyrpad ïa me ban sngew ïa nga da kaba ïaishah slem.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> “Ïa ka rukom ka jinglong jingim jong nga te, la myndang khynnah kaba la long naduh kaba mynnyngkong hapdeng ki para jaid jong nga bad ha Jerusalem, ki Jiw baroh ki ïatip;",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> ki da ithuh ïa nga na ka banyngkong, lada ki ïamon ban ïaphla, ba kum ka jaid niam kaba bniah tam jong ka niam jong ngi, nga la long u Pharisi.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Mynta ruh, namar ka jingkyrmen jong kata ka jingkular ba la buh bad kita ki kpa da U Blei, nga la ïeng ba yn bishar ïa nga;",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> sha kata ka jingkular, ki khat-ar jaid jong ngi, haba shakri ïa U Blei da kaba sngew-shitrhem mynmiet bad mynsngi, ki kyrmen ban kot. Shaphang kane ka jingkyrmen, la tian bishar ïa nga da ki Jiw, ko syiem Agrippa.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Balei yn kheiñ kum ka bym lah ngeit ha phi, lada U Blei u pynmih pat ïa ki baïap?",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> “Nga shisha nga la ju tharai ha lade ba ka dei ïa nga ban leh shibun kiei kiei ruh pyrshah ïa ka kyrteng U Jisu u nong Nasaret.",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> Ïa kane, nga la leh ruh ha Jerusalem. Bad shibun ki riewkhuid nga la set ha ki ïing byndi, haba nga la ïoh hukum na ki rangbah lyngdoh; bad mynba la pynïap noh ïa ki, nga la noh ïa la u mawria ba ïakohnguh;",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> da kaba pynshitom ruh ïa ki bunsien ha ki synagog baroh, nga la ju ïaleh ban pynbor ïa ki ban krenbeiñ blei; bad haba nga la bitar lamwir shikatdei eh ïa ki, nga la ju behbeiñ ïa ki wat haduh ki nongbah kiba sha palat ilaka.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> “Ha kane ruh, haba dang leit sha Damaskos, bad ka bor bad ka hukum ruh na kita ki rangbah lyngdoh,",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> hamar shiteng sngi, ko syiem, nga la ïohi ha kata ka lynti ka jingshai na bneng, tam ïa ka jingtyngshaiñ ka sngi, ka da tyngshaiñ sawdong ïa nga, bad ïa kita kiba leit jingleit lem bad nga.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Te mynba ngi la lah kyllon kram baroh ha khyndew, nga la ïohsngew ka ktien ba kren ha nga, ha ka ktien Hebru, ‘Saul, Saul, balei me pynshitombeiñ ïa nga? Ka long kaba eh ïa me ban kynjat pyrshah ïa ki dieng tyndung.’",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Nga la ong te, ‘Me long uei, A Trai?’ Te U Trai u la ïathuh, ‘Nga long U Jisu, ïa uba me pynshitombeiñ ma me.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Hynrei, to khie to ïeng ruh, namar khnang ïa kane keiñ nga la mihpaw ha me, ban thung ïa me ban long u nongïalap bad u nongphla ïa kine kiei kiei ha kiba me la ïohi ïa nga, bad ïa kita kiei kiei ruh ha kiba ngan pynpaw ïa lade ha me,",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> da kaba pyllait noh ïa me na u paidlang, bad na ki Jentil ha kiba nga phah noh ïa me,",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> ban pynpeit ïa ki khmat jong ki, ba kin ïoh phai na ka jingdum sha ka jingshai, bad na ka bor jong u Soitan sha U Blei, ba kin ïoh pdiang kaba map ki pop, bad ka bynta hapdeng kita ïa kiba la pynkhuid da ka jingngeit kaba ha nga.’ ”",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> “Nangta, ko syiem Agrippa, ngam shym la long u bymkohnguh ïa kata ka jingithuhpaw bneng;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> hynrei, nga la ïalap nyngkong ha kiba ha Damaskos, bad ha Jerusalem ruh, bad ha ka ri Judia baroh, bad ha ki Jentil ruh, ba kin kylla-ka-bamut, bad kin phai sha U Blei, da kaba leh ïa ki kam ba dei biang ïa ka jingkylla-ka-bamut.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Namar kane, ki Jiw haba ki la ïakem ïa nga ha ka templ, ki la ïapyrshang ban pynïap noh ïa nga.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Hynrei, haba la ïoh kata ka jingïarap kaba na U Blei, nga ïai-ïeng haduh kane ka sngi, nga da phla ha u barit ruh bad ha u bakhraw, khlem da ong ei ei ruh em tam ïa kaba la lah ong ki nongïathuhlypa bad u Moses ba kin sa long;",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> kumno ba ka la dei ïa U Khrist ban shah, bad kumno nyngkong da ka jingmihpat na ki baïap, un pynbna ka jingshai ha u paidlang ruh, bad ha ki Jentil.”",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te haba u dang ïasaid-da ïa lade kumne, u Phistos u la ong da ka ktien bajam, “Paul, me lamwir! Ka jingbun ka jingstad jong me ka pynlamwir ïa me.”",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Hynrei, u Paul u ong, “Ngam lamwir, ko Phistos u babha tam eh, hynrei, nga kren shynna ki ktien ka jingshisha bad ka jingtipbriew.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Namar u syiem u tip shaphang kine kiei kiei, ha u, namar kata, nga kren da kaba shlur; namar nga ngeit skhem bymdon kawei na kine kiei kiei ba la buhrieh na u; naba ym shym la leh ïa kane ha kyndong.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Ko syiem Agrippa, me ngeit ïa ki nongïathuhlypa? Nga tip ba me ngeit.”",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Ynda kumta, u Agrippa u la ong ha u Paul, “Sa khyndiat men ngeit ba me la pynkohnguh ïa nga ban long Khristan.”",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> U Paul te u la ong, “Nga duwai ha U Blei, ba da kaba khyndiat ne da kaba shibun, ym tang ma me, hynrei, baroh kiba ïohsngew ïa nga ha kane ka sngi, phin ïalong kum nga, lait na kine ki kynjri.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te u syiem u la ïeng joit, bad u lyngskor, bad ka Berniki, bad kita kiba ïashong lem bad ki.",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> Te haba ki la lah ïaleit noh kyrpang, ki la ïakren paralok hi ki da ïa-ong, “Une u briew um shym leh ei ei ruh em kaba dei ïa ka ban ïap, lane ïa ka ban khum.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ynda kumta, u Agrippa u la ong ha u Phistos, “Lah ban pyllait noh ïa une u briew, lada um shym la lah appil ha u Kaisar.”"
		},
		"27": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te mynba la pynkut ba ngin leit da ka lieng sha Itali, ki la ïa-aiti pateng ïa u Paul bad kiwei pat ki nongsah byndi ha u rangbah shispah uba kyrteng “u Julios”, uba na ka kynhun u Agustos.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Te ynda ngi la leit kiew ha ka lieng kaba na Adramyttion, ka ban sa leit ha kita ki jaka jong ka Asia kiba harud duriaw, ngi la ïamih noh; don lem bad ngi u Aristarkhos na Makedonia, u nong Thessaloni.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Te kum lashai ngi la ïahiar ha Sidon. U Julios te, u la leh sbun ïa u Paul, bad u la shah ïa u ban leit sha la ki lok ban ïoh ka jingsumar sukher.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Haba ngi la ïamih noh nangta ruh, ngi la leit da ka lieng hapoh Kypros, namar ba ki lyer ki la pyrshah.",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Te ynda ngi la lah leit lyngba ïa kata ka duriaw kaba pyrshah Kilikia bad Pamphilia, ngi la ïapoi sha Maira, ka shnong jong ka Lykia.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hangta te, uta u rangbah shispah, haba u la shem ka lieng kaba na Aleksandria kaba leit sha Itali, u la pynkiew ïa ngi ha ka.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te haba ngi la lah ïaid lieng mian mian bun sngi, bad la poi da kaba eh ha pyrshah Knidos, ba ka lyer kam da shah shuh ïa ngi, ngi la ïaid hapoh ka Krit ha pyrshah ka Salmoni;",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> bad haba ngi la pynïaid da kaba eh narud narud jong ka, ngi la poi ha kawei ka jaka ba khot, “Ki jaka rieh lieng bajai jai”, hajan kata la don ka shnong Lasia.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te haba la lah pynleit noh bun sngi, bad ka jingïaid lieng ka da long mynta kaba ma; namar Ka Niam Shah Jingit ka la lah palat noh, u Paul u la sneng,",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> bad u la ong ha ki: “Ko rangbah, nga ïohi ba kane ka jingïaid lieng kan sa long lem bad ka jingmynsaw bad shibun ka jingduh, ym tang ïa ka jingkit bad ka lieng, hynrei, ïa ki jingim jong ngi ruh.”",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Hynrei, uta u rangbah shispah u la kham kohnguh ïa u maji bad u trai ka lieng ban ïa kita kiei kiei ba la kren u Paul.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Te namar ba kata ka jaka rieh lieng ka la long ka bymbit ban rieh tlang, kham bun ki la ïakyntu ban pynmih noh nangta, lada da kumno kumno ki lah ban poi haduh Phoiniks, ban rieh tlang hangta, kaba long ka jaka rieh lieng ka Krit, kaba phai shaphang shatei lam mihngi, bad shaphang shathie lam mihngi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Te haba ka lyer na shathie ka la beh jem jai, ba ki da ïamut ba ki la ïoh ïa kaba ki la thmu, ki la ïaring angkor bad ki la ïa-ïaid ha syndah ka Krit, narud narud.",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> Hynrei, ym slem hadien, la beh na ryngkew ka 'erïong, kaba la khot “Ïurakuilo.”",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Te haba la lap ïa ka lieng, bad kam lah ban tur pyrshah ïa ka lyer, ngi la shu shah ïa ka, bad la rong noh ïa ngi.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Bad haba ngi la ïaphet narum iwei i 'dewlynnong ba khot “Klauda”, da kaba eh ngi la lah ban pynskhem ïa ka lieng rit;",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> te haba ki la lah ïakyntiew ïa ka, ki la spaiñ ïa ka lieng bah da ki tyllai; ba ki da sheptieng ruh ïoh yn ñiat ïa ki ha ki jingkyrsoi shyiap Syrtis, ki la ïa-pynhiar ïa ki mastul, kumta la rong noh ïa ki.",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> Te haba ngi la ïaleh tyngeh shikatdei bad ka 'erïong, kum lashai ki la sdang ban bred noh ïa ka jingkit;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> bad ha ka sngi ka balai, ki la ïabred noh da ki kti jong ki hi ïa ki tiar ki tar jong ka lieng.",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> Te mynba ka sngi lymne ki khlur kim paw shuh ha ngi bun sngi, bad ka 'erïong kaba jur ka ban khia ha ngi, ka jingkyrmen ban im ka la duh noh baroh.",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Hynrei, ynda ki la long slem khlem jingbam, ynda kumta, u Paul haba u la ïeng hapdeng jong ki u la ong, “Ko rangbah, ka la dei ïa phi ban shahshkor ïa nga ban ym mih noh na Krit, ïa ka ban ïoh kat kane ka jingmynsaw bad ka jingduh.",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> Mynta ruh nga kyntu ïa phi ba phin sngewshngain; namar napdeng jong phi kan ym jah kawei ka mynsiem ruh, hynrei, tang kane ka lieng.",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Namar la ïeng hajan jong nga ha kane ka miet u angel U Blei, u jong uba nga long, bad ïa uba nga shakri ruh,",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> u da ong, ‘Ko Paul, wat sheptieng; ka dei ïa me ban ïeng ha khmat u Kaisar. Ha khmih ruh U Blei u la ai ha me ïa kito baroh kiba ïaid lieng lem bad me.’",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Naba kumta to sngewshngain phi, ko rangbah; namar nga ngeit ïa U Blei, ba kan long kumta kumba la kren ha nga.",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> Hynrei, ka dei ban kynting noh ïa ngi ha kawei ka 'dewlynnong.”",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Te ynda ka miet ka bakhatsaw ka la poi, katba dang rong pynshad kylleng ïa ngi ha kata ka duriaw Adria; hamar shiteng synñia, kita ki riewlieng ki la ïamut ba ki la jan sha kawei ka ri.",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> Te haba ki la bred da u sisa ban thew, ki la shem arphew pad; te haba ki la lah ïaid khyndiat, ki la ïathew pat, bad ki la shem khatsan pad.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te ba ki da sheptieng ïoh ba kumno re kumno yn kynting ïa ngi ha ki jaka maw, haba ki la ïabred saw tylli ki angkor na ka tdong lieng, ki la ïakwah hir hir ban mih ka sngi.",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> Te katba kita ki riewlieng ki la ïawad lad ban phet ïap noh na kata ka lieng, bad haba ki la lah ïa-pynhiar noh ïa kata ka lieng rit ha ka duriaw, kum ki ban sa pynhiar noh ïa ki angkor na ka khmat lieng,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> u Paul u la ong ha uta u rangbah shispah, bad ha kita ki shipai, “Lymda kine ki sah ha ka lieng, phi phim lah ban ïohlait im.”",
			"32": "<sup>32</sup> Ynda kumta, kita ki shipai ki la ïa-ot noh ïa ki tyllai jong kata ka lieng rit, kumta ki la pyllait ïa ka.",
			"33": "<sup>33</sup> Te katba ka sngi ka la sdang mih, u Paul u la kyrpad ïa ki baroh ban ïabam jingbam, u da ong, “Kane ka dei ka sngi ka bakhatsaw ba phi ïa-ap, bad shah jingit khlem da bam ei ei.",
			"34": "<sup>34</sup> Naba kumta, nga kyrpad ïa phi ban ïabam jingbam; namar kane ka long khnang ïa ka ban pynim ïa phi; namar iwei i shñiuh in ym hap na ka khlieh jongno jongno ruh na phi.”",
			"35": "<sup>35</sup> Te haba u la lah ong ïa kane, bad haba u la lah shim ïa u kpu, u la ainguh ïa U Blei ha khmat jong ki baroh; bad u la kdiah ïa u, bad u la sdang ban bam.",
			"36": "<sup>36</sup> Ynda kumta, baroh ki la ïasngew im, ki hi ruh ki la ïabam jingbam.",
			"37": "<sup>37</sup> Te ngi la don baroh ha kata ka lieng, arspah hynñiewphew hynriew ki mynsiem.",
			"38": "<sup>38</sup> Te ynda ki la lah ïabam ïasa, ki la ïa-pynsting ïa kata ka lieng da kaba bred noh ïa u Kew sha ka duriaw.",
			"39": "<sup>39</sup> Te haba ka lashai, kim shym ithuh ïa kata ka ri; hynrei, ki la ïohi ïa kawei ka kdong um kaba don ka rud duriaw shyiap, bad ki la ïapyrkhat lada ki lah ban pynsah kut noh ïa kata ka lieng hangta.",
			"40": "<sup>40</sup> Kumta te, haba ki la lah pyllait noh ïa kita ki angkor, ki la iehnoh ïa ki ha duriaw, ki ïapynsynjor artad ïa ki tyllai ki boitha, bad haba ki la lah pynïeng ïa ka phar kaba sha khmat sha ka lyer, ki la ïaking sha kata ka rud duriaw.",
			"41": "<sup>41</sup> Hynrei, haba la kyndat ïa ki ha ka jaka kaba ïashem ar duriaw, ki la pynsuh ïa kata ka lieng sha ryngkew; te kumta ka khmat lieng ka la kiew ryngkew bad ka la neh den, hynrei, ka tdong lieng ka la sdang pait da ka bor jong ki jingat phyllung.",
			"42": "<sup>42</sup> Te ka jingthmu jong kita ki shipai ka la long ba kin pynïap noh ïa kita ki koidi, ïoh ba uno uno ruh na ki un jngi sha ryngkew bad un lait noh.",
			"43": "<sup>43</sup> Hynrei, uta u rangbah shispah, ba u da kwah ban pynim ïa u Paul, u la khang noh ïa ki na kata ka jingthmu, bad u la hukum kat kiba nang jngi ba kin ryngkoh na ka lieng, bad ban poi nyngkong sha ryngkew,",
			"44": "<sup>44</sup> bad ïa kita kiba sah, kiwei halor ki lyntang, kiwei pat de halor kiwei kiei kiei ruh kiba na kata ka lieng. Kumta te, ka la jia ba baroh ki la lait im sha ka ryngkew."
		},
		"28": {
			"1": "<sup>1</sup> Te ynda ngi la ïohlait im, ynda kumta ngi la ïatip ba khot kyrteng ïa kata ka 'dewlynnong “Melita”.",
			"2": "<sup>2</sup> Bad kita ki nongkyndong ki la pyni ka jingleh ieit ïa ngi kaba kham phylla, namar ki la sliew ding, bad ki la ïakhot sngewbha ïa ngi baroh, namar uta u slap uba mynkata, bad namar ka jingpjah.",
			"3": "<sup>3</sup> Hynrei, u Paul haba u la lah khar shi bah ki dieng, bad u la lah tei ïa ki ha ding, u 'seiñpuh u la mih noh namar ba shit, bad u la snoh na ka kti jong u.",
			"4": "<sup>4</sup> Te mynba kita ki nongkyndong ki la ïohi ïa uta u mrad ba u sdien na ka kti jong u, ki la ïa-ong paralok, “Khlem artatien une u briew u long u nongpynïap briew, uba, la u la ïohlait na ka duriaw, ka kput kam shym la shah ba un im.”",
			"5": "<sup>5</sup> Pynban, haba u la kynther noh ïa uta u mrad ha ding, um pang ei ei.",
			"6": "<sup>6</sup> Hynrei, ki la ïakhmih lynti ba un sa sieb noh, lane ba un sa kyllon ïap shisyndon, hynrei, haba ki dang ïakhmih lynti slem bad ki la ïohi ba um shym sniew ei ei ruh, ki la ïakylla jingmut, bad ki la ong ba u long u blei.",
			"7": "<sup>7</sup> Te hajan kata ka jaka la don ki khyndew ki jong u rangbah kata ka 'dewlynnong, uba kyrteng “u Publios”; une u la pdiang ïa ngi bad u la sumar bha ïa ngi lai sngi da kaba lehburom.",
			"8": "<sup>8</sup> Ka la jia ruh ba u kpa uta u Publios u la pang khieshoh bad ka suhot, ha uba u Paul u la leit rung, bad haba u la duwai, bad u la buh ïa la ki kti ha u, u la pynkhiah ïa u.",
			"9": "<sup>9</sup> Te ynda la leh ïa kane, kita kiwei ruh kiba la don ki jingpang ha kata ka 'dewlynnong ki la ïawan ha u, bad la pynkhiah ïa ki;",
			"10": "<sup>10</sup> kiba la ïaleh burom ruh ïa ngi da shibun ki jingai burom, te haba ngi la ïa-pynmih noh, ki la ïabuh ha ka lieng ïa kiei kiei katba ngi donkam.",
			"11": "<sup>11</sup> Te hadien lai bnai ngi la ïa-pynmih noh ha ka lieng kaba na Aleksandria, kaba la rieh tlang ha kata ka 'dewlynnong, kaba ka dak jong ka “ki Dioskuri”.",
			"12": "<sup>12</sup> Haba ngi la lah ïahiar ruh ha Surakus, ngi la sah hangta, lai sngi.",
			"13": "<sup>13</sup> Nangta haba ngi la ïaid kyrwiang ngi la poi ha Rhejiom; bad hadien kawei ka sngi, la mih ka lyer kaba na shathie, bad ha ka ba-ar sngi, ngi la poi ha Putioli;",
			"14": "<sup>14</sup> hangta ngi la shem ki parabangeit, bad ki la kyrpad ïa ngi ban sah bad ki, hynñiew sngi. Te kumta ngi la poi sha Rom.",
			"15": "<sup>15</sup> Bad nangta ki parabangeit haba ki la lah ïohsngew shaphang jong ngi, ki la ïamih noh ïa ka ban wan tan ïa ngi haduh “Ka Ïew Apios”, bad “Ki Lai ïingbasa”, ïa kiba haba u Paul u la ïohi, u la nguh ïa U Blei, bad u la sngewshngain.",
			"16": "<sup>16</sup> Te mynba ngi la poi ha Rom, uta u rangbah shispah u la aiti ïa kita ki nongsah byndi ha u lyngskor kynhun shipai, hynrei, la shah ïa u Paul ban shong kyrpang marwei, lem bad u shipai uba ap ïa u.",
			"17": "<sup>17</sup> Ka la jia ruh hadien lai sngi, ba u la khot ïaseng ïa kita kiba kham rangbah jong ki Jiw; te ynda ki la ïawan lang, u la ong ha ki, “Ko para, nga, la ngam shym la leh ei ei ruh em pyrshah ïa u paidlang, lane ïa kita ki niam ki rukom ki kpa tymmen jong ngi, pynban, la aiti noh ïa nga kum u nongsah byndi na Jerusalem ha ki kti ki nong Rom:",
			"18": "<sup>18</sup> kiba la kwah, ynda ki la lah kylli ïit ïa nga, ban pyllait noh ïa nga, namar ba ym don ei ei ka daw ïa nga ban ïap;",
			"19": "<sup>19</sup> hynrei, haba ki Jiw ki la kren pyrshah ïa kata, la pynleh keiñ ïa nga ban appil ha u Kaisar; ym ba nga don ei ei ban mudui ïa ka kynja jong nga;",
			"20": "<sup>20</sup> kumta, na kane ka daw, nga la khot ïa phi ban ïohi, bad ban ïoh ïakren bad nga; naba na ka bynta ka jingkyrmen jong ki Israel la khum ïa nga da une u kynjri.”",
			"21": "<sup>21</sup> Ki te ki la ïa-ong ha u, “Ngi ngim shym la ïoh ki shithi na Judia shaphang jong me, lymne mano mano na kita ki para kim shym wan shane ban ïathuh lane kren ei ei ka basniew shaphang jong me;",
			"22": "<sup>22</sup> hynrei, ngi ïakwah ban ïohsngew na me, me mut kumno; namar shaphang kane ka kynja niam ngi la tip ba la krenbeiñ ïa ka kylleng la kylleng.”",
			"23": "<sup>23</sup> Te kumta haba ki la ïabuh sngi bad u, ki la ïawan shibun ha u hapoh ka ïingbasa jong u; ha kita u la pynpaw, u da phla ïa ka hima U Blei, bad u da pynkohnguh ïa ki shaphang U Jisu, na Ka Hukum u Moses, bad na Ki Nongïathuhlypa ruh, naduh mynstep haduh janmiet.",
			"24": "<sup>24</sup> Te don kiba la ngeit ïa kiei kiei ruh ba la kren, hynrei, don ki bym shym la ngeit.",
			"25": "<sup>25</sup> Te haba kim ïadei jingmut paralok hi, ki la ïaleit noh, ynda u Paul u la lah ong shikyntien, “Kaba dei ba la kren U Mynsiem Bakhuid da u Isaïah u nongïathuhlypa ha ki kpa jong phi,",
			"26": "<sup>26</sup> u da ong: “ ‘To khie leit ha une u paidlang, to ong ruh: “Da kaba ïohsngew phin ïohsngew, te phin ym sngewthuh shuh; bad haba ïohi phin ïohi, hynrei, phin ym ishemphang shuh.",
			"27": "<sup>27</sup> Namar ka dohnud jong une u paidlang ka la rben, bad ki la sngewkhia da la ki shkor, bad ki la khapbrip ïa la ki khmat, ba ïoh kin ïohi da la ki khmat, bad ba kin ïohsngew da la ki shkor, bad ba kin sngewthuh da la ka dohnud, bad ba kin kylla pat, bad ba ngan pynkhiah ïa ki.” ’",
			"28": "<sup>28</sup> “Namar kata, to tip phi, ba la phah ïa kane ka jingpynim U Blei ha ki Jentil; ki ruh kin ïohsngew ïa ka.",
			"29": "<sup>29</sup> Te ynda u la lah ong ïa kine ki ktien, kita ki Jiw ki la ïaleit noh, ki da ïadon shibun ka jingïasaid kylliang paralok hi.”",
			"30": "<sup>30</sup> U te u la shong ar snem kynthih ha ka ïing ba u la wai hi, bad u pdiang baroh kiba wan hapoh ha u,",
			"31": "<sup>31</sup> u da ïalap ïa ka hima U Blei, bad u da hikai ïa kiei kiei ruh shaphang U Jisu Khrist uba U Trai da ka jingsngewshlur suda, bymdon ba khang ïa u."
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;